WEBVTT

0
00:00:04.416 --> 00:00:08.416
This subtitle is a fan-made translation and
not affiliated with the original content creators.

1
00:01:26.067 --> 00:01:30.404
"Will you not look at me?"

2
00:01:33.972 --> 00:01:39.213
"Why not take a look properly?"

3
00:01:39.805 --> 00:01:45.661
"Like a peacock longing for the rain to be
as I pass by. won't you look at me?"

4
00:01:45.686 --> 00:01:48.246
"Will you not talk to me?
Why not talk properly?"

5
00:01:48.246 --> 00:01:51.366
"Why can't you chat lovingly?"

6
00:01:51.571 --> 00:01:56.406
"Like a honeyed Tamil song of glee
won't you speak to me melodiously?"

7
00:01:57.362 --> 00:02:02.869
"Will you not look at me?
Why not take a look properly?"

8
00:02:03.206 --> 00:02:09.047
"Like a peacock longing for a sky cloudy
as I pass by. won't you look at me?"

9
00:02:09.086 --> 00:02:14.409
"Will you not talk to me?
Why can't you chat lovingly?"

10
00:02:14.918 --> 00:02:20.678
"Like a honeyed Tamil song of glee
won't you speak to me melodiously?"

11
00:02:32.046 --> 00:02:33.446
[temple bell ringing]

12
00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:38.641
[mobile alarm beeps]

13
00:02:43.662 --> 00:02:44.782
[steam hissing]

14
00:02:53.526 --> 00:02:54.622
[dog barking]

15
00:02:54.820 --> 00:02:56.293
[alarm beeping continues]

16
00:02:58.542 --> 00:03:00.062
[steam hissing louder]

17
00:03:01.607 --> 00:03:02.726
Sakthi

18
00:03:03.675 --> 00:03:04.755
'Sakthi?'

19
00:03:04.923 --> 00:03:05.979
Hmmmm

20
00:03:06.003 --> 00:03:07.404
Hey Parasakthi

21
00:03:08.238 --> 00:03:09.326
Hmmm!

22
00:03:09.350 --> 00:03:10.735
'You wake up at 8'o clock'

23
00:03:10.759 --> 00:03:13.727
'Then why do you keep your alarm
from 6:00 a.m and bug us?'

24
00:03:13.967 --> 00:03:15.047
'Hey Parasakthi'

25
00:03:15.409 --> 00:03:16.809
Do you have college or not?

26
00:03:17.195 --> 00:03:18.476
No. ma

27
00:03:19.036 --> 00:03:20.044
Then okay

28
00:03:21.606 --> 00:03:22.806
Exam. ma

29
00:03:23.707 --> 00:03:24.947
Exam?!

30
00:03:25.247 --> 00:03:26.966
'Will you get out of bed or shall I come?'

31
00:03:30.606 --> 00:03:31.727
Pcccht!!

32
00:03:37.484 --> 00:03:38.872
[rapping on door]

33
00:03:38.985 --> 00:03:40.026
Madhu?

34
00:03:40.247 --> 00:03:41.286
Hey Madhu

35
00:03:42.658 --> 00:03:43.664
Amma...?

36
00:03:43.689 --> 00:03:45.814
You've been sitting in the loo
for an hour and a half

37
00:03:45.892 --> 00:03:47.126
'Intend coming out or not?'

38
00:03:47.150 --> 00:03:48.291
[loud rap on door]

39
00:03:48.580 --> 00:03:50.166
'Hey! Come out. di'

40
00:03:50.343 --> 00:03:51.421
HEY!

41
00:03:51.446 --> 00:03:54.047
[rhythmic rapping on door]

42
00:04:02.606 --> 00:04:03.726
What. di?

43
00:04:06.074 --> 00:04:08.017
Please. open the door. di

44
00:04:09.527 --> 00:04:10.607
Pcccht!

45
00:04:12.806 --> 00:04:13.919
Hey! Listen

46
00:04:16.367 --> 00:04:19.145
Hey Madhu. used up the water
and dancing here happily

47
00:04:19.806 --> 00:04:21.806
Hey! No one else needs to
bathe other than you?

48
00:04:22.727 --> 00:04:24.167
[door bell rings]

49
00:04:27.047 --> 00:04:28.286
Is this Parimala's residence?

50
00:04:28.357 --> 00:04:29.876
Yes. Parimala's family

51
00:04:30.028 --> 00:04:32.286
- You are...?
- We are here to verify voter details

52
00:04:32.346 --> 00:04:33.426
Who is Parimala?

53
00:04:33.548 --> 00:04:34.588
Appa

54
00:04:34.667 --> 00:04:35.667
Your father?

55
00:04:35.886 --> 00:04:37.526
Yes. Parimala is my appa

56
00:04:38.333 --> 00:04:39.333
Yes

57
00:04:39.566 --> 00:04:40.847
I am Parimala

58
00:04:41.206 --> 00:04:42.322
My grandmother's name

59
00:04:42.346 --> 00:04:43.706
Pccht! Just a sentiment

60
00:04:46.526 --> 00:04:47.664
Who is Sudhandhiram?

61
00:04:48.013 --> 00:04:49.053
Amma

62
00:04:49.127 --> 00:04:51.647
I was born on August 15th
That's why my name means freedom!

63
00:04:51.686 --> 00:04:53.766
I haven't got any freedom
for anything so far!

64
00:04:53.766 --> 00:04:55.926
I stepped into this kitchen 20 years ago

65
00:04:55.967 --> 00:04:56.982
Parasakthi?

66
00:04:57.126 --> 00:04:58.127
Enemy

67
00:04:58.343 --> 00:04:59.633
Sorry...sorry. my elder sister

68
00:05:01.926 --> 00:05:03.606
- Madhu?
- Madhumitha

69
00:05:03.764 --> 00:05:04.803
That's me

70
00:05:04.827 --> 00:05:05.867
S.I.R. huh?

71
00:05:05.891 --> 00:05:06.973
- Yes. sir
- Oh!

72
00:05:06.997 --> 00:05:08.726
- Will we be able to vote?
- Yes. sir

73
00:05:08.766 --> 00:05:10.127
Okay...okay
Move. move aside

74
00:05:10.686 --> 00:05:11.846
Give me way
Right of way

75
00:05:13.286 --> 00:05:14.606
Anyone else in your family?

76
00:05:14.606 --> 00:05:16.326
- Tina?
- Your younger sister?

77
00:05:16.727 --> 00:05:17.773
Over there

78
00:05:17.993 --> 00:05:19.232
[dog barking]

79
00:05:19.607 --> 00:05:21.407
Before her. we had Rina

80
00:05:21.686 --> 00:05:22.926
Pccht! She died

81
00:05:24.362 --> 00:05:25.400
- Fill this form
- Okay

82
00:05:25.790 --> 00:05:28.846
'Sudhandhiram. Rs 2000
for 1 gas cylinder'

83
00:05:29.914 --> 00:05:31.714
'If we book now
we will get after 1 month'

84
00:05:41.933 --> 00:05:43.697
Were you drunk
when you named me 'Madhu'. pa?

85
00:05:43.722 --> 00:05:45.246
Whoever pronounces 'Madhu'

86
00:05:45.246 --> 00:05:47.635
They don't even emphasize
They draaag my name to the fullest

87
00:05:47.660 --> 00:05:49.486
Parasakthi
I chose that name

88
00:05:49.926 --> 00:05:51.647
Madhumitha
Your mother's selection

89
00:05:51.919 --> 00:05:54.238
When we were traveling by train
from her hometown Palakkad

90
00:05:54.263 --> 00:05:56.702
She thought long and deep
and came up with your name

91
00:05:57.206 --> 00:05:58.806
- Ready. ma
- So soon. di?

92
00:05:59.319 --> 00:06:00.951
- Showered?
- I washed my face

93
00:06:00.975 --> 00:06:03.331
I dabbed perfume all over
I'll shower after my exam. bye

94
00:06:03.356 --> 00:06:04.906
How will Goddess Saraswati bless you?

95
00:06:05.770 --> 00:06:07.210
Now do you understand?

96
00:06:07.326 --> 00:06:09.287
Why even Goddess Lakshmi
doesn't enter our house?

97
00:06:10.286 --> 00:06:12.527
You'll say. because of her
you didn't find your Mr Right

98
00:06:12.527 --> 00:06:13.686
Go

99
00:06:14.046 --> 00:06:15.806
Is this how you talk to a girl?

100
00:06:16.046 --> 00:06:17.166
Wretched wife!

101
00:06:18.404 --> 00:06:20.804
Why will I say this if she behaves
like a prim & proper girl?

102
00:06:20.927 --> 00:06:22.727
Your mother has come back in her form

103
00:06:24.047 --> 00:06:27.047
If you don't drag my mother
every single day. you can't sleep in peace!

104
00:06:27.606 --> 00:06:31.367
A daughter-in-law mudslinging
her mother-in-law and vice versa

105
00:06:31.526 --> 00:06:33.846
That is the order of the day
in every corner of India

106
00:06:33.887 --> 00:06:35.886
That too. in middle class
100% impossible

107
00:06:45.435 --> 00:06:46.835
[crow cawing]

108
00:06:47.447 --> 00:06:49.046
[water overflowing]

109
00:06:52.001 --> 00:06:53.601
[door bell rings]

110
00:06:55.446 --> 00:06:57.566
Who has placed a flower pot on my doorstep?

111
00:06:57.667 --> 00:06:58.927
Huh? Flower pot?

112
00:07:01.521 --> 00:07:03.681
Oh! Uyir Ulag brother

113
00:07:03.740 --> 00:07:05.204
I got confused. come in

114
00:07:06.760 --> 00:07:08.307
Tell me why I rang your door bell?

115
00:07:09.476 --> 00:07:12.324
Must be short term memory loss
I've already paid your rent

116
00:07:12.525 --> 00:07:13.685
What if you've paid?

117
00:07:14.166 --> 00:07:15.767
Switching on the motor often

118
00:07:15.987 --> 00:07:17.755
Is this how you will
waste precious water?

119
00:07:17.780 --> 00:07:20.540
Aiyo! My eldest daughter Sakthi's doing

120
00:07:20.639 --> 00:07:23.294
She will insert the charger cable?
She will forget to switch it on

121
00:07:25.007 --> 00:07:27.647
She will switch on the motor
and forget to switch it off

122
00:07:27.767 --> 00:07:29.406
- Switch on the fan-
- Enough. stop

123
00:07:30.020 --> 00:07:31.820
- Enough?
- This is my house

124
00:07:31.926 --> 00:07:32.927
Hope you remember that?

125
00:07:32.966 --> 00:07:34.959
Of course. that's why
I look after it as my own

126
00:07:34.983 --> 00:07:37.646
Don't change the ownership documents
Just pay the rent promptly

127
00:07:37.984 --> 00:07:39.034
Okay?

128
00:07:39.059 --> 00:07:40.156
Definitely

129
00:07:50.646 --> 00:07:51.767
[clearing throat]

130
00:07:51.966 --> 00:07:53.447
What do you want for dinner?

131
00:07:54.006 --> 00:07:55.007
'Idli'

132
00:07:55.166 --> 00:07:56.246
'Dosa'

133
00:07:56.246 --> 00:07:57.287
'Chappathi'

134
00:07:57.326 --> 00:07:58.806
- All 3
- 'No'

135
00:07:58.953 --> 00:07:59.984
Only 1 option

136
00:08:01.806 --> 00:08:03.126
- Chappathi
- Dosa

137
00:08:03.126 --> 00:08:04.487
- Idli
- Okay

138
00:08:04.886 --> 00:08:05.927
Then it is 'pongal'

139
00:08:06.558 --> 00:08:07.559
[dog barking]

140
00:08:07.637 --> 00:08:09.041
Not for you. darling

141
00:08:09.287 --> 00:08:10.926
Your favorite bread omelet for you

142
00:08:11.327 --> 00:08:12.846
Pongal was not even in your list

143
00:08:13.206 --> 00:08:14.846
Your votes got split. one each

144
00:08:15.126 --> 00:08:17.766
This committee decided on 'pongal'

145
00:08:20.286 --> 00:08:23.246
Aiyo! No need rice and lentil at night. ma

146
00:08:23.886 --> 00:08:26.006
Appa wanted chappathi. right?
I'll vote for the same

147
00:08:26.526 --> 00:08:27.767
I vote for chappathi too

148
00:08:28.961 --> 00:08:30.366
3 votes counted

149
00:08:30.806 --> 00:08:33.528
Committee has decided
on 'chappathi' for dinner

150
00:08:33.686 --> 00:08:35.166
I want only dosa

151
00:08:35.412 --> 00:08:37.533
Okay. dear
You can have your dosa

152
00:08:37.570 --> 00:08:39.970
Give her Rs 50 in her account

153
00:08:40.127 --> 00:08:42.167
She can have her dosa
in the roadside mobile eatery

154
00:08:42.287 --> 00:08:43.349
Go. my dear

155
00:08:44.567 --> 00:08:46.326
[shared chuckle]

156
00:08:49.659 --> 00:08:50.739
8

157
00:08:51.113 --> 00:08:52.353
8:30

158
00:08:52.766 --> 00:08:53.966
9

159
00:08:54.206 --> 00:08:55.247
What is that?

160
00:08:55.271 --> 00:08:56.790
If I cook all by myself. 9

161
00:08:56.886 --> 00:08:59.126
If one of the girls help. 8:30

162
00:08:59.366 --> 00:09:00.806
If everyone lends a hand. then 8

163
00:09:08.631 --> 00:09:09.791
8

164
00:09:09.937 --> 00:09:11.004
Okay

165
00:09:11.029 --> 00:09:12.047
- Okay
- 8

166
00:09:12.868 --> 00:09:13.915
I choose 8 too

167
00:09:14.646 --> 00:09:15.983
Then I agree to 8:00 p.m too

168
00:09:16.007 --> 00:09:17.447
Okay. come on

169
00:09:17.641 --> 00:09:18.721
Tina. come

170
00:09:25.352 --> 00:09:29.286
"While Time usually races right through
its hands now stand still for you"

171
00:09:29.310 --> 00:09:30.551
Parasakthi

172
00:09:30.575 --> 00:09:31.621
'Open the damn door'

173
00:09:31.646 --> 00:09:33.326
Parasakthi
Parasakthi

174
00:09:33.374 --> 00:09:40.094
"The tune that runs online
a real koel sings 'live' so divine"

175
00:09:40.616 --> 00:09:47.038
"Will sadness fade anew
into the sky. out of view?"

176
00:09:48.027 --> 00:09:54.747
"Will gladness out of the blue
climb on the rooftop seeking you?"

177
00:10:08.726 --> 00:10:10.286
- Coffee
- In 10 minutes

178
00:10:10.616 --> 00:10:12.056
Can you get me juice?

179
00:10:13.046 --> 00:10:14.126
Juice

180
00:10:14.126 --> 00:10:16.646
In 10 minutes
can you give me soup?

181
00:10:17.606 --> 00:10:19.607
- Soup
- Buttermilk?

182
00:10:20.046 --> 00:10:22.046
- Buttermilk
- Can you make black coffee for me?

183
00:10:22.076 --> 00:10:23.196
Black coffee?

184
00:10:23.220 --> 00:10:24.954
Give your stomach
some rest please

185
00:10:25.646 --> 00:10:26.966
Why are you stalking me?

186
00:10:27.486 --> 00:10:29.726
- I like you
- Took you 13 months to say this?

187
00:10:30.999 --> 00:10:33.419
My horoscope has certified me
as a stubborn. headstrong shrew

188
00:10:33.444 --> 00:10:36.348
My husband has to toe my line
My amma tried her best to reform me

189
00:10:36.446 --> 00:10:39.446
No way. she has changed her ways now
Falling in line with my wishes

190
00:10:39.606 --> 00:10:41.966
To sift and sieve and
marry such a strong-willed girl

191
00:10:42.006 --> 00:10:43.007
That's my ambition

192
00:10:44.366 --> 00:10:45.606
What a weirdo!

193
00:10:45.630 --> 00:10:49.782
"If spice is lessened in chutney
will that change its name. tell me?"

194
00:10:49.806 --> 00:10:52.945
Iran is being bombed and
you are hitting coins here

195
00:10:52.969 --> 00:10:57.287
"Like the 4 wheels moving a car
let's always stay as a family together"

196
00:10:57.311 --> 00:10:58.671
Is my black coffee ready?

197
00:10:59.356 --> 00:11:00.556
What-
HEY!

198
00:11:00.686 --> 00:11:01.727
I swear!

199
00:11:02.606 --> 00:11:03.846
What to do with this family?

200
00:11:03.887 --> 00:11:05.726
YOV! Parimi

201
00:11:07.086 --> 00:11:09.264
Even the dog barks in reply
But their lips are zipped!

202
00:11:09.289 --> 00:11:13.247
"Will gladness climb anew
the terrace in search of you?"

203
00:11:19.766 --> 00:11:21.446
Uncle...uncle

204
00:11:25.007 --> 00:11:27.606
The water is mossy green
because the tank hasn't been cleaned

205
00:11:27.647 --> 00:11:29.207
- So?
- Tank has to be cleaned

206
00:11:29.207 --> 00:11:30.606
Hire someone to clean it

207
00:11:31.046 --> 00:11:32.366
We can do it ourselves

208
00:11:33.246 --> 00:11:34.406
Not enough. no. di?

209
00:11:37.382 --> 00:11:38.403
'Aiyaiyo!'

210
00:11:39.726 --> 00:11:40.847
I'll get even with you

211
00:11:42.366 --> 00:11:43.406
Appa!

212
00:11:43.446 --> 00:11:44.486
Let go of me. di

213
00:11:47.966 --> 00:11:50.846
No one in this world is worse
than those who fall in love

214
00:11:50.927 --> 00:11:53.192
'Dress isn't good. color is bad
Why do you use lipstick?'

215
00:11:53.217 --> 00:11:55.729
'Who is that chap? Who is this fellow?
Why do you talk to him?'

216
00:11:55.754 --> 00:11:57.326
Aiyo! Plaguing questions

217
00:11:57.366 --> 00:11:58.487
'And killing me'

218
00:11:58.766 --> 00:12:01.046
Such control freaks are
just not my type at all

219
00:12:01.086 --> 00:12:02.886
Describing your character as mine

220
00:12:03.126 --> 00:12:04.686
I like that very much

221
00:12:05.366 --> 00:12:06.926
- Let's see
- See you

222
00:12:11.037 --> 00:12:12.223
Your pot is full. move

223
00:12:12.247 --> 00:12:14.207
Hey! Is this free Govt water supply?

224
00:12:14.207 --> 00:12:15.542
We informed your owner

225
00:12:15.566 --> 00:12:17.486
- What? Owner-
- Go and ask him whatever

226
00:12:17.721 --> 00:12:19.253
Parimi...hey!

227
00:12:19.342 --> 00:12:21.422
- What is it?
- Neighbor females are taking our water

228
00:12:21.447 --> 00:12:22.474
Where is your father. di?

229
00:12:22.499 --> 00:12:23.695
Appa is bathing

230
00:12:23.846 --> 00:12:26.124
Whaaat? Ask him to come out and bathe!

231
00:12:26.526 --> 00:12:27.891
Should ask him to vacate at once

232
00:12:27.916 --> 00:12:29.956
Hey. take your damn pot and get out

233
00:12:33.383 --> 00:12:34.463
Uncle

234
00:12:34.582 --> 00:12:35.662
Your look

235
00:12:35.687 --> 00:12:36.850
Awe...some

236
00:12:39.526 --> 00:12:40.902
[dog barking]

237
00:12:40.926 --> 00:12:42.246
Parimala uncle

238
00:12:42.246 --> 00:12:43.367
'Madhu darling'

239
00:12:43.406 --> 00:12:44.447
She is not my lady-love

240
00:12:45.446 --> 00:12:46.487
My liiife

241
00:12:47.526 --> 00:12:50.366
Your words and actions
are not at all decent

242
00:12:50.567 --> 00:12:52.247
Don't follow my daughter hereafter

243
00:12:52.286 --> 00:12:54.512
Not follow her even in FB
and Insta too. Parimala uncle?

244
00:12:54.714 --> 00:12:55.751
Don't stalk-

245
00:12:58.166 --> 00:12:59.166
Hi

246
00:13:02.304 --> 00:13:04.344
I'll kidnap Madhumitha
and marry her. challenge?

247
00:13:04.503 --> 00:13:05.557
Weed weirdo

248
00:13:05.743 --> 00:13:07.104
Why is appa talking to that creep?

249
00:13:07.767 --> 00:13:09.542
He has been acting cheap with Madh-

250
00:13:09.566 --> 00:13:10.566
Hey Madhu darling

251
00:13:10.727 --> 00:13:12.366
- I love you
- Chee!

252
00:13:12.407 --> 00:13:13.453
Yuck. huh?

253
00:13:15.126 --> 00:13:16.686
Madhu darling
Want to taste this fish?

254
00:13:17.188 --> 00:13:18.978
- Get lost. madcap!
- Wowww!

255
00:13:19.002 --> 00:13:20.122
Real torture it seems

256
00:13:20.366 --> 00:13:22.406
How can he torture a 'torture'. ma?

257
00:13:22.847 --> 00:13:24.167
Torture squared!

258
00:13:24.206 --> 00:13:25.247
You go inside

259
00:13:25.286 --> 00:13:26.567
'Hello. 'freedom' aunty'

260
00:13:26.606 --> 00:13:28.166
'You tell
Give me your daughter'

261
00:13:28.367 --> 00:13:29.927
Dai! I'll break your teeth

262
00:13:30.246 --> 00:13:31.886
One more step and I will slap you

263
00:13:31.886 --> 00:13:33.294
Public place. so I'm sparing you

264
00:13:33.318 --> 00:13:35.687
Okay uncle. how many time
you beat also. beat...beat

265
00:13:35.945 --> 00:13:36.985
Go in

266
00:13:37.011 --> 00:13:38.290
And me. Madhumitha

267
00:13:38.314 --> 00:13:39.634
'Loving and marriaging'

268
00:13:39.658 --> 00:13:41.378
'And sitting my bike and riding'

269
00:13:41.474 --> 00:13:42.914
How...how...how beautiful. uncle

270
00:13:43.086 --> 00:13:45.887
So you...marriage
your daughter with me

271
00:13:46.046 --> 00:13:48.566
'Uncle. it will be wonderful
if we dance together as a family'

272
00:13:51.286 --> 00:13:52.405
Hey! Go away. please

273
00:13:52.491 --> 00:13:53.612
Why is he stepping out?

274
00:13:53.636 --> 00:13:55.803
- Uncle. why are you praying?
- Listen. please go

275
00:13:55.878 --> 00:13:57.024
Amma. 1 coffee

276
00:13:59.308 --> 00:14:01.127
This bold babe is ready to fight

277
00:14:01.679 --> 00:14:03.471
- 'Why tension?'
- You there!

278
00:14:04.554 --> 00:14:06.117
- Look at her. ma
- I am watching you

279
00:14:06.140 --> 00:14:07.650
You are stepping off limit?

280
00:14:07.674 --> 00:14:09.462
Humiliating my dad
in the middle of the road

281
00:14:09.486 --> 00:14:11.207
Huh? Think you're a big shot?

282
00:14:11.231 --> 00:14:12.551
Please. Parasakthi

283
00:14:13.622 --> 00:14:15.902
I thought she's a student
She's even ready to kill

284
00:14:16.155 --> 00:14:18.627
Excusing you only because
you are my babe's akka. otherwise-

285
00:14:19.138 --> 00:14:21.224
Before I bash up your face
shut your gob and get lost

286
00:14:25.286 --> 00:14:27.164
Uncle. what upbringing?

287
00:14:28.289 --> 00:14:29.592
- What the hell?
- Parasakthi

288
00:14:29.617 --> 00:14:32.083
I won't hesitate this is a road
You'll hang your head in shame

289
00:14:32.108 --> 00:14:33.153
Go inside. pa

290
00:14:33.178 --> 00:14:34.639
What are you gawking at? Go away

291
00:14:34.663 --> 00:14:35.687
Please...please

292
00:14:35.726 --> 00:14:38.286
Clear out before I spit on your face

293
00:14:38.286 --> 00:14:40.231
You have the guts to spit?
That too. on my face?

294
00:14:43.886 --> 00:14:45.486
Madhumitha is mine

295
00:14:45.789 --> 00:14:47.146
'Anyone dares to butt in'

296
00:14:47.526 --> 00:14:48.706
Sure to hit the grave

297
00:14:51.549 --> 00:14:52.629
STOP IT!

298
00:14:52.967 --> 00:14:54.806
You know what's good for this face?

299
00:14:55.378 --> 00:14:56.739
A splash of acid will add color

300
00:14:56.763 --> 00:14:58.402
- I'll do it. di
- Scoot before I count 5

301
00:14:58.487 --> 00:14:59.687
- Clear out
- Come inside

302
00:14:59.687 --> 00:15:01.926
We have tortured this girl
a hell of a lot

303
00:15:01.958 --> 00:15:03.131
You think she will hurt us?

304
00:15:04.005 --> 00:15:05.829
'Using your daughter
to threaten me?'

305
00:15:05.960 --> 00:15:07.794
- Go...go...go. please
- Advise your daughter

306
00:15:07.818 --> 00:15:09.655
- Lower your nightie
- He's being so boorish

307
00:15:09.679 --> 00:15:10.886
Act decent
Untie this

308
00:15:11.627 --> 00:15:13.268
- Don't beg. I'm going
- Please go

309
00:15:13.394 --> 00:15:15.139
That mop-head is
watching from upstairs

310
00:15:15.583 --> 00:15:17.067
Is this a show to watch?
Clear out. da

311
00:15:17.092 --> 00:15:19.177
[Malayalam] No other work in the morning

312
00:15:19.201 --> 00:15:20.281
'Parimi'

313
00:15:21.114 --> 00:15:22.823
Your son-in-law
is the find of the year

314
00:15:22.847 --> 00:15:24.926
'Your family can
weed away to glory'

315
00:15:32.207 --> 00:15:33.606
Bye. 'freedom' aunty

316
00:15:34.749 --> 00:15:38.982
I have no hassle or shame
he came and created an ugly scene

317
00:15:39.606 --> 00:15:41.403
But the fact you picked a fight with him!

318
00:15:42.486 --> 00:15:44.046
Aiyo!

319
00:15:44.966 --> 00:15:46.003
Then what. pa?

320
00:15:46.028 --> 00:15:48.846
Should a girl be stuck in the kitchen
like our amma and watch the fun?

321
00:15:48.871 --> 00:15:49.901
I can't be like that

322
00:15:49.926 --> 00:15:50.966
Coffee

323
00:15:52.756 --> 00:15:55.076
Do you know
how dangerous he is?

324
00:16:10.346 --> 00:16:11.478
My dear husband!

325
00:16:12.588 --> 00:16:13.628
HEY!

326
00:16:16.127 --> 00:16:18.786
I'll ensure my son kills you. da

327
00:16:48.796 --> 00:16:50.836
She etched a feud for
12 years in her son's mind

328
00:16:50.860 --> 00:16:52.322
So Varghese smoked up
and killed him

329
00:16:53.277 --> 00:16:54.460
'Good lord!'

330
00:16:54.485 --> 00:16:55.925
How do you know all this?

331
00:16:57.295 --> 00:16:59.176
A fellow who is following my child

332
00:16:59.736 --> 00:17:01.096
Won't I follow him?

333
00:17:01.531 --> 00:17:03.600
Varghese will carry out his threat
Even that's okay

334
00:17:03.624 --> 00:17:05.562
Whatever it is. doesn't appa
deserve respect. ma?

335
00:17:06.132 --> 00:17:08.452
Will you be so vulgar
to spew swear words at him?

336
00:17:08.966 --> 00:17:10.847
[muttering cuss words]

337
00:17:11.207 --> 00:17:13.526
Even now she's cussing me. pa

338
00:17:13.886 --> 00:17:15.143
- Heard her?
- Shut up!

339
00:17:15.167 --> 00:17:16.196
I'll get even with you

340
00:17:16.221 --> 00:17:17.846
Stupid of me to take your side

341
00:17:17.879 --> 00:17:19.658
- Now she's blaming me
- Both of you. stop it

342
00:17:19.683 --> 00:17:20.856
- Let go
- How to stop them?

343
00:17:20.880 --> 00:17:22.547
- Did I ask you to defend me?
- Let go. di

344
00:17:22.572 --> 00:17:24.628
Oh no! You shouldn't
fight like this. dear

345
00:17:24.735 --> 00:17:27.615
You get a regular knife
You pick the traditional kitchen cutter

346
00:17:28.286 --> 00:17:31.086
Go chop each other outside
in the middle of the road

347
00:17:31.086 --> 00:17:33.287
Only then it will turn into a reel
and become viral

348
00:17:33.287 --> 00:17:34.326
Is that so?

349
00:17:35.896 --> 00:17:37.336
[clenching teeth]

350
00:17:38.126 --> 00:17:39.566
[snorting]

351
00:17:48.619 --> 00:17:49.622
Parimala

352
00:17:49.646 --> 00:17:50.726
Not just 1

353
00:17:50.726 --> 00:17:52.172
Both your daughters are for me

354
00:17:53.170 --> 00:17:54.647
Ahaaaa!

355
00:17:55.293 --> 00:17:57.086
Freedom! Here you are

356
00:17:57.126 --> 00:17:59.246
Old man. she is my mother-in-law

357
00:17:59.286 --> 00:18:01.286
Give whatever she wants
I'll pay you. not to worry

358
00:18:01.766 --> 00:18:03.846
She has given me
pure gold. 2 gems?

359
00:18:04.286 --> 00:18:06.486
Look. don't create a ruckus
wherever we go

360
00:18:06.486 --> 00:18:07.902
Then you'll feel real bad

361
00:18:07.926 --> 00:18:09.326
As if I'll feel bad!

362
00:18:09.366 --> 00:18:12.206
Listen to me. you had better
get both your girls married to me

363
00:18:12.230 --> 00:18:14.846
Otherwise. your freedom will be caged!

364
00:18:14.884 --> 00:18:16.965
See you?
Freedom. Jai ho!

365
00:18:26.807 --> 00:18:28.007
Madhu darling

366
00:18:28.104 --> 00:18:30.223
Why is your father filing
a complaint against me?

367
00:18:30.400 --> 00:18:32.515
You think a mere complaint will scare me?

368
00:18:32.696 --> 00:18:34.313
Glaring daggers at me
Selfie sweety. huh?

369
00:18:35.331 --> 00:18:36.411
Let me click a selfie

370
00:18:36.948 --> 00:18:38.560
Pcccht! Delete that

371
00:18:38.765 --> 00:18:39.982
Give me the phone

372
00:18:40.247 --> 00:18:41.261
Delete that photo

373
00:18:41.286 --> 00:18:42.926
'How dare you. da!'

374
00:18:42.966 --> 00:18:45.157
- Warning you once isn't enough?
- Hey Parasakthi!

375
00:18:45.472 --> 00:18:47.272
I've got a gift for you

376
00:18:47.646 --> 00:18:48.887
Why are you
talking to him. di?

377
00:18:48.926 --> 00:18:50.807
'As if I did!
He is stalking me'

378
00:18:56.646 --> 00:18:58.086
- Dai!
- Hey!

379
00:19:03.366 --> 00:19:04.406
Hey Parasakthi

380
00:19:04.406 --> 00:19:06.366
You pounced on me that day

381
00:19:06.823 --> 00:19:08.098
Egg...eggy

382
00:19:08.122 --> 00:19:09.562
[gloating loudly]

383
00:19:11.366 --> 00:19:12.686
[fireworks popping]

384
00:19:17.046 --> 00:19:19.166
Why have you bought only sweets. pa?

385
00:19:19.205 --> 00:19:20.995
- Let me expla-
- Where are the crackers. pa?

386
00:19:21.020 --> 00:19:22.797
There are 2 ways
of bursting crackers

387
00:19:22.822 --> 00:19:24.221
AIYO! APPA!!

388
00:19:24.246 --> 00:19:25.686
Hear me out. darlings

389
00:19:25.686 --> 00:19:28.862
The first one is buying crackers
spending money from our pocket

390
00:19:28.886 --> 00:19:30.767
Getting scared while lighting it

391
00:19:30.806 --> 00:19:33.686
That powder inside it smearing stains
on your hands and new dress

392
00:19:33.686 --> 00:19:36.086
End up burning holes
in your new dress as well

393
00:19:36.086 --> 00:19:39.749
Neither is it safe nor does it provide
satisfaction even if it is saturation level

394
00:19:41.687 --> 00:19:42.726
The second way?

395
00:19:42.726 --> 00:19:45.806
Make it a picnic on our terrace
Munching on our sweets happily

396
00:19:45.806 --> 00:19:49.967
Watching others bursting crackers
pretending we got people to do so

397
00:19:49.991 --> 00:19:53.071
Screaming loudly in pleasure and
enjoying to the fullest is the other way

398
00:19:53.207 --> 00:19:55.007
You get safety

399
00:19:55.046 --> 00:19:56.327
Satisfaction

400
00:19:56.807 --> 00:19:57.846
Savings too

401
00:19:58.247 --> 00:20:00.518
Short & sweet
Zero budget Deepavali?

402
00:20:00.551 --> 00:20:01.581
Bingo!

403
00:20:03.527 --> 00:20:06.887
Ours is the best fireworks show
in this entire neighborhood. no?

404
00:20:09.511 --> 00:20:10.911
That must have cost Rs 500

405
00:20:10.961 --> 00:20:12.494
Rs 500 vanished into smoky air!

406
00:20:12.806 --> 00:20:14.327
Look. that must be Rs 1500!

407
00:20:14.418 --> 00:20:15.498
Click that

408
00:20:15.767 --> 00:20:16.967
Upload in your status

409
00:20:17.451 --> 00:20:18.531
'Ahaa!'

410
00:20:18.726 --> 00:20:21.407
We must have burst crackers
roughly to the cost of Rs 10.000. no?

411
00:20:21.446 --> 00:20:23.324
No. we have burst for 12500

412
00:20:24.406 --> 00:20:26.461
- Heard that?
- 'How he's tricking those poor girls'

413
00:20:26.486 --> 00:20:29.087
Couldn't you have bought crackers
at least for Rs 2000 - 3000?

414
00:20:29.087 --> 00:20:31.539
If he does that. I will gladly
transfer this house to his name

415
00:20:32.856 --> 00:20:34.526
Buy just to make him lose the bet

416
00:20:34.566 --> 00:20:36.566
Even then your husband
won't spend a single rupee

417
00:20:36.964 --> 00:20:38.284
Sudhandhiram

418
00:20:38.654 --> 00:20:40.174
Actually I went to
buy crackers for us

419
00:20:40.206 --> 00:20:42.259
Adjacent to the fireworks shop
I saw a jewelry store

420
00:20:42.284 --> 00:20:43.860
A girl invited me in
to buy jewelry

421
00:20:43.885 --> 00:20:45.860
Another girl urging
passersby to buy crackers

422
00:20:45.915 --> 00:20:47.276
Jewelry or crackers?

423
00:20:47.846 --> 00:20:49.206
A middle class family like us

424
00:20:49.247 --> 00:20:50.927
We scrimp and save somehow

425
00:20:51.047 --> 00:20:54.047
And tend to buy gold
to get our gems married

426
00:20:54.779 --> 00:20:55.806
That is why

427
00:20:56.766 --> 00:20:58.046
I opted for gold

428
00:20:59.383 --> 00:21:00.486
Sudhandhiram

429
00:21:00.527 --> 00:21:02.246
Fighting with life to stay afloat

430
00:21:02.366 --> 00:21:04.286
Swimming against the tide to survive

431
00:21:04.367 --> 00:21:06.806
Our middle class existence slips away. no?

432
00:21:08.766 --> 00:21:10.124
[loud explosion]

433
00:21:10.646 --> 00:21:11.766
Yov! Parimala

434
00:21:12.928 --> 00:21:15.579
Tomorrow morning if you don't wish
'Happy Deepavali. son-in-law'

435
00:21:15.674 --> 00:21:18.086
And willingly tell me
'you are the groom'

436
00:21:18.126 --> 00:21:19.607
- He will tell
- You will agree

437
00:21:19.806 --> 00:21:20.807
See you. uncs

438
00:21:20.846 --> 00:21:23.006
Happpy Deepavaliii

439
00:21:23.126 --> 00:21:24.366
- Here. dude
- Give

440
00:21:24.407 --> 00:21:25.607
Deepavali crackers

441
00:21:25.646 --> 00:21:26.766
Hey! Enjoy

442
00:21:26.807 --> 00:21:30.386
'Parimala. this is your last night
Think well before you decide'

443
00:21:32.886 --> 00:21:34.166
We will

444
00:21:34.526 --> 00:21:35.766
We will vacate tomorrow

445
00:21:36.647 --> 00:21:39.146
I will withhold 3 months rent
And give balance deposit. okay?

446
00:21:41.807 --> 00:21:43.607
You are a real son of a-

447
00:21:54.592 --> 00:21:56.154
'He has posted on Insta'

448
00:22:02.046 --> 00:22:03.126
Aiyaiyo!

449
00:22:04.406 --> 00:22:05.406
Appa

450
00:22:07.327 --> 00:22:08.407
One day

451
00:22:09.047 --> 00:22:10.166
One day...?

452
00:22:11.846 --> 00:22:13.127
He pulled me and hugged me

453
00:22:19.446 --> 00:22:20.526
Yuck!

454
00:22:31.487 --> 00:22:33.686
We can live in peace
only if he 'rests in peace'

455
00:22:35.956 --> 00:22:37.083
Shall we kill him?

456
00:22:39.006 --> 00:22:40.086
Agreed. pa

457
00:22:41.782 --> 00:22:43.542
I am so furious right now

458
00:22:43.566 --> 00:22:45.167
I feel like murdering him

459
00:22:46.446 --> 00:22:47.486
But

460
00:22:47.966 --> 00:22:49.646
Won't it be a crime
and become a case?

461
00:22:52.660 --> 00:22:54.847
To kill is a crime. it will
naturally be a murder case

462
00:22:58.148 --> 00:23:00.293
How do we murder
without anyone's knowledge?

463
00:23:00.628 --> 00:23:02.268
No need such drastic measures. pa

464
00:23:02.500 --> 00:23:04.021
We will get caught. pa

465
00:23:04.046 --> 00:23:06.926
Yes. dear. even I feel
we will get caught

466
00:23:11.592 --> 00:23:13.152
[crows cawing]

467
00:23:16.028 --> 00:23:17.141
[dog barking]

468
00:23:23.571 --> 00:23:25.771
[crackers exploding]

469
00:23:25.943 --> 00:23:28.384
Hey! Doesn't that chap resemble
your younger brother Raghavan?

470
00:23:28.615 --> 00:23:31.144
Your brother is also with him
Keep quiet and walk with us

471
00:23:31.184 --> 00:23:33.277
[siren wailing]

472
00:23:35.350 --> 00:23:36.423
'Move...move'

473
00:23:36.463 --> 00:23:37.943
Move this side
Don't block the way

474
00:23:50.030 --> 00:23:52.630
I wanted to have a proper oil bath
on Deepavali day

475
00:23:52.733 --> 00:23:54.640
You are ruining the festivity
by calling me here

476
00:23:54.665 --> 00:23:55.738
Move out of the way

477
00:23:56.144 --> 00:23:57.605
Move...move

478
00:23:58.223 --> 00:23:59.304
'Hey! Open'

479
00:24:05.031 --> 00:24:06.831
He has been strangled
with a wire. sir

480
00:24:07.823 --> 00:24:09.103
He is a hot-headed fellow

481
00:24:09.127 --> 00:24:11.943
He would've acted with temerity
Someone must have killed him

482
00:24:11.943 --> 00:24:13.349
Aiyo! My son

483
00:24:13.443 --> 00:24:14.763
Varghese!

484
00:24:15.638 --> 00:24:16.958
'Varghese'

485
00:24:18.582 --> 00:24:19.654
'Varghese'

486
00:24:20.535 --> 00:24:21.833
Your mother is here. da

487
00:24:21.991 --> 00:24:23.377
Don't touch the body
Come this side

488
00:24:23.401 --> 00:24:24.682
Move...clear the scene

489
00:24:24.706 --> 00:24:25.977
Go...clear out

490
00:24:26.001 --> 00:24:27.718
Ambulance. drive here

491
00:24:29.117 --> 00:24:30.215
[siren wailing]

492
00:24:30.567 --> 00:24:31.662
What do you mean?

493
00:24:31.760 --> 00:24:33.191
Yes. pa
He's dead

494
00:24:33.675 --> 00:24:35.651
The police are planning
to investigate. it seems

495
00:24:49.280 --> 00:24:51.001
Just to bash up. one amount

496
00:24:51.086 --> 00:24:53.485
To separate the limbs
Hands and legs. another amount

497
00:24:53.531 --> 00:24:55.548
Finish off once and for all
That's a bigger amount

498
00:24:55.548 --> 00:24:57.588
Why are you overthinking?
We can do a clean job

499
00:24:57.680 --> 00:24:58.706
Shall we do the needful?

500
00:24:58.730 --> 00:24:59.786
Er...I don't

501
00:25:01.068 --> 00:25:02.422
[smug chuckle]

502
00:25:05.868 --> 00:25:07.188
Parimi

503
00:25:07.647 --> 00:25:08.926
Happy Deepavali

504
00:25:12.917 --> 00:25:14.611
Happy Diwali

505
00:25:20.502 --> 00:25:22.932
[crackers exploding]

506
00:25:33.818 --> 00:25:36.180
'Parimala & Co'

507
00:25:37.953 --> 00:25:39.114
Why did you do this?

508
00:25:39.138 --> 00:25:41.525
I used to burst crackers only
this way even when I was a kid

509
00:25:41.550 --> 00:25:43.868
Only yesterday you asked us
how we can get rid of him

510
00:25:43.868 --> 00:25:45.468
How did you kill him so soon?

511
00:25:45.468 --> 00:25:48.547
Hey! Didn't we all decide
unanimously yesterday?

512
00:25:48.547 --> 00:25:50.867
We will get caught if we kill
So we won't resort to murder

513
00:25:50.892 --> 00:25:51.892
Then what?

514
00:25:51.917 --> 00:25:54.577
I'm asking you why you killed him
when all of us decided not to

515
00:25:54.602 --> 00:25:55.722
Why...kill-

516
00:25:55.747 --> 00:25:57.148
[muttering under his breath]

517
00:25:57.172 --> 00:25:58.459
'Freedom aunty'

518
00:26:02.434 --> 00:26:03.988
'Then you'll feel real bad'

519
00:26:04.028 --> 00:26:07.025
I'm so scared we'll be stuck
in some mess because of him. da

520
00:26:07.311 --> 00:26:09.151
I think it is better
to vacate this house

521
00:26:09.588 --> 00:26:12.593
Why shift your house. akka?
We'll shift him to hell instead

522
00:26:12.618 --> 00:26:14.738
Hey! Don't rush in
and do something rash

523
00:26:15.151 --> 00:26:17.124
As if we don't have a PhD in murder. huh!

524
00:26:17.148 --> 00:26:18.627
Ohhh!

525
00:26:18.627 --> 00:26:21.067
You used your younger brother
and did everything

526
00:26:21.067 --> 00:26:23.467
Then turning the track my way. huh?

527
00:26:24.167 --> 00:26:25.180
Yes

528
00:26:25.205 --> 00:26:26.446
Dial 100

529
00:26:26.609 --> 00:26:29.107
Call the police. hand me over
claiming I am the murderer

530
00:26:29.707 --> 00:26:30.941
Dad

531
00:26:31.067 --> 00:26:32.904
- She is the culprit. pa
- Me...?!

532
00:26:38.850 --> 00:26:41.453
Send me his photo. address
and all the details you have

533
00:26:41.477 --> 00:26:42.518
Okay. uncle

534
00:26:42.921 --> 00:26:45.041
My actions will give you a solid headache

535
00:26:45.074 --> 00:26:46.268
Are you okay with that?

536
00:26:46.589 --> 00:26:47.641
That is life

537
00:26:47.787 --> 00:26:48.988
Then will you help me?

538
00:26:49.867 --> 00:26:51.068
But it is very risky

539
00:26:52.387 --> 00:26:53.394
Why?

540
00:26:53.587 --> 00:26:54.948
You want me to kill someone?

541
00:26:55.788 --> 00:26:57.228
Shall we?

542
00:26:59.787 --> 00:27:01.227
I'll slap you
Don't spin some yarn

543
00:27:01.227 --> 00:27:02.315
Hey! Wait...wait

544
00:27:02.339 --> 00:27:04.827
Didn't you crack your knuckles
and threaten to kill him?

545
00:27:04.827 --> 00:27:06.364
'I will kill you for sure'

546
00:27:06.388 --> 00:27:09.132
'All I have to do is nod my head
4-5 goons will close your chapter'

547
00:27:09.156 --> 00:27:10.268
'Want to bet?'

548
00:27:10.268 --> 00:27:11.587
Who are those 4 goons?

549
00:27:11.667 --> 00:27:14.311
Appa. words spilled out
of my mouth in a flow that day

550
00:27:14.667 --> 00:27:16.028
I am just a pitiful soul

551
00:27:16.410 --> 00:27:18.410
I put up a brave front

552
00:27:18.948 --> 00:27:20.947
Even she said. 'you will die in my hands'

553
00:27:24.015 --> 00:27:25.276
'You will die in my hands'

554
00:27:26.508 --> 00:27:29.686
An impending death before her wedding
is assured as per this girl's horoscope

555
00:27:29.831 --> 00:27:31.031
Oh God!

556
00:27:31.348 --> 00:27:34.027
Her stars are aligned
making her a murderess

557
00:27:35.594 --> 00:27:36.788
AMMA!

558
00:27:36.812 --> 00:27:39.572
- What do we-
- "Up the stairs...upstairs"

559
00:27:40.028 --> 00:27:42.107
Let's go inside
and discuss calmly

560
00:27:43.082 --> 00:27:44.482
Happy Diwali

561
00:27:44.506 --> 00:27:45.510
Happy Deepavali

562
00:27:49.471 --> 00:27:51.871
Who killed that Varghese. huh?

563
00:27:52.014 --> 00:27:53.515
Sir. that's personal revenge

564
00:27:53.575 --> 00:27:54.602
How do you say so?

565
00:27:54.627 --> 00:27:56.946
If this were business
he'll be a corpse dumped on the road

566
00:27:56.971 --> 00:27:59.196
Chopped his right hand. sir
With a deep seated vengeance

567
00:27:59.221 --> 00:28:00.731
I'm sure this is family revenge. sir

568
00:28:00.755 --> 00:28:03.239
- Why do you say that?
- He crossed a line somewhere

569
00:28:03.883 --> 00:28:06.282
What did he touch
which he shouldn't have?

570
00:28:06.336 --> 00:28:07.856
I want to meet the Inspector. sir

571
00:28:11.907 --> 00:28:13.867
- Who is the Inspector?
- Of course you. sir

572
00:28:14.947 --> 00:28:17.188
They say I am the Inspector of this station

573
00:28:17.227 --> 00:28:18.307
If you want. tell me

574
00:28:18.331 --> 00:28:20.300
Or meet the Inspector
in the next police station

575
00:28:21.588 --> 00:28:22.627
Sorry. sir

576
00:28:22.668 --> 00:28:23.761
I need to file a complaint

577
00:28:23.786 --> 00:28:24.826
What complaint?

578
00:28:25.428 --> 00:28:27.108
Sir. my bike is missing

579
00:28:27.787 --> 00:28:30.027
'I parked my bike in
the free parking section'

580
00:28:30.067 --> 00:28:31.652
'When I came back
it was missing'

581
00:28:32.067 --> 00:28:34.387
You couldn't afford Rs 100
as parking fee

582
00:28:35.067 --> 00:28:36.468
Penny wise and pound foolish!

583
00:28:36.642 --> 00:28:38.522
- Eat this 'bhajji'
- No. thanks. sir

584
00:28:38.988 --> 00:28:40.228
Take it

585
00:28:40.707 --> 00:28:42.268
I won't accept
your complaint otherwise

586
00:28:46.785 --> 00:28:47.905
Eat. da

587
00:28:50.230 --> 00:28:51.430
Tasty?

588
00:28:52.807 --> 00:28:53.807
Yes. sir

589
00:28:56.268 --> 00:28:57.307
Tell me

590
00:28:57.427 --> 00:28:58.428
This morning

591
00:28:59.034 --> 00:29:00.674
A chap called Varghese was found dead

592
00:29:01.229 --> 00:29:02.590
Do you know him?

593
00:29:04.267 --> 00:29:05.310
No. sir

594
00:29:06.787 --> 00:29:09.787
'Notorious rowdy Varghese from
Foreshore Estate in Chennai'

595
00:29:09.828 --> 00:29:11.215
Finished him off. huh?

596
00:29:11.667 --> 00:29:13.027
He deserved to die

597
00:29:13.402 --> 00:29:14.922
Why are you so negative?

598
00:29:15.387 --> 00:29:16.587
No. my dear

599
00:29:16.828 --> 00:29:18.868
He is responsible for
my wife Karmegam's demise

600
00:29:19.828 --> 00:29:23.375
He was on drugs and ran over my wife
who was walking by the side of the road

601
00:29:23.399 --> 00:29:24.897
The police claimed
it was an accident

602
00:29:24.921 --> 00:29:26.723
Or they threatened to
turn the case against me

603
00:29:26.748 --> 00:29:27.932
How can I fight him?

604
00:29:29.748 --> 00:29:30.828
That's why

605
00:29:31.604 --> 00:29:32.787
Someone killed him

606
00:29:38.392 --> 00:29:41.593
Emperuman. you are nabbing
the murderer of Varghese in 24 hours

607
00:29:41.937 --> 00:29:43.817
Yes. sir. I am still
following that case

608
00:29:44.610 --> 00:29:48.338
Aiyo! He has left me
to suffer in pain like this

609
00:29:49.107 --> 00:29:52.188
What will I do without him hereafter?

610
00:29:53.310 --> 00:29:55.068
'Oh God!'

611
00:29:56.594 --> 00:29:59.908
I undertake catering
I cook and deliver food

612
00:30:01.428 --> 00:30:05.668
He will follow me everywhere
calling out 'amma' every second minute

613
00:30:06.359 --> 00:30:10.153
He was more of a friend
than a son to me. sir

614
00:30:10.559 --> 00:30:14.038
He was in love with a girl
for a few years. sir

615
00:30:14.630 --> 00:30:18.228
He was so frank. didn't hide
even that from me. sir

616
00:30:18.252 --> 00:30:19.428
Who is that girl. madam?

617
00:30:29.365 --> 00:30:30.420
Madhu?

618
00:30:31.196 --> 00:30:32.396
'Sudhandhiram'

619
00:30:33.046 --> 00:30:34.887
Why does she look
like she has seen a ghost?

620
00:30:34.987 --> 00:30:36.147
'Hey!'

621
00:30:37.037 --> 00:30:38.237
What is bothering you?

622
00:30:38.740 --> 00:30:39.819
Nothing

623
00:30:40.237 --> 00:30:41.437
I did

624
00:30:42.565 --> 00:30:43.924
I did not

625
00:30:44.383 --> 00:30:46.143
I did not kill him
I swear. pa

626
00:30:47.732 --> 00:30:49.652
I didn't love him either. pa

627
00:30:50.142 --> 00:30:52.828
Hey! You haven't even spoken to him

628
00:30:53.173 --> 00:30:54.708
Then why are you scared?

629
00:30:55.512 --> 00:30:57.187
No. I did not talk to him

630
00:30:58.037 --> 00:30:59.194
But-

631
00:31:01.547 --> 00:31:03.066
What is that 'but'?

632
00:31:04.079 --> 00:31:06.040
Nothing. ma
Forget about it

633
00:31:08.169 --> 00:31:09.369
Pa...?

634
00:31:09.571 --> 00:31:10.972
She is hiding something. pa

635
00:31:11.315 --> 00:31:13.311
Before the police knock
at our door for an inquiry

636
00:31:13.336 --> 00:31:15.577
You start interrogating them
in your police style. dear

637
00:31:18.041 --> 00:31:20.400
Have you spoken to him?

638
00:31:20.508 --> 00:31:22.003
Or is the answer 'no'?

639
00:31:22.027 --> 00:31:24.427
I haven't looked at his face
and uttered a single word. pa

640
00:31:26.770 --> 00:31:28.411
Then why are you scared?

641
00:31:30.256 --> 00:31:32.017
I've spoken over the phone. pa

642
00:31:32.437 --> 00:31:34.437
Is that so?
For what?

643
00:31:37.515 --> 00:31:40.195
I wondered why this chap
is piling so much respect on me

644
00:31:40.218 --> 00:31:42.939
'I got his number and
gave him a courtesy call. pa'

645
00:31:43.145 --> 00:31:45.019
Varghese. I'm Madhumitha speaking

646
00:31:45.227 --> 00:31:46.907
No...no. I yelled at him. pa

647
00:31:47.268 --> 00:31:48.305
Hey!

648
00:31:48.330 --> 00:31:50.329
[yelling at supersonic speed]

649
00:31:51.157 --> 00:31:52.351
Madhu darling

650
00:31:53.603 --> 00:31:56.426
Your string of cuss words
is awwwwesome!

651
00:31:56.525 --> 00:31:58.166
Did you call to yell at him?

652
00:31:58.445 --> 00:32:00.326
Or did you yell at him
as an excuse to call him?

653
00:32:00.588 --> 00:32:02.416
Did you talk to him
because you disliked him?

654
00:32:02.440 --> 00:32:04.279
Or did you talk to him
to entice him?

655
00:32:04.548 --> 00:32:06.228
[gritting teeth]

656
00:32:07.981 --> 00:32:09.824
[mobile vibrating]

657
00:32:11.551 --> 00:32:12.895
Pcccht!

658
00:32:13.885 --> 00:32:15.497
He told his mother

659
00:32:16.387 --> 00:32:17.456
Mother...mother

660
00:32:17.481 --> 00:32:19.022
- I'm in love with this girl
- Really?

661
00:32:19.547 --> 00:32:20.604
'His mother'

662
00:32:20.628 --> 00:32:22.147
Proudly announced
to all her relatives

663
00:32:22.399 --> 00:32:24.588
'This girl is my daughter-in-law to-be'

664
00:32:24.627 --> 00:32:26.868
She pointed a finger
to my face and said so. pa

665
00:32:28.158 --> 00:32:29.918
I was hopping mad

666
00:32:30.415 --> 00:32:33.199
Then I called him once more
and spoke to him. pa

667
00:32:34.352 --> 00:32:36.100
Call on top of call?

668
00:32:36.324 --> 00:32:38.264
How else will she refer
to her 'daughter-in-law'?

669
00:32:38.289 --> 00:32:40.250
You found out my # and called me

670
00:32:40.382 --> 00:32:42.910
If you wanted to yell at me
you could have spat on my face

671
00:32:42.935 --> 00:32:44.152
'What do you call this then?'

672
00:32:44.177 --> 00:32:45.257
Love. right?

673
00:32:45.422 --> 00:32:46.707
Get lost. you lunatic

674
00:32:46.747 --> 00:32:47.908
The way you scold me

675
00:32:48.108 --> 00:32:49.307
Awe-some

676
00:32:49.307 --> 00:32:51.147
He spoke like a lunatic

677
00:32:51.398 --> 00:32:53.118
[mobile vibrating]

678
00:32:55.308 --> 00:32:56.945
I'm in an inquiry. you stupid girl

679
00:32:56.969 --> 00:32:58.169
I'll call back
Hang up now

680
00:33:07.279 --> 00:33:08.679
The thing is

681
00:33:09.047 --> 00:33:10.134
That moment

682
00:33:10.324 --> 00:33:11.920
I punched his face. pa

683
00:33:12.044 --> 00:33:13.645
Achacho!

684
00:33:14.347 --> 00:33:16.587
- I thought I gave birth to only 1 rowdy!
- Pcccht!

685
00:33:17.727 --> 00:33:19.125
Are you a rowdy too?

686
00:33:20.364 --> 00:33:23.431
How dare you hit my son. huh?

687
00:33:23.867 --> 00:33:27.067
If he is still a wild fellow
after your marriage. then hit him

688
00:33:27.091 --> 00:33:28.827
Even I hit my husband like that

689
00:33:29.107 --> 00:33:31.228
- What do you say. Fafa?
- Yes. akka

690
00:33:32.427 --> 00:33:35.827
His mother finds it funny
and laughs shamelessly

691
00:33:36.062 --> 00:33:37.495
What an odd family. ma

692
00:33:38.233 --> 00:33:41.192
One swift blow from me and
his nose went red and swollen

693
00:33:41.673 --> 00:33:44.464
The moment I noticed that
I couldn't control my laughter

694
00:33:45.770 --> 00:33:47.894
I laughed at his puffed up nose. pa

695
00:33:48.508 --> 00:33:51.761
'But she thought I was
smiling at her son'

696
00:33:51.837 --> 00:33:55.788
She is hiding tonnes of love
within her heart. my son

697
00:33:56.621 --> 00:33:57.981
So she said loudly

698
00:33:59.021 --> 00:34:00.069
Oh gawd!

699
00:34:00.280 --> 00:34:03.080
He looked like Panda
with that swollen nose

700
00:34:03.802 --> 00:34:05.122
Who is Pandan?

701
00:34:05.692 --> 00:34:08.013
Like the cartoon figure Panda

702
00:34:08.988 --> 00:34:11.082
I was so amused
I started laughing

703
00:34:13.921 --> 00:34:16.042
The lady standing next to them said

704
00:34:16.077 --> 00:34:18.957
'She is just blooming
Naturally she'll feel shy'

705
00:34:21.243 --> 00:34:25.204
You sound like Vadivelu joking
about the pee-street in the film 'Giri'

706
00:34:25.468 --> 00:34:26.628
Huhum

707
00:34:27.139 --> 00:34:29.624
With his swollen nose he piped in

708
00:34:30.093 --> 00:34:31.708
Awe....some!

709
00:34:31.868 --> 00:34:33.457
He complimented shamelessly

710
00:34:34.188 --> 00:34:37.748
My dear. this reminds me of
the bakery comedy in the film 'Giri'

711
00:34:38.749 --> 00:34:40.428
Bakery?
What is that?

712
00:34:40.719 --> 00:34:43.080
That dialog. dear
'I will keep your sister'

713
00:34:43.828 --> 00:34:46.404
'You can keep the bakery'
Vadivelu will joke in that film

714
00:34:46.427 --> 00:34:47.622
[cackling laughter]

715
00:34:47.653 --> 00:34:48.942
[gnashing teeth]

716
00:34:49.028 --> 00:34:50.061
Why that look?

717
00:34:50.085 --> 00:34:52.102
Is this a joke to share
in front of our girls?

718
00:34:52.428 --> 00:34:54.948
Is pee-street comedy alone a moral story?

719
00:34:55.107 --> 00:34:56.269
[dog barking]

720
00:34:59.143 --> 00:35:02.062
You had such a detailed
screenplay in your hand

721
00:35:02.193 --> 00:35:03.513
In one line

722
00:35:03.708 --> 00:35:07.867
'Appa. he is stalking me'
You painted it short and simple

723
00:35:08.322 --> 00:35:09.428
Double wow!

724
00:35:09.901 --> 00:35:12.620
Pa. we will be arrested for sure

725
00:35:20.135 --> 00:35:22.423
[humming]

726
00:35:32.976 --> 00:35:35.099
[humming]

727
00:35:38.396 --> 00:35:39.518
Hmmm...tell me

728
00:35:39.748 --> 00:35:41.917
'We are a gang of 7
Thick friends from childhood. sir'

729
00:35:41.943 --> 00:35:43.008
Yes. sir

730
00:35:43.107 --> 00:35:44.269
Varghese is a good chap. sir

731
00:35:44.308 --> 00:35:45.392
Yes. sir

732
00:35:45.416 --> 00:35:47.418
If all of you certify
will Varghese become a saint?

733
00:35:47.444 --> 00:35:48.578
Yes. sir

734
00:35:52.093 --> 00:35:53.935
You are all into lip pillow
nicotine pouch. no?

735
00:35:53.959 --> 00:35:55.040
No. sir

736
00:35:55.263 --> 00:35:57.224
Whether you are stoned.
baked or blazed

737
00:35:57.550 --> 00:35:58.687
I need a hit

738
00:35:58.843 --> 00:36:00.042
Who has it?

739
00:36:00.141 --> 00:36:03.568
"Don't wane or fade so soon
Stay. my silver-white moon"

740
00:36:03.693 --> 00:36:04.853
- Don't have?
- Sir

741
00:36:05.095 --> 00:36:06.455
Not lip pillow. sir

742
00:36:06.821 --> 00:36:08.341
But we have 'stamp' with us

743
00:36:10.000 --> 00:36:11.280
Stamp?

744
00:36:11.468 --> 00:36:12.548
LSD

745
00:36:13.309 --> 00:36:14.667
Lip pillow is local. sir

746
00:36:14.947 --> 00:36:16.708
Stamp is mind blowing

747
00:36:17.339 --> 00:36:18.378
Show me

748
00:36:18.403 --> 00:36:22.101
"Don't look at me; please refrain
My fragile heart can't bear the pain"

749
00:36:22.352 --> 00:36:23.469
Give

750
00:36:24.360 --> 00:36:25.680
I'll pop one too

751
00:36:31.243 --> 00:36:32.604
Go over there

752
00:36:32.718 --> 00:36:33.917
You go there

753
00:36:34.238 --> 00:36:35.238
GET LOST. DA!

754
00:36:35.708 --> 00:36:36.947
You come here. da

755
00:36:37.568 --> 00:36:38.807
You come here

756
00:36:40.433 --> 00:36:41.581
Tell me now

757
00:36:41.604 --> 00:36:43.324
- Who killed Varghese?
- Don't know. sir

758
00:36:43.446 --> 00:36:44.726
Cough up the truth. da

759
00:36:45.687 --> 00:36:47.328
Jomi. sir

760
00:36:47.750 --> 00:36:49.470
- Tell me. sir
- George

761
00:36:49.968 --> 00:36:51.110
Tell me. bro

762
00:36:51.459 --> 00:36:52.604
Nicholas

763
00:36:52.627 --> 00:36:54.468
- Tell me. baby
- Cage

764
00:36:55.100 --> 00:36:56.183
Boys. come here

765
00:36:57.309 --> 00:36:58.310
Who is Jomi?

766
00:36:58.791 --> 00:37:00.867
Who is George?
Who is Nicholas?

767
00:37:00.907 --> 00:37:02.029
One man for all names. sir

768
00:37:02.068 --> 00:37:04.148
Yes. sir. Jomi George Nicholas Cage

769
00:37:06.109 --> 00:37:07.109
Repeat

770
00:37:07.147 --> 00:37:09.590
Jomi George Nicholas Cage is a brand

771
00:37:10.059 --> 00:37:12.139
If you try to destroy that brand

772
00:37:12.589 --> 00:37:15.589
I'll go bang-bang-bang
Shoot all of you and move on

773
00:37:15.791 --> 00:37:17.231
I am a brand label. da

774
00:37:17.628 --> 00:37:18.908
Don't be scared

775
00:37:19.010 --> 00:37:20.032
Whatever

776
00:37:20.058 --> 00:37:21.298
Whatever happened has happened

777
00:37:22.387 --> 00:37:23.708
The police will knock at our door

778
00:37:24.234 --> 00:37:26.914
They will press and probe
Grilling us with question after question

779
00:37:28.078 --> 00:37:30.279
We should be in sync and lie

780
00:37:31.911 --> 00:37:33.666
- Okay. pa
- Kamal Haasan's 'Papanasam'

781
00:37:33.689 --> 00:37:35.345
Haven't you watched that film?

782
00:37:36.188 --> 00:37:37.789
In Hindi the hero is Ajay Devgan

783
00:37:37.829 --> 00:37:40.348
In the original Malayalam version
Mohan Lal is the hero

784
00:37:40.387 --> 00:37:41.989
You left out hero Venkatesh in Telugu

785
00:37:42.184 --> 00:37:43.205
[gnashing teeth]

786
00:37:43.229 --> 00:37:45.669
- Why?
- Is that important now?

787
00:37:46.597 --> 00:37:47.781
'If you tell the truth'

788
00:37:48.147 --> 00:37:50.833
I will save you
like Kamal Haasan did

789
00:37:51.791 --> 00:37:54.194
How will you save us
when you were the murderer?

790
00:37:54.218 --> 00:37:55.897
You will be behind bars. no?

791
00:37:56.059 --> 00:37:57.937
Only we will be able to save you

792
00:37:58.531 --> 00:37:59.543
I did-

793
00:38:00.272 --> 00:38:01.780
I did not-

794
00:38:02.121 --> 00:38:03.760
I did not kill him. di

795
00:38:04.539 --> 00:38:05.660
I am not the murderer

796
00:38:05.819 --> 00:38:06.939
Okay if you say so

797
00:38:07.682 --> 00:38:08.843
I did not kill him

798
00:38:11.668 --> 00:38:14.309
Hey! Touch your conscience and speak up

799
00:38:16.008 --> 00:38:17.369
You killed him. right?

800
00:38:17.907 --> 00:38:20.188
Appa. I swear I did not kill him

801
00:38:21.644 --> 00:38:24.066
I promise on both of you.
it wasn't me. pa

802
00:38:24.391 --> 00:38:25.517
[dog barking]

803
00:38:29.147 --> 00:38:30.147
Okay

804
00:38:30.147 --> 00:38:32.468
Both of you promise
by touching your mother's head

805
00:38:32.509 --> 00:38:33.964
Why am I the lamb for the slaughter?

806
00:38:33.988 --> 00:38:35.208
I swear I did not lie

807
00:38:35.232 --> 00:38:36.684
If you lie. amma's head will explode

808
00:38:36.708 --> 00:38:37.986
HUH?

809
00:38:38.010 --> 00:38:39.371
Now both of you promise

810
00:38:41.405 --> 00:38:43.725
We are your parents
Why should we promise. huh?

811
00:38:43.750 --> 00:38:44.790
True that!

812
00:38:44.824 --> 00:38:46.232
[mobile ringing]

813
00:38:46.405 --> 00:38:48.523
May be he is the kill-

814
00:38:49.685 --> 00:38:50.816
'Who is calling?'

815
00:38:50.936 --> 00:38:52.781
- Hello?
- 'Did my husband come there. anna?'

816
00:38:52.943 --> 00:38:54.463
- Raghavan?
- 'Yes'

817
00:38:54.788 --> 00:38:56.677
He said he is going to Chennai
and left Palakkad

818
00:38:56.703 --> 00:38:57.888
'He hasn't returned yet'

819
00:38:57.912 --> 00:38:59.228
- Here?
- 'Yes'

820
00:38:59.359 --> 00:39:01.189
Ahh...1 minute

821
00:39:01.600 --> 00:39:03.280
Hey! Did Raghavan come here?

822
00:39:04.724 --> 00:39:05.974
Promise. he didn't come?

823
00:39:06.313 --> 00:39:07.360
Trust me

824
00:39:08.193 --> 00:39:09.946
- No
- Okay. anna

825
00:39:12.959 --> 00:39:15.343
'Hey! Doesn't that chap resemble
your brother Raghavan?'

826
00:39:15.366 --> 00:39:17.908
'Your brother is also with him
Keep quiet and walk with us'

827
00:39:18.280 --> 00:39:19.560
'Is my brother tagging along?'

828
00:39:23.292 --> 00:39:24.813
Is he suspicious now?

829
00:39:26.628 --> 00:39:27.675
Cheers!

830
00:39:41.345 --> 00:39:42.506
Why is he hmmming?

831
00:39:42.538 --> 00:39:43.577
Hmmmm

832
00:39:44.095 --> 00:39:45.256
'I will figure it out'

833
00:39:45.281 --> 00:39:46.964
[mobile vibrating]

834
00:40:03.190 --> 00:40:04.391
'Madhu darling'

835
00:40:05.388 --> 00:40:06.391
Who are you?

836
00:40:06.414 --> 00:40:08.123
'A chap called Varghese is dead'

837
00:40:08.314 --> 00:40:10.239
The last call he received
was from your number

838
00:40:10.292 --> 00:40:11.322
Who are you?

839
00:40:11.347 --> 00:40:12.988
I...I called by mistake

840
00:40:13.508 --> 00:40:15.168
Is that so?
Whom are you kidding?

841
00:40:15.221 --> 00:40:17.061
You told him to meet you
in Duming Lane

842
00:40:17.093 --> 00:40:19.717
'You told him you'll give him a gift
Your voice has been recorded'

843
00:40:19.741 --> 00:40:20.863
Hello?

844
00:40:25.188 --> 00:40:26.749
- She cut my call
- Cut your call?

845
00:40:44.677 --> 00:40:45.957
[dog barking]

846
00:40:47.551 --> 00:40:48.671
Sssshhhh!

847
00:40:50.576 --> 00:40:51.857
All of you. come here

848
00:40:53.582 --> 00:40:55.106
Madhu. appa is calling us

849
00:40:55.131 --> 00:40:56.134
I...I'm...coming

850
00:41:00.892 --> 00:41:02.052
Come soon

851
00:41:08.478 --> 00:41:09.758
My guess is

852
00:41:10.122 --> 00:41:11.425
The police are on their way here

853
00:41:11.449 --> 00:41:13.290
[police siren wailing]

854
00:41:13.427 --> 00:41:17.506
We will make it clear we have
absolutely nothing to do with this murder

855
00:41:17.840 --> 00:41:21.080
But the truth of the matter is
one of us must have killed him

856
00:41:21.475 --> 00:41:22.675
Correct?

857
00:41:28.454 --> 00:41:30.453
Let that secret stay with us

858
00:41:30.685 --> 00:41:31.805
Okay?

859
00:41:32.667 --> 00:41:34.627
Remember the film 'Papanasam'?

860
00:41:35.449 --> 00:41:37.250
I have forgotten most of it

861
00:41:37.708 --> 00:41:39.788
Can we watch it together?

862
00:41:42.107 --> 00:41:43.988
You can watch it in YouTube

863
00:41:44.639 --> 00:41:45.719
Search

864
00:41:47.604 --> 00:41:49.564
Not uploaded as a full movie

865
00:41:49.715 --> 00:41:50.715
Only as scenes

866
00:41:50.739 --> 00:41:53.498
It will be better to watch it
in a flow. right?

867
00:41:54.002 --> 00:41:55.322
Check which OTT platform?

868
00:41:56.291 --> 00:41:57.331
Sun NXT. pa

869
00:41:57.724 --> 00:41:58.743
How much?

870
00:41:58.768 --> 00:42:00.048
Rs 899

871
00:42:00.920 --> 00:42:02.680
Eight hundred and ninety nine?!

872
00:42:03.138 --> 00:42:05.177
Only Rs 299 if we choose
the 3 month plan. pa

873
00:42:06.416 --> 00:42:09.776
Nothing wrong in spending
Rs 300 for a murder case. no?

874
00:42:11.708 --> 00:42:13.070
Subscribed?

875
00:42:13.416 --> 00:42:15.615
Starring Kamal Haasan
'Papanasam'

876
00:42:16.867 --> 00:42:18.468
[inhaling camphor]

877
00:42:30.189 --> 00:42:31.479
Appa. police

878
00:42:31.502 --> 00:42:32.563
How can it be?

879
00:42:32.760 --> 00:42:34.601
Tamil Nadu Police
faster than lightning?

880
00:42:34.722 --> 00:42:36.362
They have tracked us so soon

881
00:42:36.385 --> 00:42:37.586
Aiyo! Evidence

882
00:42:37.611 --> 00:42:38.770
Switch off the TV

883
00:42:42.156 --> 00:42:45.019
All I wanted was to try a 'lip-pillow'
They gave me some rotten stuff

884
00:42:45.042 --> 00:42:47.683
Got me buzzed flat
to lie low on a big pillow

885
00:42:48.455 --> 00:42:50.002
My head is spinning like a giant wheel

886
00:42:50.034 --> 00:42:51.274
Drive me home

887
00:42:51.892 --> 00:42:53.047
'Have they come?'

888
00:42:53.464 --> 00:42:54.468
They have left. pa

889
00:42:55.229 --> 00:42:56.427
Ohhh!

890
00:42:57.299 --> 00:42:58.788
They are in Observation Mode

891
00:43:10.752 --> 00:43:12.364
Hang it properly
Fix the clip firmly

892
00:43:12.388 --> 00:43:14.062
Aiyaiyo! They are here

893
00:43:14.364 --> 00:43:15.913
[siren wailing]

894
00:43:16.022 --> 00:43:17.741
Ma. that was an ambulance

895
00:43:19.253 --> 00:43:23.726
'On India's stance regarding drug use
in South Asian countries'

896
00:43:23.749 --> 00:43:26.109
'United Nations has expressed its concern'

897
00:43:26.604 --> 00:43:32.925
'Annually 17 tonne heroin
worth 70 billion is being consumed'

898
00:43:32.965 --> 00:43:36.085
'In India according to statistic reports'

899
00:43:36.124 --> 00:43:40.016
'To control this. Central and
State narcotics agencies'

900
00:43:40.345 --> 00:43:41.420
[mobile ringing]

901
00:43:41.445 --> 00:43:42.445
Sir?

902
00:43:42.484 --> 00:43:44.487
Round up all the rowdies
in Varghese's gang

903
00:43:44.511 --> 00:43:45.524
Okay. sir

904
00:43:45.524 --> 00:43:47.844
- Did you trace the # I told you to?
- Yes. sir

905
00:43:48.124 --> 00:43:49.245
'Madhumitha P
D/o Parimala R'

906
00:43:49.245 --> 00:43:50.965
'24/1. Uyir Ulag house
Periyapalli street'

907
00:43:51.925 --> 00:43:52.927
Sudhandhiram

908
00:43:52.951 --> 00:43:53.987
Coming

909
00:43:55.163 --> 00:43:56.229
[clearing throat]

910
00:43:56.252 --> 00:43:58.052
You will be alone at home

911
00:43:59.278 --> 00:44:00.407
The police will come

912
00:44:00.685 --> 00:44:02.125
They will conduct an inquiry too

913
00:44:02.445 --> 00:44:05.005
Whatever question they ask
show no fear whatsoever

914
00:44:05.249 --> 00:44:06.569
Tell them. 'I don't know'

915
00:44:06.963 --> 00:44:08.243
Can I say something?

916
00:44:08.268 --> 00:44:09.348
I'll stay inside

917
00:44:09.538 --> 00:44:11.009
You lock the door on the outside

918
00:44:11.371 --> 00:44:13.447
I will lie low
staying off the radar

919
00:44:15.165 --> 00:44:16.844
'Hello. Parami
Office. huh?'

920
00:44:18.188 --> 00:44:20.541
That Varghese who hit on
your daughter is dead it seems

921
00:44:20.564 --> 00:44:21.901
Aiyo!
When?

922
00:44:21.925 --> 00:44:23.043
You didn't know?

923
00:44:23.084 --> 00:44:26.644
Hey! You ganged up as a family and
killed him as you claimed you would

924
00:44:26.925 --> 00:44:28.133
I'm happy too

925
00:44:28.156 --> 00:44:29.240
But scared heart of hearts

926
00:44:29.266 --> 00:44:30.547
His mother is a big-time rowdy

927
00:44:32.336 --> 00:44:34.145
She will barge in here
and bash up all of you

928
00:44:34.170 --> 00:44:35.229
Police will come

929
00:44:35.324 --> 00:44:36.636
'Maybe even the military'

930
00:44:37.245 --> 00:44:38.404
What do you want me to do?

931
00:44:38.404 --> 00:44:39.843
I'm asking you to vacate

932
00:44:40.005 --> 00:44:41.284
- I can't shift. Ulag
- Why?

933
00:44:41.324 --> 00:44:42.324
I mean. Uyir

934
00:44:42.364 --> 00:44:44.208
We are in no way connected
to this murder. sir

935
00:44:44.234 --> 00:44:45.314
Not only that

936
00:44:45.339 --> 00:44:46.579
They are still students. Ulag

937
00:44:47.440 --> 00:44:49.125
Give me 3 years time. Uyir

938
00:44:49.165 --> 00:44:51.765
3 years? You want me to
count bars for those 3 years?

939
00:44:51.804 --> 00:44:53.844
Yov! I am the one in a soup

940
00:44:53.884 --> 00:44:56.561
Better vacate now. man
Give me the house key this evening

941
00:44:56.584 --> 00:44:58.725
3 years indeed!
Why not ask for 30 years?

942
00:44:58.924 --> 00:45:00.685
Your faces look like an accused

943
00:45:00.724 --> 00:45:01.738
'Soup ready. my dear'

944
00:45:01.762 --> 00:45:02.788
'I am ready too'

945
00:45:15.450 --> 00:45:17.041
The police won't find
the killer. akka

946
00:45:17.245 --> 00:45:19.125
They are acting
as if they are investigating

947
00:45:19.284 --> 00:45:20.644
We have to hunt him down

948
00:45:21.284 --> 00:45:23.283
Whoever nabs my son's murderer

949
00:45:23.927 --> 00:45:25.628
I'll transfer this house
in his name

950
00:45:25.701 --> 00:45:26.815
'Gift him a car'

951
00:45:26.894 --> 00:45:28.773
And cover his entire wedding expenses

952
00:45:29.856 --> 00:45:31.257
'Find the killer. da'

953
00:45:31.746 --> 00:45:32.906
Hunt him down

954
00:45:33.205 --> 00:45:35.284
Akka. all that is fine

955
00:45:35.804 --> 00:45:37.725
Why didn't Jomi George
attend the funeral. akka?

956
00:45:40.725 --> 00:45:42.724
Akka. Aslam Mustafa also
didn't attend the funeral

957
00:45:51.885 --> 00:45:53.084
Hey Jayanthy

958
00:45:53.644 --> 00:45:54.843
Aren't you a nurse?

959
00:45:54.901 --> 00:45:56.821
[humming a song from 'Yuddham Sei']

960
00:45:56.844 --> 00:45:58.245
'Don't tell anyone. di'

961
00:45:58.363 --> 00:46:00.042
'I am trusting you completely'

962
00:46:00.278 --> 00:46:03.447
'You know this camphor
I like sniffing it often'

963
00:46:03.843 --> 00:46:05.884
I chew betel nut often too

964
00:46:06.167 --> 00:46:07.256
'And then'

965
00:46:07.284 --> 00:46:09.511
I am addicted to
Axe brand balm

966
00:46:10.112 --> 00:46:12.681
Will I have any health issue
later on in life. because of this?

967
00:46:12.706 --> 00:46:13.947
Who is inside?

968
00:46:15.940 --> 00:46:17.341
- WHO IS INSIDE?
- Oh God!

969
00:46:17.364 --> 00:46:18.484
Anybody there?

970
00:46:18.674 --> 00:46:20.234
[doorbell ringing]

971
00:46:22.916 --> 00:46:24.685
I can see you reversing your steps

972
00:46:24.996 --> 00:46:26.676
String hopper head

973
00:46:26.844 --> 00:46:28.044
Is anyone inside?

974
00:46:29.164 --> 00:46:30.244
Sudden silence?

975
00:46:30.514 --> 00:46:31.980
Having done all this

976
00:46:32.005 --> 00:46:34.084
She has acted as if
she is so innocent

977
00:46:35.051 --> 00:46:36.820
That's why you didn't pick my call?

978
00:46:36.917 --> 00:46:38.324
Have you noticed
this trait in some?

979
00:46:38.324 --> 00:46:41.005
Curse them all you want
Use your choicest cuss words

980
00:46:41.005 --> 00:46:42.577
Advise them till
your throat is hoarse

981
00:46:42.600 --> 00:46:43.832
They will still be the same

982
00:46:44.564 --> 00:46:46.394
That character fits my sister to the T

983
00:46:46.454 --> 00:46:47.582
Super character

984
00:46:47.844 --> 00:46:49.284
- Huh?
- Very interesting

985
00:46:49.644 --> 00:46:50.833
I must meet my sis-in-law

986
00:46:51.533 --> 00:46:52.633
No need

987
00:46:54.114 --> 00:46:56.084
Did my husband call you?

988
00:46:56.125 --> 00:46:57.697
And ask if you came to Chennai?

989
00:46:57.720 --> 00:46:58.764
'No. akka'

990
00:46:58.764 --> 00:47:01.253
I won't blabber
You zip your lips

991
00:47:01.284 --> 00:47:04.083
'He has some kind of
doubt about you. da'

992
00:47:04.125 --> 00:47:05.440
Is anyone in there?

993
00:47:05.561 --> 00:47:06.621
'How?'

994
00:47:06.645 --> 00:47:07.765
Talking to yourself?

995
00:47:07.789 --> 00:47:08.829
'I AM SPOOKED'

996
00:47:09.582 --> 00:47:10.885
Open your mouth
and speak up

997
00:47:10.924 --> 00:47:12.014
'Open the door'

998
00:47:12.038 --> 00:47:13.395
'I will even reduce your rent'

999
00:47:13.419 --> 00:47:14.447
'Hello?'

1000
00:47:14.844 --> 00:47:15.933
I'll be back

1001
00:47:18.741 --> 00:47:20.240
[humming]

1002
00:47:25.444 --> 00:47:26.685
Hey! Tell me

1003
00:47:27.399 --> 00:47:29.023
Where did you get this Stamp?

1004
00:47:29.125 --> 00:47:30.405
Post office. sir

1005
00:47:33.312 --> 00:47:34.915
I'll slice your mouth
and stitch you up

1006
00:47:34.937 --> 00:47:36.123
Don't know. sir

1007
00:47:36.580 --> 00:47:38.140
Friend is dead
and he's joking

1008
00:47:38.164 --> 00:47:39.405
Sir. we are grieving inside

1009
00:47:39.405 --> 00:47:40.885
He deserved to die. sir

1010
00:47:40.924 --> 00:47:43.645
- Why should he die?
- He's more dangerous than his mother

1011
00:47:43.924 --> 00:47:44.965
Why dangerous?

1012
00:47:45.010 --> 00:47:47.211
'He has 15 schools
and 18 colleges. sir'

1013
00:47:53.445 --> 00:47:55.405
Is Varghese loaded that much?

1014
00:47:55.444 --> 00:47:56.725
Drug supply. sir

1015
00:47:56.965 --> 00:47:59.177
'He supplies drugs to
all the schools and colleges. sir'

1016
00:47:59.201 --> 00:48:02.685
'Drug supplier to students. staff
and children of affluent families'

1017
00:48:11.084 --> 00:48:14.485
'He hosts parties every night. sir
You can have any drug you dream of'

1018
00:48:14.523 --> 00:48:17.884
'Sir. you know Aslam Mustafa?
Close friend of Varghese. sir'

1019
00:48:18.405 --> 00:48:21.165
'He didn't even attend the funeral
I have my doubts on him. sir'

1020
00:48:21.524 --> 00:48:23.125
'He is hosting a party tomorrow too'

1021
00:48:23.125 --> 00:48:24.284
Heard that. sir?

1022
00:48:25.204 --> 00:48:26.884
How about gate-crashing that party?

1023
00:48:36.804 --> 00:48:38.523
What? Did the police land up?

1024
00:48:38.564 --> 00:48:40.524
Only 'fear' gripped me
No one else turned up

1025
00:48:40.645 --> 00:48:43.444
What's wrong with the police?
Slower than a snail in their inquiry

1026
00:48:43.810 --> 00:48:47.851
Only if they inquire with lightning speed
can they zero in on the killer

1027
00:48:48.520 --> 00:48:51.142
I feel like I am catching the flu. dear

1028
00:48:51.276 --> 00:48:52.543
Only I'm feeling that way?

1029
00:48:52.566 --> 00:48:54.645
- Or you have the same symptom?
- I feel sick too

1030
00:48:54.645 --> 00:48:56.725
I bought some tablets
on my way back from work

1031
00:48:58.645 --> 00:48:59.725
Me too. pa

1032
00:49:00.984 --> 00:49:04.264
Even I went to the doctor
Had IV drips and injection

1033
00:49:04.323 --> 00:49:05.404
Aiyo!

1034
00:49:05.445 --> 00:49:07.485
- 'So sad'
- How much did you spend. dear?

1035
00:49:07.764 --> 00:49:09.484
Pa. I spent my personal money

1036
00:49:09.484 --> 00:49:10.885
Don't get me wrong

1037
00:49:11.164 --> 00:49:14.205
I need to maintain an account
of our expenses because of this case

1038
00:49:14.245 --> 00:49:15.604
'That's why I asked'

1039
00:49:18.484 --> 00:49:19.680
Good lord!

1040
00:49:20.763 --> 00:49:22.524
'A chap called Varghese is dead'

1041
00:49:22.563 --> 00:49:24.604
'The last call he received
was from your number'

1042
00:49:24.604 --> 00:49:25.965
'Who are you?'

1043
00:49:30.205 --> 00:49:32.125
Swear you didn't kill Varghese

1044
00:49:32.164 --> 00:49:33.425
Hey! Swear now

1045
00:49:33.448 --> 00:49:34.471
Do it now

1046
00:49:34.844 --> 00:49:36.090
Who else would have killed him?

1047
00:49:36.114 --> 00:49:37.235
Swear...swear now

1048
00:49:44.924 --> 00:49:46.124
'Hey! You there'

1049
00:49:46.844 --> 00:49:48.925
You must swallow
the bull's eye fully

1050
00:49:49.885 --> 00:49:51.564
If a single drop of yolk spills

1051
00:49:52.313 --> 00:49:53.954
- FIR only
- Aiyaiyo!

1052
00:49:56.566 --> 00:49:57.727
'Listen'

1053
00:49:58.444 --> 00:50:00.371
'If rowdies take on
the job of the police'

1054
00:50:01.248 --> 00:50:03.127
Will the police turn into rowdies?

1055
00:50:03.677 --> 00:50:06.877
You want me to wait
hand and foot on your boss lady?

1056
00:50:06.925 --> 00:50:09.525
Nothing of that sort. sir
She wants super fast action

1057
00:50:09.549 --> 00:50:10.645
A mother's grief

1058
00:50:10.676 --> 00:50:11.812
On fire. huh?

1059
00:50:12.724 --> 00:50:13.799
Shut up and sit down

1060
00:50:15.013 --> 00:50:17.045
"Don't look at me; please refrain"

1061
00:50:17.374 --> 00:50:18.460
Dai!

1062
00:50:19.676 --> 00:50:21.843
'You don't even know
to swallow a sunny-side up'

1063
00:50:22.364 --> 00:50:24.205
You intend tracking down the killer. eh?

1064
00:50:25.323 --> 00:50:26.685
I ate it without spilling. sir

1065
00:50:26.725 --> 00:50:28.324
Is that so?
Clap...clap...clap

1066
00:50:29.093 --> 00:50:30.205
Clap for him. da

1067
00:50:33.618 --> 00:50:35.377
I believe your boss lady
has a love interest

1068
00:50:40.444 --> 00:50:42.005
Varghese got to know that. it seems

1069
00:50:49.073 --> 00:50:51.724
'Jomi George Nicholas Cage is a brand. da'

1070
00:50:51.748 --> 00:50:53.907
'If you try to destroy that brand'

1071
00:50:54.072 --> 00:50:57.072
'I will go bang-bang-bang
Shoot all of you and move on'

1072
00:50:57.356 --> 00:50:58.382
Shoot. da

1073
00:50:58.406 --> 00:51:01.584
If I see you anywhere
near my house again

1074
00:51:03.499 --> 00:51:06.339
If he dares to step
into our home once more

1075
00:51:07.298 --> 00:51:08.947
I won't make allowance
for you as mother

1076
00:51:08.978 --> 00:51:11.892
I'll pound your skull
and coolly walk away

1077
00:51:12.280 --> 00:51:13.918
He didn't attend Varghese's funeral

1078
00:51:14.230 --> 00:51:15.825
Maybe he killed Varghese?

1079
00:51:22.134 --> 00:51:23.773
If you didn't kill him

1080
00:51:24.061 --> 00:51:27.666
Then why the hell
did you go hiding in the sea?

1081
00:51:27.802 --> 00:51:30.082
Huh? To fish in the Bay of Bengal!

1082
00:51:30.944 --> 00:51:33.184
It is all a safety precaution

1083
00:51:33.439 --> 00:51:36.413
Or did the mother kill her son
because he found out about her lover?

1084
00:51:37.364 --> 00:51:38.564
Of course not. sir

1085
00:51:38.604 --> 00:51:40.725
Who the hell killed Varghese?

1086
00:51:40.779 --> 00:51:41.847
Don't know. sir

1087
00:51:44.841 --> 00:51:45.964
Eat

1088
00:51:46.055 --> 00:51:48.284
My daughter is ready to become a wife

1089
00:51:48.343 --> 00:51:50.262
She has learnt to
make coconut chutney!

1090
00:51:50.287 --> 00:51:52.517
Should girls always be linked
only with the kitchen?

1091
