1093
00:51:59.364 --> 00:52:01.427
'M.Emperuman
Inspector'

1094
00:52:16.524 --> 00:52:17.722
[Tina barking]

1095
00:52:21.572 --> 00:52:23.149
- Amma
- 'What. di?'

1096
00:52:24.645 --> 00:52:25.697
Come in

1097
00:52:26.941 --> 00:52:27.970
Hi aunty

1098
00:52:27.996 --> 00:52:30.580
You wanted to see
my lifetime prisoner. no?

1099
00:52:31.604 --> 00:52:32.965
Here is that 'piece'

1100
00:52:33.031 --> 00:52:34.069
Take a good look

1101
00:52:35.445 --> 00:52:36.645
His name is Chittu

1102
00:52:36.925 --> 00:52:38.324
'Chittarasan'

1103
00:52:38.364 --> 00:52:39.645
Er...please sit

1104
00:52:40.485 --> 00:52:42.227
There are 2 ways of getting married

1105
00:52:42.484 --> 00:52:44.925
1 - inform your parents
and all your relatives

1106
00:52:44.965 --> 00:52:47.844
Invite family. friends and serve
piping hot coffee and crisp 'bhajji'

1107
00:52:47.934 --> 00:52:49.705
'We'll get back to you'
will be the reaction

1108
00:52:49.729 --> 00:52:51.409
Waiting endlessly
for a groom to say 'yes'

1109
00:52:51.764 --> 00:52:52.844
2nd way

1110
00:52:52.885 --> 00:52:54.843
Don't give any hassles to anyone

1111
00:52:54.885 --> 00:52:57.864
No wasted expense
on coffee. fritters etc

1112
00:52:58.526 --> 00:53:01.245
Finding my own Mr Right
Bring him home

1113
00:53:01.245 --> 00:53:03.604
Saying. 'he is my choice'
like I am doing now

1114
00:53:04.478 --> 00:53:06.437
Money saved for parents

1115
00:53:06.468 --> 00:53:08.749
No stress running around
and no tension either

1116
00:53:10.803 --> 00:53:11.834
1 minute

1117
00:53:11.860 --> 00:53:12.916
Okay. aunty

1118
00:53:13.376 --> 00:53:15.461
- Come in. di
- 1 minute

1119
00:53:16.165 --> 00:53:17.445
Looks like she is shell shocked

1120
