1130
00:53:41.197 --> 00:53:42.604
Let's postpone it

1131
00:53:45.031 --> 00:53:47.351
For the time being. no need
to tell your appa anything

1132
00:53:47.375 --> 00:53:49.125
I'll tell him myself
when the time is right

1133
00:53:49.924 --> 00:53:51.777
Have you watched 'Papanasam'?

1134
00:53:51.802 --> 00:53:53.411
Huh? No

1135
