'But very useful
if I hand it over to you'

1167
00:55:34.852 --> 00:55:35.979
'That is why'

1168
00:55:36.333 --> 00:55:38.133
'I want you to pay me 20 lakhs'

1169
00:55:40.485 --> 00:55:43.364
'Otherwise I will upload it
on social media'

1170
00:55:44.691 --> 00:55:46.819
'The police will automatically
come to your doorstep'

1171
00:55:46.843 --> 00:55:48.618
'If you think of hiding it'

1172
00:55:48.644 --> 00:55:50.603
'I will make sure
you go behind bars'

1173
