Aiyaiyo!

1182
00:56:12.506 --> 00:56:13.528
'Er...hmmm'

1183
00:56:13.965 --> 00:56:16.323
Our girls swore on us that day

1184
00:56:19.252 --> 00:56:20.734
But somehow I have

1185
00:56:20.992 --> 00:56:23.072
A strong suspicion only about  you

1186
