1191
00:56:36.385 --> 00:56:37.731
On the day of the murder

1192
00:56:39.001 --> 00:56:42.218
Your brother has lied and
travelled all the way here

1193
00:56:42.563 --> 00:56:44.020
Where did he go?

1194
00:56:44.043 --> 00:56:45.503
Where did he say-

1195
00:56:45.645 --> 00:56:47.182
You know my health is fragile!

1196
00:56:48.925 --> 00:56:51.964
In the end looks like he will
accuse me of the murder

1197
00:56:52.005 --> 00:56:53.685
Good lord!
I can't take this

1198
00:56:53.771 --> 00:56:55.526
'This is why I don't come
anywhere near you'

1199
00:56:56.930 --> 00:56:58.842
'If you had joined
the police force. game over'

1200
00:56:58.865 --> 00:57:00.547
'Our country would have
gone to the dogs'

1201
00:57:13.245 --> 00:57:14.524
Hey dude!

1202
00:57:14.564 --> 00:57:17.523
'Partying with just booze
is outdated style now'

1203
00:57:17.679 --> 00:57:19.039
'Only one intoxicant'

1204
00:57:19.188 --> 00:57:21.029
Stamp
Present trend

1205
00:57:21.243 --> 00:57:23.564
Can you see everything
in kaleidoscopic colors?

1206
00:57:23.884 --> 00:57:25.364
- Yessss
- Eyyyy!

1207
00:57:28.105 --> 00:57:29.128
'Heady. huh?'

1208
00:57:29.154 --> 00:57:30.432
Hey...Vicky...Vicky

1209
00:57:30.457 --> 00:57:31.697
Don't go on a bad trip

1210
00:57:31.722 --> 00:57:32.963
What happened?

1211
00:57:33.247 --> 00:57:34.510
What's wrong with him?

1212
00:57:34.563 --> 00:57:36.165
[siren wailing]

1213
00:57:36.524 --> 00:57:37.924
'HEY! WHAT HAS HAPPENED?'

1214
00:57:38.272 --> 00:57:39.385
'The police are here'

1215
00:57:40.570 --> 00:57:41.680
Shucks!

1216
00:57:51.872 --> 00:57:53.152
Heart attack. sir

1217
00:57:53.333 --> 00:57:54.694
He has used LSD

1218
00:57:54.934 --> 00:57:57.093
This drug goes by different names

1219
00:57:57.117 --> 00:57:58.558
We call it 'Stamp'

1220
00:57:59.205 --> 00:58:01.204
'College students
IT boys and girls'

1221
00:58:01.204 --> 00:58:02.404
'All of them are addicted'

1222
00:58:02.763 --> 00:58:05.763
'With repetitive consumption
it affects the nerve in the brain'

1223
00:58:05.788 --> 00:58:07.468
'They become psychotic. sir'

1224
00:58:08.445 --> 00:58:12.285
Sir. unless the Govt takes
immediate action to cure these fellows

1225
00:58:12.804 --> 00:58:14.763
It's going to be very.
very dangerous. sir

1226
00:58:14.804 --> 00:58:16.165
That's my word of caution

1227
00:58:17.125 --> 00:58:18.324
Thank you. doctor

1228
00:58:18.883 --> 00:58:19.912
- Kovi
- Sir

1229
00:58:19.937 --> 00:58:22.867
Drag all those in that party
to the station forcefully

1230
00:58:22.893 --> 00:58:23.937
Yes. sir

1231
00:58:24.165 --> 00:58:26.466
I am actually suspecting my dad

1232
00:58:27.032 --> 00:58:28.674
Appa is doubting my amma

1233
00:58:28.924 --> 00:58:31.924
Amma thinks my sister and I
did something hand in glove

1234
00:58:32.497 --> 00:58:34.500
I know my sister is not so capable

1235
