Hey!

1240
00:58:50.323 --> 00:58:52.454
- What are you doing here?
- Pani puri. sir

1241
00:58:52.778 --> 00:58:54.382
- Who is she?
- Friend

1242
00:58:54.802 --> 00:58:55.803
What is your name?

1243
00:58:55.803 --> 00:58:57.445
- Parasakthi
- Which college?

1244
00:58:57.718 --> 00:58:58.750
A R M college

1245
00:59:01.364 --> 00:59:02.763
How long have you known him?

1246
00:59:03.925 --> 00:59:05.604
We met recently. sir

1247
00:59:08.925 --> 00:59:10.885
- Did you find your bike. da?
- Not yet. sir

1248
00:59:11.451 --> 00:59:13.148
- You'll get it
- 'Thank you. sir'

1249
00:59:13.197 --> 00:59:14.203
Come here

1250
00:59:18.440 --> 00:59:19.508
Go

1251
00:59:24.484 --> 00:59:26.224
- Hello?
- The girls will be glued to the TV

1252
00:59:26.720 --> 00:59:28.903
- Or fiddle with their phone
- Aiyo!

1253
00:59:29.804 --> 00:59:31.083
'From when?'

1254
00:59:34.645 --> 00:59:36.165
What happened?

1255
00:59:37.323 --> 00:59:38.364
What is it. dear?

1256
00:59:38.404 --> 00:59:39.508
My akka-

1257
00:59:39.685 --> 00:59:40.966
My elder sister is unwell

1258
00:59:41.725 --> 00:59:44.284
Why this dramatic pause?
You can say that promptly

1259
00:59:44.725 --> 00:59:46.444
You need to go visit her?

1260
00:59:47.063 --> 00:59:48.503
Why are you overthinking?

1261
00:59:48.528 --> 00:59:49.562
Please go

1262
00:59:49.947 --> 00:59:51.509
You girls want to go
with your father?

1263
00:59:51.533 --> 00:59:52.571
You should tag along

1264
00:59:52.748 --> 00:59:54.827
You can't get a better aunt than her

1265
00:59:54.851 --> 00:59:55.988
'In this whole world!'

1266
00:59:57.020 --> 00:59:58.250
You were our first born

1267
00:59:58.485 --> 01:00:00.328
She saw you for the first time
when you were 3

1268
01:00:00.353 --> 01:00:03.119
You were born next. she didn't even
peep in till you were 4 years plus

1269
01:00:03.144 --> 01:00:04.264
Shut up!

1270
01:00:04.563 --> 01:00:06.524
All you can do is shut me up

1271
01:00:06.564 --> 01:00:09.604
As a bride wanting to marry you
I became your wife. you see

1272
01:00:09.685 --> 01:00:10.765
Take it out on me

1273
01:00:13.683 --> 01:00:14.963
1 egg 'dosa'?

1274
01:00:14.987 --> 01:00:17.587
My akka is critical
You are thinking of egg 'dosa'!

1275
01:00:17.928 --> 01:00:19.729
Don't want?
Fine. forget it

1276
01:00:21.243 --> 01:00:22.725
You know trip setter Mustafa. sir?

1277
01:00:22.764 --> 01:00:24.106
Someone has murdered him. sir

1278
01:00:29.157 --> 01:00:31.290
'Move back...clear out'

1279
01:00:34.113 --> 01:00:35.353
Sir. take a look

1280
01:00:38.925 --> 01:00:40.125
Sir. post

1281
01:00:40.125 --> 01:00:41.205
[dog barking]

1282
01:00:53.763 --> 01:00:54.774
Agnisatchi. ma

1283
01:00:56.804 --> 01:00:57.828
'Not bad at all'

1284
01:00:58.083 --> 01:01:00.044
'You are still full of
guts and temerity'

1285
01:01:00.802 --> 01:01:03.362
'A family member
in your home is the killer'

1286
01:01:03.572 --> 01:01:05.531
'I will eliminate
1 out of you 4'

1287
01:01:05.685 --> 01:01:07.525
'Because you suffer from
high BP and diabetes'

1288
01:01:07.524 --> 01:01:08.854
'I will release you alone'

1289
01:01:09.124 --> 01:01:10.194
'Sudhandhiram'

1290
01:01:14.404 --> 01:01:16.405
'Then who is the culprit
amongst the balance 3'

1291
01:01:16.517 --> 01:01:17.685
'The killer will know'

1292
01:01:18.430 --> 01:01:20.031
'Hereafter not 2 million'

1293
01:01:20.222 --> 01:01:21.851
'My demand is 2.5 million'

1294
01:01:22.323 --> 01:01:23.925
He is multiplying
by compound interest

1295
01:01:24.395 --> 01:01:25.429
'Read on'

1296
01:01:26.283 --> 01:01:27.804
'I can give you 2 more days'

1297
01:01:28.165 --> 01:01:29.764
'Yours graciously
Agnisatshi'

1298
01:01:37.180 --> 01:01:38.422
Which one of you?

1299
01:01:38.885 --> 01:01:40.172
Is it you. di?

1300
01:01:40.545 --> 01:01:41.842
Pcccht! Keep quiet. ma

1301
01:01:49.195 --> 01:01:50.806
Arnold. go to Camera #01

1302
01:01:51.445 --> 01:01:53.925
'Who is this chap?
Staring guiltily at the camera?'

1303
01:01:55.557 --> 01:01:56.618
'Who are these two?'

1304
01:01:57.662 --> 01:01:59.160
'Whom is he calling
outside his gate?'

1305
01:02:00.686 --> 01:02:01.686
'Stop'

1306
01:02:01.764 --> 01:02:03.243
'What is that in front of his bike?'

1307
01:02:03.284 --> 01:02:04.323
'Box of crackers. sir'

1308
01:02:04.386 --> 01:02:05.626
'Go to Parimala's house now'

1309
01:02:06.321 --> 01:02:07.323
'Zoom in on that gate'

1310
01:02:07.364 --> 01:02:08.804
'Same box of crackers. sir'

1311
01:02:08.844 --> 01:02:10.165
'Watch it. I will kill you'

1312
01:02:16.260 --> 01:02:17.572
Kovi. saw that?

1313
01:02:17.595 --> 01:02:20.037
The crackers Varghese bought
is in Parimala's house

1314
01:02:20.220 --> 01:02:21.708
What more evidence do you need. sir?

1315
01:02:22.049 --> 01:02:23.142
- Arnold
- Sir?

1316
01:02:23.586 --> 01:02:25.052
The tower range records?

1317
01:02:25.075 --> 01:02:26.267
- Did you collect?
- Yes. sir

1318
01:02:26.947 --> 01:02:30.724
Sir. Madhumitha calls Varghese
at 9:40 p.m and invites him

1319
01:02:31.044 --> 01:02:33.044
But before that.
at 9:35 p.m

1320
01:02:33.084 --> 01:02:35.490
'Madhumitha gets a call
from an unknown number. sir'

1321
01:02:35.766 --> 01:02:36.952
'At 9:56 p.m'

1322
01:02:36.976 --> 01:02:39.843
Varghese comes to Duming Lane
as specified by Madhumitha

1323
01:02:39.843 --> 01:02:41.644
'Sir. you know what is interesting here'

1324
01:02:41.685 --> 01:02:45.181
'The call to Madhumitha's # and Varghese
are at the same tower for 7 minutes'

1325
01:02:45.205 --> 01:02:46.245
Madhu darling

1326
01:02:46.803 --> 01:02:48.324
No Madhu darling here

1327
01:02:48.924 --> 01:02:50.898
Her uncles. both maternal
and paternal are here

1328
01:02:50.958 --> 01:02:55.637
'8th minute that unknown #
travels to Alwarpet tower range'

1329
01:02:55.930 --> 01:02:57.892
Kovi. Sengamalam's boyfriend

1330
01:02:57.916 --> 01:02:59.277
He's Jomi George. sir

1331
01:02:59.301 --> 01:03:01.300
He went into the sea. sir

1332
01:03:01.323 --> 01:03:03.278
'Then out of the blue
he comes ashore. sir'

1333
01:03:03.302 --> 01:03:04.989
'Then he suddenly
disappears into the sea'

1334
01:03:05.012 --> 01:03:06.771
Comes. goes. enters. exits

1335
01:03:06.795 --> 01:03:08.677
Exists. exits
Appears. disappears

1336
01:03:08.725 --> 01:03:10.885
He comes and buys
all the items he has to

1337
01:03:10.885 --> 01:03:13.506
Calls whomever he has to call
and returns to the sea. sir

1338
01:03:15.512 --> 01:03:17.182
'Yov Arnold?
Why get hyper?'

1339
01:03:17.967 --> 01:03:19.000
Ma...?

1340
01:03:20.604 --> 01:03:22.070
Appa's sister passed away. it seems

1341
01:03:22.773 --> 01:03:23.835
Oh gawd!

1342
01:03:26.691 --> 01:03:28.291
[tutting pseudo-sympathetically]

1343
01:03:28.433 --> 01:03:30.220
Why did she leave
in such a tearing hurry?

1344
01:03:30.243 --> 01:03:31.405
'I feel sad for her'

1345
01:03:31.405 --> 01:03:33.284
Leave your sadness aside

1346
01:03:33.685 --> 01:03:35.965
'I killed Varghese'

1347
01:03:35.989 --> 01:03:38.627
Your brother just confessed to me
standing here smiling ear to ear

1348
01:03:38.653 --> 01:03:39.886
'When I asked him. he said'

1349
01:03:39.911 --> 01:03:41.485
'My sister knows
everything A to Z'

1350
01:03:41.644 --> 01:03:42.688
What is this. di?

1351
01:03:49.203 --> 01:03:50.273
Hello?

1352
01:03:50.307 --> 01:03:51.383
'Hello?'

1353
01:03:51.673 --> 01:03:52.797
HELLO!

1354
01:03:53.182 --> 01:03:55.902
Why? Is my brother the only culprit?

1355
01:03:56.299 --> 01:03:59.069
'Your brother is an accessory
to the murder. didn't he tell you?'

1356
01:04:05.485 --> 01:04:06.577
Kamatchi

1357
01:04:06.602 --> 01:04:07.695
Coming

1358
01:04:08.960 --> 01:04:11.040
Did you join hands
to kill that chap. huh?

1359
01:04:11.063 --> 01:04:13.144
Brother. why are you yelling?
Why raise your voice?

1360
01:04:13.292 --> 01:04:16.179
'We asked him to delete
your daughter's photo from Insta'

1361
01:04:16.204 --> 01:04:18.256
He refused point blank
Your bro-in-law hit Varghese

1362
01:04:18.281 --> 01:04:21.382
Varghese retaliated. hit your bro-in-law
I hit him for hitting your bro-in-law

1363
01:04:21.406 --> 01:04:23.427
He hit me. seeing that
your bro-in-law hit him back

1364
01:04:23.451 --> 01:04:24.456
'I retaliated'

1365
01:04:24.480 --> 01:04:26.408
He hit me and bro-in-law pushed him

1366
01:04:26.434 --> 01:04:28.465
He fell down with a thud
on a stone and died

1367
01:04:28.489 --> 01:04:30.114
- Became a corpse
- AIYO!

1368
01:04:30.139 --> 01:04:32.378
If you yell like this
will the dead chap come alive?

1369
01:04:33.053 --> 01:04:35.557
Let's cremate our akka first
Let the police catch us

1370
01:04:35.581 --> 01:04:37.178
Let's cross the bridge then
Am I right?

1371
01:04:38.523 --> 01:04:39.865
Give the phone to Sakthi

1372
01:04:40.684 --> 01:04:42.405
Sakthi. here

1373
01:04:43.071 --> 01:04:44.093
Pa...?

1374
01:04:44.644 --> 01:04:46.604
It wasn't a random stranger
who killed Varghese

1375
01:04:47.283 --> 01:04:49.284
Both your uncles
closed his chapter

1376
01:04:49.532 --> 01:04:50.584
I know. pa

1377
01:04:51.617 --> 01:04:52.695
You know?!

1378
01:04:53.949 --> 01:04:55.125
Oho!

1379
01:04:55.406 --> 01:04:57.141
Then everyone knows everything

1380
01:04:57.175 --> 01:04:59.125
'Only I don't know anything'

1381
01:05:01.045 --> 01:05:02.191
Let it be

1382
01:05:02.283 --> 01:05:03.964
Even if they are the murderers

1383
01:05:04.115 --> 01:05:06.044
When the police come
we won't get caught. right?

1384
01:05:06.186 --> 01:05:07.525
We will get caught. pa

1385
01:05:07.769 --> 01:05:08.941
Are you serious?

1386
01:05:08.965 --> 01:05:10.165
How is that possible?

1387
01:05:10.165 --> 01:05:11.604
They may be the killers

1388
01:05:11.725 --> 01:05:13.324
But you instigated them. pa

1389
01:05:13.645 --> 01:05:15.205
You are blaming me?

1390
01:05:15.364 --> 01:05:16.563
How?

1391
01:05:16.803 --> 01:05:17.965
No. pa

1392
01:05:17.965 --> 01:05:20.284
The police will say 'you'
meaning all of us. pa

1393
01:05:21.044 --> 01:05:22.125
'Then'

1394
01:05:22.165 --> 01:05:24.564
Our entire family will be caught. pa

1395
01:05:28.939 --> 01:05:30.207
I swear I'll thrash-

1396
01:05:32.198 --> 01:05:33.478
Bro-in-law

1397
01:05:33.501 --> 01:05:35.583
Somehow 2 other murders followed

1398
01:05:36.500 --> 01:05:38.780
Instead of thinking
how to murder the 3rd person

1399
01:05:39.268 --> 01:05:41.204
Let's plan the future
to move from the present

1400
01:05:41.367 --> 01:05:42.897
Relax. uncle
Cool...cool

1401
01:05:43.604 --> 01:05:45.045
My head is spinning. da

1402
01:05:45.274 --> 01:05:47.715
- I don't know if the earth is spinning
- Come with us. bro

1403
01:05:48.124 --> 01:05:50.737
All of you have pitched in
to kill Varghese. no?

1404
01:05:53.101 --> 01:05:54.386
Why are you yelling. di?

1405
01:05:56.138 --> 01:05:59.618
What crime did he do to you
for you to kill him?

1406
01:05:59.965 --> 01:06:01.150
- Aiyo!
- Ma

1407
01:06:02.054 --> 01:06:03.925
She has fallen in love with him. ma

1408
01:06:10.395 --> 01:06:11.436
Oh God!

1409
01:06:11.884 --> 01:06:14.739
I don't know if my head is swirling
or the earth is twirling

1410
01:06:14.762 --> 01:06:16.322
My guardian deity. help

1411
01:06:18.946 --> 01:06:20.790
Your son has tortured
that family too much

1412
01:06:21.313 --> 01:06:23.084
He has threatened to
splash acid on her face

1413
01:06:23.245 --> 01:06:24.604
Our boy has hurled eggs at Sakthi

1414
01:06:24.604 --> 01:06:27.843
Akka. the father of those 2 girls
is manager in Velumani group

1415
01:06:28.604 --> 01:06:31.125
'Velumani's job is to
use mercenaries and murder'

1416
01:06:31.148 --> 01:06:33.388
'His signature is to chop
the victim's right hand'

1417
01:06:33.413 --> 01:06:35.483
'Same with our Varghese. akka'

1418
01:06:35.518 --> 01:06:36.932
I will handle everything

1419
01:06:38.965 --> 01:06:42.045
Kovi. didn't Varghese threaten
to splash acid on a girl's face?

1420
01:06:42.385 --> 01:06:44.026
Did you find out that girl's address?

1421
01:06:44.135 --> 01:06:46.256
Both the girls live under the same roof

1422
01:06:46.323 --> 01:06:47.709
They are both sisters. sir

1423
01:06:47.734 --> 01:06:50.014
'Parimala has even
complained against Varghese'

1424
01:06:50.177 --> 01:06:52.458
Hey! Get the car ready

1425
01:06:53.177 --> 01:06:54.677
I will destroy that family to ashes

1426
01:07:12.374 --> 01:07:14.494
- Sir
- Did you nab the accused or not?

1427
01:07:14.518 --> 01:07:16.478
We can reach in 10 minutes
We can arrest them. sir

1428
01:07:17.343 --> 01:07:18.383
Amma

1429
01:07:18.479 --> 01:07:19.799
Amma. you'll be fine

1430
01:07:29.916 --> 01:07:31.876
[hysterical laughter]

1431
01:07:39.378 --> 01:07:40.690
'Madhu...?'

1432
01:08:19.936 --> 01:08:21.656
We'll be there. pa
We'll catch the Govt bus

1433
01:08:21.696 --> 01:08:22.895
Govt bus?

1434
01:08:23.136 --> 01:08:24.136
Give me the phone

1435
01:08:26.256 --> 01:08:28.296
Do we have to be there?

1436
01:08:28.528 --> 01:08:29.961
- No need at all
- 'Thought as much'

1437
01:08:29.986 --> 01:08:31.414
Buy 1/2 kilo mutton

1438
01:08:31.439 --> 01:08:33.515
Make mutton curry.
relish and sleep peacefully

1439
01:08:33.864 --> 01:08:35.864
I'm boiling mad. I feel like-

1440
01:08:35.895 --> 01:08:39.175
All I asked was. should we come?
Why are you yelling your throat hoarse?

1441
01:08:39.256 --> 01:08:42.643
Sudhandhiram. I'm holding my temper
because my sister is lying lifeless

1442
01:08:42.667 --> 01:08:46.072
What can I do if your sister
passed away. my dear?

1443
01:08:46.096 --> 01:08:48.096
Want me to go with her
to keep her company?

1444
01:08:48.096 --> 01:08:49.896
Everyone has to die
some day or the other

1445
01:08:49.936 --> 01:08:51.016
Okay. fine

1446
01:08:51.016 --> 01:08:52.336
Get on to a bus at the earliest

1447
01:08:52.456 --> 01:08:53.936
I can't travel by bus

1448
01:08:54.862 --> 01:08:56.703
Bus stand has shifted
as far as Chengelpet!

1449
01:08:57.176 --> 01:08:58.296
I will come only by car

1450
01:08:58.816 --> 01:09:01.040
- Whaaat?
- My concern is the safety of my girls

1451
01:09:01.064 --> 01:09:03.183
'I have to travel to and fro
only by hiring a car'

1452
01:09:03.207 --> 01:09:04.450
How will you pay for the ca-

1453
01:09:04.616 --> 01:09:06.136
Is the funeral as early as today?

1454
01:09:06.136 --> 01:09:07.456
- Yes
- Oh! Yes

1455
01:09:07.696 --> 01:09:09.051
Otherwise it will stink

1456
01:09:09.075 --> 01:09:10.315
What did you say?

1457
01:09:10.976 --> 01:09:13.347
My sister will stink. huh?

1458
01:09:13.371 --> 01:09:14.856
My dear sister

1459
01:09:14.856 --> 01:09:16.176
How can you say she will stink?

1460
01:09:16.176 --> 01:09:18.136
I didn't mean your sister specifically

1461
01:09:18.136 --> 01:09:20.656
Even she were my sister.
a corpse is bound to stink!

1462
01:09:20.696 --> 01:09:22.205
- Stink?
- Aiyo!

1463
01:09:22.229 --> 01:09:23.795
I was so flustered
It just slipped out

1464
01:09:23.819 --> 01:09:25.371
I am sorry
Oh God!

1465
01:09:26.336 --> 01:09:28.496
She says our akka
will stink to high heaven

1466
01:09:29.128 --> 01:09:30.254
Stink. it seems

1467
01:09:30.390 --> 01:09:32.451
- Anna
- Akka...!

1468
01:09:33.656 --> 01:09:35.443
- Sister!
- Aunt!!

1469
01:09:44.176 --> 01:09:45.496
- Amma?
- Huh?

1470
01:09:45.819 --> 01:09:49.458
Middle class family like us only in
such emergency cases can take a flight

1471
01:09:49.816 --> 01:09:52.336
How about going by flight
for our aunt's funeral?

1472
01:09:53.016 --> 01:09:54.616
It will be a good memory for us

1473
01:09:55.056 --> 01:09:58.936
Want to attend your aunt's funeral
And then cremate your father too?

1474
01:09:59.616 --> 01:10:03.216
If your father even hears your idea
he will get a heart attack

1475
01:10:03.260 --> 01:10:05.780
Instead of flying high
go and get ready for the trip

1476
01:10:18.896 --> 01:10:20.616
Move a bit to the side

1477
01:10:21.056 --> 01:10:23.033
[Tina barking]
We will come back soon. my pet

1478
01:10:23.416 --> 01:10:25.216
- Appa?
- Not yet started?

1479
01:10:25.856 --> 01:10:27.567
We are ready. pa
Waiting for the car

1480
01:10:27.816 --> 01:10:29.358
Hurry up. only after you reach

1481
01:10:29.381 --> 01:10:31.263
- We can start the rituals
- We are coming. pa

1482
01:10:45.390 --> 01:10:46.471
[crows cawing]

1483
01:10:47.216 --> 01:10:48.248
Big relief!

1484
01:10:48.654 --> 01:10:51.494
No hassles from
that Speed Post man today

1485
01:10:57.023 --> 01:10:58.536
Emperuman
Reverse...move it

1486
01:11:04.991 --> 01:11:06.272
Why the hell is she here?

1487
01:11:09.147 --> 01:11:10.907
Watch me in action now

1488
01:11:12.086 --> 01:11:13.766
'Hey Curly mop head!
Come here'

1489
01:11:14.601 --> 01:11:16.136
- Yes. sir
- Is this Parimala's house?

1490
01:11:16.136 --> 01:11:17.176
My house. sir

1491
01:11:17.200 --> 01:11:18.512
What are you doing here?

1492
01:11:18.536 --> 01:11:19.816
Rented it to Parimala

1493
01:11:19.896 --> 01:11:22.343
- Where is Parimala. da?
- He just left with his family. sir

1494
01:11:22.976 --> 01:11:24.536
- What is your name?
- Uyir Ulag. sir

1495
01:11:24.656 --> 01:11:26.336
- Whaat?
- Uyir Ulag

1496
01:11:26.658 --> 01:11:28.640
- What is your profession?
- Foreign returned. sir

1497
01:11:28.936 --> 01:11:30.776
- Returned from?
- Nigeria

1498
01:11:30.896 --> 01:11:32.096
Come outside. da

1499
01:11:34.318 --> 01:11:35.456
Tell me. sir

1500
01:11:35.585 --> 01:11:36.985
Call that chap Parimala

1501
01:11:37.835 --> 01:11:39.496
- Tell me the number. sir
- HEY!

1502
01:11:39.496 --> 01:11:41.496
Sorry. sir
A small confusion

1503
01:11:42.496 --> 01:11:43.976
[mobile ringing]

1504
01:11:45.496 --> 01:11:47.616
You forgot to switch off the motor?

1505
01:11:47.616 --> 01:11:48.816
Aiyo! Yes. ma

1506
01:11:48.816 --> 01:11:50.336
- Not picking up. sir
- Call again

1507
01:11:51.130 --> 01:11:52.336
Oh gawd!

1508
01:11:52.336 --> 01:11:54.460
Why didn't you switch it off?
He will call me nonstop

1509
01:11:56.096 --> 01:11:57.414
- Not picking. sir
- Try again

1510
01:11:58.055 --> 01:11:59.225
Mad with a capital M

1511
01:11:59.359 --> 01:12:00.559
[water overflowing]

1512
01:12:02.416 --> 01:12:03.711
This is their daily routine. sir

1513
01:12:03.736 --> 01:12:05.773
Switch on the motor
and forget to switch it off

1514
01:12:05.798 --> 01:12:07.531
They won't spend money
even on an auto. sir

1515
01:12:07.556 --> 01:12:10.076
But early in the morning
imagine they took a cab

1516
01:12:10.301 --> 01:12:11.511
'Something fishy. sir'

1517
01:12:12.284 --> 01:12:13.335
Aiyo!

1518
01:12:14.413 --> 01:12:15.813
Switch off the motor. dear

1519
01:12:17.656 --> 01:12:18.913
Totally irresponsible. sir

1520
01:12:18.937 --> 01:12:20.416
Big deal!
Call him

1521
01:12:20.616 --> 01:12:21.696
What. di?

1522
01:12:22.696 --> 01:12:23.776
Hey! Block his #

1523
01:12:23.856 --> 01:12:25.136
Simple solution

1524
01:12:25.976 --> 01:12:27.118
No doubt at all. sir

1525
01:12:27.656 --> 01:12:28.936
Cell switched off. sir

1526
01:12:29.456 --> 01:12:32.188
I am sure they have committed
some crime and escaped altogether

1527
01:12:32.212 --> 01:12:33.696
What do you think they did. sir?

1528
01:12:33.720 --> 01:12:35.576
You're saying that family
has the guts to kill?

1529
01:12:35.616 --> 01:12:36.856
Murder. huh?

1530
01:12:37.292 --> 01:12:38.652
What do you mean. sir?

1531
01:12:38.676 --> 01:12:40.116
- How many?
- 3

1532
01:12:40.202 --> 01:12:41.802
- 3. huh?
- 2

1533
01:12:41.989 --> 01:12:43.960
- 2. is it?
- Hey! 1 murder is still a crime. da

1534
01:12:44.096 --> 01:12:45.296
Aiyaiyo!

1535
01:12:45.320 --> 01:12:46.839
- He is beyond any asylum
- DAI!

1536
01:12:46.863 --> 01:12:47.947
Where are you off to?

1537
01:12:47.972 --> 01:12:49.932
Sir. my head is
spinning like a top

1538
01:12:51.056 --> 01:12:52.633
What the hell have you both done?

1539
01:12:53.056 --> 01:12:55.216
- Ordered the bier
- Waiting for the garland

1540
01:12:55.256 --> 01:12:56.389
[gritting teeth]

1541
01:12:56.413 --> 01:12:58.336
Lord Krishna in Guruvayur. save me

1542
01:12:58.336 --> 01:12:59.656
- Hey
- Yes. sir

1543
01:12:59.758 --> 01:13:02.819
At the time of murder. where did you go
in your bike returning 2 hours later?

1544
01:13:02.936 --> 01:13:05.896
Sir. if I drive around for 2 hours
during the crime time

1545
01:13:05.936 --> 01:13:07.376
Does it mean
I'm the murderer. sir?

1546
01:13:07.856 --> 01:13:10.416
You think this face looks
like that of a murderer?

1547
01:13:10.496 --> 01:13:13.256
Then why did you stare at the CCTV
like you were a thief?

1548
01:13:13.768 --> 01:13:14.916
Sir

1549
01:13:15.018 --> 01:13:16.779
Any face on CCTV footage

1550
01:13:17.416 --> 01:13:18.896
Bound to look sneaky

1551
01:13:18.936 --> 01:13:20.831
Do you want to try
glaring at any CCTV?

1552
01:13:21.176 --> 01:13:23.296
Hey! Your face will go
beyond recognition

1553
01:13:23.320 --> 01:13:24.364
Call him. da

1554
01:13:24.646 --> 01:13:26.409
[mobile ringing]

1555
01:13:29.016 --> 01:13:30.203
Yov! Parimala

1556
01:13:30.496 --> 01:13:32.251
They tell me you killed and escaped?

1557
01:13:32.409 --> 01:13:35.441
These cops are taking my life out
in the name of inquiry drinking gruel here

1558
01:13:35.466 --> 01:13:37.189
Where the hell are you?
Come back now. man

1559
01:13:37.214 --> 01:13:38.690
'The police are all around your-'

1560
01:13:38.715 --> 01:13:40.115
Hello? Yov! Parimala

1561
01:13:41.056 --> 01:13:42.536
Sir. he cut the call

1562
01:13:42.536 --> 01:13:43.553
Call once more

1563
01:13:43.578 --> 01:13:44.618
Hello?

1564
01:13:47.160 --> 01:13:48.856
Definitely they are the culprits. sir

1565
01:13:49.176 --> 01:13:51.710
- He switched off his mobile. sir
- Call till he switches it on

1566
01:13:52.216 --> 01:13:54.713
What is the use of me calling
if he hasn't switched it on?

1567
01:13:54.737 --> 01:13:56.663
- Just do it. man
- Aiyo! God help me

1568
01:13:56.687 --> 01:13:59.601
Is the Govt blind?
Given this loony uniform and jeep

1569
01:13:59.625 --> 01:14:00.643
Who is this?

1570
01:14:01.795 --> 01:14:02.995
Who is 'who'?

1571
01:14:05.228 --> 01:14:06.548
Your daughter?

1572
01:14:07.336 --> 01:14:08.816
Mrs...Uyir Ulag

1573
01:14:09.603 --> 01:14:10.763
Yov!

1574
01:14:11.096 --> 01:14:13.336
Take down his # first
He is number 1 accused

1575
01:14:13.376 --> 01:14:14.656
Tell me your #. man

1576
01:14:14.869 --> 01:14:15.902
Go. hon

1577
01:14:16.776 --> 01:14:18.803
9 88
444 444

1578
01:14:18.896 --> 01:14:19.896
73. sir

1579
01:14:21.536 --> 01:14:22.980
Hey! It shows up as Parimala

1580
01:14:23.176 --> 01:14:24.610
I can give only his #. sir

1581
01:14:24.839 --> 01:14:26.056
You are here to nab him. no?

1582
01:14:26.080 --> 01:14:27.600
"Your spoken words have no rhythm"

1583
01:14:27.624 --> 01:14:30.408
Driver brother. please stop
in the shade somewhere

1584
01:14:30.432 --> 01:14:31.713
- 'Under a tree
- Okay. madam'

1585
01:14:32.191 --> 01:14:34.766
"Chasing the gates of light ahead"

1586
01:14:35.777 --> 01:14:37.584
'Ashes from the lies'

1587
01:14:37.843 --> 01:14:40.359
'Reflecting in your eyes'

1588
01:14:40.515 --> 01:14:42.545
'Whereabouts to find'

1589
01:14:42.711 --> 01:14:45.242
'In a speed of time'

1590
01:14:45.536 --> 01:14:47.216
- Enough
- Amma

1591
01:14:47.343 --> 01:14:49.296
I have a long term wish. ma

1592
01:14:49.536 --> 01:14:52.536
To sit under a tree and eat
as a family. together

1593
01:14:52.976 --> 01:14:55.456
I used to think every time
we traveled by bus

1594
01:14:57.016 --> 01:15:01.213
Look how my wish has come true
because our aunt died!

1595
01:15:05.936 --> 01:15:07.296
Bro-in-law

1596
01:15:07.396 --> 01:15:08.555
UNCLE!

1597
01:15:08.856 --> 01:15:09.976
One shot

1598
01:15:11.136 --> 01:15:13.376
Wanted to know if you
want a shot of strong coffee

1599
01:15:15.534 --> 01:15:16.856
- Go...go
- Okay. uncle

1600
01:15:16.896 --> 01:15:17.934
Get lost!

1601
01:15:18.643 --> 01:15:21.003
He is telling you to scoot. go. da

1602
01:15:22.176 --> 01:15:24.246
The drummers need
Rs 5000 as advance

1603
01:15:24.576 --> 01:15:26.319
Otherwise they won't beat
the funeral drum

1604
01:15:27.376 --> 01:15:30.676
Why are you tense now?
Anyway the police will nab us

1605
01:15:30.700 --> 01:15:33.598
Upload your tension after that
Be calm and cool till then

1606
01:15:35.724 --> 01:15:36.730
- Come
- What?

1607
01:15:40.994 --> 01:15:42.123
Go now

1608
01:15:42.148 --> 01:15:44.216
- Password is my birthday 12-12
- Okay. go

1609
01:15:44.241 --> 01:15:45.656
If you press 13. it will get lock-

1610
01:15:45.680 --> 01:15:46.974
Stop bugging me

1611
01:15:46.998 --> 01:15:48.918
- Talk
- 'Chithappa'

1612
01:15:49.474 --> 01:15:51.435
Not your appa's brother
I'm your appa speaking

1613
01:15:52.096 --> 01:15:53.145
'Where are you?'

1614
01:15:53.168 --> 01:15:54.296
When will you reach?

1615
01:15:54.456 --> 01:15:56.216
Another 2 hours. pa

1616
01:15:56.216 --> 01:15:57.241
We felt hungry

1617
01:15:57.266 --> 01:15:58.276
'So we stopped to eat'

1618
01:15:58.696 --> 01:16:00.054
Are you in a hotel?

1619
01:16:00.536 --> 01:16:01.656
Not a hotel. pa

1620
01:16:01.875 --> 01:16:04.176
Amma made chappathi at home
We packed it to eat on the way

1621
01:16:04.201 --> 01:16:06.186
'We parked by the roadside
and we are eating'

1622
01:16:07.285 --> 01:16:08.765
Give the phone to your amma

1623
01:16:09.184 --> 01:16:10.231
Rock it

1624
01:16:10.783 --> 01:16:12.536
Have you eaten?

1625
01:16:12.536 --> 01:16:14.576
Don't you have a conscience?
Not even a tiny bit?

1626
01:16:14.896 --> 01:16:16.376
Are you enjoying a picnic now?

1627
01:16:16.776 --> 01:16:17.815
My dear husband

1628
01:16:17.840 --> 01:16:21.376
Just because your sister died.
can all of us take a vow of starvation?

1629
01:16:21.416 --> 01:16:24.792
'Young girls will definitely get hungry
How can we come there and eat?'

1630
01:16:24.816 --> 01:16:26.376
What's wrong in that?

1631
01:16:26.376 --> 01:16:27.896
Hey! You want 'kurma'?

1632
01:16:28.056 --> 01:16:29.816
Did you cook in a rush. ma?

1633
01:16:29.917 --> 01:16:32.197
- Why?
- Not your usual yummy taste

1634
01:16:32.816 --> 01:16:34.666
No need to wait for us

1635
01:16:35.176 --> 01:16:37.096
If you need to cremate the body. do so

1636
01:16:37.776 --> 01:16:39.056
'Body'. huh?

1637
01:16:39.096 --> 01:16:40.816
If you dare refer
to my akka as 'body'

1638
01:16:40.816 --> 01:16:42.536
I will get mad as hell. Sudhandhiram

1639
01:16:43.056 --> 01:16:44.176
Listen. dear

1640
01:16:44.317 --> 01:16:46.918
How else to call a 'body' but a body?!

1641
01:16:47.096 --> 01:16:48.172
'Okay. forget it'

1642
01:16:48.195 --> 01:16:49.643
Your sister is no more

1643
01:16:49.667 --> 01:16:52.228
Please take a few sips and
munch some snack. don't starve

1644
01:16:53.376 --> 01:16:54.896
Everyone will lament loudly

1645
01:16:54.896 --> 01:16:58.403
'Then they will vacate the place
and eat till they burp. okay?'

1646
01:16:58.427 --> 01:17:01.896
You don't stand there
stiff like a freshly starched shirt

1647
01:17:01.896 --> 01:17:03.788
- 'Let's finish eating'
- Enjoy

1648
01:17:03.812 --> 01:17:05.051
Eat till you burp!

1649
01:17:06.776 --> 01:17:09.016
The police came to
our house looking for us

1650
01:17:09.256 --> 01:17:10.336
Whaaat?

1651
01:17:17.499 --> 01:17:19.098
Eat. hurry up

1652
01:17:19.776 --> 01:17:21.038
Pass that chappathi

1653
01:17:21.062 --> 01:17:22.583
Police came looking for us. ma?

1654
01:17:28.500 --> 01:17:29.620
How did I wear this?

1655
01:17:29.846 --> 01:17:31.818
[blowing the funeral conch]

1656
01:17:34.745 --> 01:17:35.808
Get lost!

1657
01:17:35.833 --> 01:17:36.854
Yes. Molly

1658
01:17:36.879 --> 01:17:38.461
Why did you switch off
your phone. da?

1659
01:17:39.056 --> 01:17:41.102
We are going to Palakkad
My dad's sister passed away

1660
01:17:41.127 --> 01:17:42.247
Oh!

1661
01:17:42.336 --> 01:17:43.416
Sorry

1662
01:17:43.441 --> 01:17:44.921
Poppy. I was a bit busy

1663
01:17:45.576 --> 01:17:47.096
Continue being busy

1664
01:17:47.136 --> 01:17:48.736
We are hatching eggs here. no?

1665
01:17:49.136 --> 01:17:50.182
'How is that. da?'

1666
01:17:50.207 --> 01:17:51.831
If a girl says yes to her guy

1667
01:17:51.856 --> 01:17:53.136
Expectations rise higher

1668
01:17:53.136 --> 01:17:55.296
'But if boys decide on a girl as wife'

1669
01:17:55.496 --> 01:17:57.456
He starts taking her totally for granted

1670
01:17:57.915 --> 01:17:59.235
Do you agree with me?

1671
01:17:59.259 --> 01:18:00.936
You have no sense of
time or place. Sakthi

1672
01:18:01.308 --> 01:18:03.422
- I'll call when I'm free
- What's the tearing hurry?

1673
01:18:03.447 --> 01:18:04.751
Chee! Hang up now

1674
01:18:05.096 --> 01:18:06.216
You hang up. useless

1675
01:18:12.166 --> 01:18:14.086
Hey vintage music master
Did you call Parimala?

1676
01:18:14.238 --> 01:18:16.758
Sir. that lady has blocked my #

1677
01:18:16.782 --> 01:18:17.912
'How will she pick my call?'

1678
01:18:17.936 --> 01:18:20.265
Gobbling fermented gruel
from Selvi akka instead of working

1679
01:18:20.290 --> 01:18:22.349
"Parimala. where are you?"

1680
01:18:22.374 --> 01:18:23.478
Kovi

1681
01:18:23.846 --> 01:18:24.856
Tell Arnold

1682
01:18:24.881 --> 01:18:26.539
- To trace Parimala's #
- Okay. sir

1683
01:18:29.776 --> 01:18:32.456
Sir. that lady has
sent a voice message

1684
01:18:33.688 --> 01:18:34.732
Let me listen

1685
01:18:35.256 --> 01:18:36.318
'Uyir Ulag'

1686
01:18:36.343 --> 01:18:39.352
'As usual Shakti forgot
to switch off the motor'

1687
01:18:39.527 --> 01:18:40.565
'Sorry'

1688
01:18:40.590 --> 01:18:42.710
'I have left Tina all alone'

1689
01:18:42.734 --> 01:18:44.935
'Please feed her
at her regular meal times'

1690
01:18:44.984 --> 01:18:46.784
- Who is Tina. da?
- Dog

1691
01:18:46.936 --> 01:18:49.176
- How dare you!
- I meant their pet dog. sir

1692
01:18:50.173 --> 01:18:51.841
Hey! You said she blocked your #

1693
01:18:52.936 --> 01:18:54.016
Wait. sir

1694
01:18:55.419 --> 01:18:57.908
[instructions on walkie-talkie]

1695
01:18:58.176 --> 01:19:00.379
She told me to feed her dog
and blocked my number. sir

1696
01:19:00.576 --> 01:19:02.216
Keep calling till she unblocks

1697
01:19:02.736 --> 01:19:03.896
- Unbloc-
- Do it. man

1698
01:19:04.153 --> 01:19:05.190
Move it

1699
01:19:05.215 --> 01:19:07.784
"In your words no rhythm appears
Fate may forget thirst of years"

1700
01:19:07.809 --> 01:19:09.630
"But this name shall conquer all fears"

1701
01:19:09.691 --> 01:19:11.272
"Across this blood-smeared street"

1702
01:19:11.296 --> 01:19:13.056
Why did you park yards away?

1703
01:19:13.056 --> 01:19:14.656
It is crowded over there. that's why

1704
01:19:14.696 --> 01:19:16.616
I want you to go there
only because of the crowd!

1705
01:19:16.656 --> 01:19:18.856
Shouldn't people notice
we have come by car!

1706
01:19:18.896 --> 01:19:19.902
Right. ma?

1707
01:19:19.927 --> 01:19:21.567
I'll smash all your teeth

1708
01:19:21.736 --> 01:19:23.816
The frame should show
the expenditure clearly. di

1709
01:19:23.856 --> 01:19:25.065
Go and park there

1710
01:19:25.089 --> 01:19:26.894
'In a speed of time'

1711
01:19:32.136 --> 01:19:33.296
[fake sobbing]

1712
01:19:34.976 --> 01:19:36.176
Sister-in-law. dear

1713
01:19:38.176 --> 01:19:39.216
Anni

1714
01:19:44.454 --> 01:19:46.496
We were not blessed enough!

1715
01:19:46.576 --> 01:19:49.358
What can we do?
She has left us now

1716
01:19:51.645 --> 01:19:53.801
'Wretched fellow!
How could you?'

1717
01:19:53.937 --> 01:19:55.325
[muttering angrily]

1718
01:19:55.964 --> 01:19:57.122
Damn your jinxed face!

1719
01:20:00.954 --> 01:20:02.144
'Just go'

1720
01:20:08.016 --> 01:20:10.934
I don't know what
we will do without her!

1721
01:20:11.296 --> 01:20:12.696
You shrugged my hand away. okay

1722
01:20:15.176 --> 01:20:16.696
Kurma was not tasty. huh?

1723
01:20:17.456 --> 01:20:18.776
Akkaâ€¦akka

1724
01:20:19.216 --> 01:20:20.336
'My dear sister-in-law'

1725
01:20:20.856 --> 01:20:24.776
As soon as you see me at the gate
you'll welcome me with open arms

1726
01:20:25.113 --> 01:20:27.878
Who will welcome me
like that hereafter?

1727
01:20:34.096 --> 01:20:35.676
Who is Madhumitha?

1728
01:20:38.013 --> 01:20:39.733
- Escape
- Escape. huh?

1729
01:20:40.125 --> 01:20:42.485
- Yes
- Hey! Who are you?

1730
01:20:43.209 --> 01:20:44.249
Uyir Ulag

1731
01:20:44.273 --> 01:20:45.353
Whaaat?

1732
01:20:45.715 --> 01:20:47.035
Uyir Ulag

1733
01:20:47.162 --> 01:20:48.442
Akka. police

1734
01:20:49.358 --> 01:20:51.976
Pass on the information
I'll dice her to pieces when she returns

1735
01:20:51.976 --> 01:20:53.226
That's what I anticipate

1736
01:20:53.250 --> 01:20:54.316
British. come. da

1737
01:20:54.416 --> 01:20:56.616
- I gave them my house
- 'Start the car'

1738
01:20:56.770 --> 01:20:58.090
Delayed rent

1739
01:20:58.115 --> 01:21:00.195
Wastage of water
Not paying the electricity bill

1740
01:21:00.220 --> 01:21:03.621
In the end they have driven me
to bang my head on my car!

1741
01:21:05.222 --> 01:21:07.136
I am so shattered

1742
01:21:08.470 --> 01:21:09.506
Okay

1743
01:21:09.531 --> 01:21:10.791
[clenching teeth]

1744
01:21:12.392 --> 01:21:13.615
Come with me. girls

1745
01:21:13.638 --> 01:21:15.896
Get the van. take money
from Kamatchi

1746
01:21:17.216 --> 01:21:19.776
You got us caught
you bloody sinner of a killer!

1747
01:21:19.856 --> 01:21:21.496
Driver. start the car

1748
01:21:21.536 --> 01:21:23.096
He was such a boorish fellow

1749
01:21:23.120 --> 01:21:24.440
He hit Kamatchi
I shoved him back

1750
01:21:26.456 --> 01:21:28.136
Who is getting into my car?

1751
01:21:28.176 --> 01:21:29.956
I proposed
Fate disposed

1752
01:21:30.067 --> 01:21:31.100
Police-

1753
01:21:31.463 --> 01:21:32.496
Are you drunk?

1754
01:21:33.936 --> 01:21:36.296
- Disappear before he appears
- He is here

1755
01:21:36.296 --> 01:21:37.841
Vanish into thin air

1756
01:21:38.848 --> 01:21:40.768
What is your beloved brother saying?

1757
01:21:41.416 --> 01:21:44.380
He proposed something
Fate disposed it seems!

1758
01:21:44.688 --> 01:21:45.902
Don't be a drama queen

1759
01:21:45.926 --> 01:21:48.981
Why did they come to Chennai?
Who told them to kill Varghese?

1760
01:21:51.257 --> 01:21:52.456
Should I answer now?

1761
01:21:53.027 --> 01:21:54.865
I can't...no

1762
01:21:55.856 --> 01:21:57.096
Great escape!

1763
01:21:57.296 --> 01:21:59.033
Come. sir
What brings you here again?

1764
01:21:59.057 --> 01:22:00.936
- Aren't you the house owner?
- Yes

1765
01:22:01.388 --> 01:22:03.119
- You have a spare key?
- No. sir

1766
01:22:03.243 --> 01:22:04.545
- Hey!
- Yes. sir

1767
01:22:04.569 --> 01:22:06.326
- Go. get it
- What do you plan to do?

1768
01:22:06.350 --> 01:22:07.816
I want to paint the interior

1769
01:22:07.816 --> 01:22:09.425
- Go. get it
- Cock and bull!

1770
01:22:12.149 --> 01:22:15.176
- I have to buy the farewell ritual sari
- Why wait for so long?

1771
01:22:15.216 --> 01:22:17.376
First tell me. did you eat?

1772
01:22:18.896 --> 01:22:20.336
I'm planning to buy a silk sari

1773
01:22:21.096 --> 01:22:23.416
Will your dead sister
come alive to drape a silk sari?

1774
01:22:23.416 --> 01:22:25.576
Why spend for her daughter
or daughter-in-law to wear?!

1775
01:22:25.616 --> 01:22:27.459
Buy a simple 'kandangi'
or cotton sari. enough

1776
01:22:27.483 --> 01:22:29.877
You had no problem
hiring a cab from Madras

1777
01:22:29.901 --> 01:22:31.805
This is more than enough
for your akka's nature

1778
01:22:31.830 --> 01:22:34.070
All this drama for a simple silk sari

1779
01:22:34.173 --> 01:22:36.493
This is a custom
everyone follows here

1780
01:22:36.752 --> 01:22:38.872
Please go ahead
and do what you want

1781
01:22:38.912 --> 01:22:41.552
You've already decided everything
and then why come and ask me?

1782
01:22:41.576 --> 01:22:42.781
Not like that. dear

1783
01:22:43.153 --> 01:22:45.752
Poor soul. she has left us
What can we do for her hereafter?

1784
01:22:46.213 --> 01:22:49.336
That's why I want to buy a silk sari
for Rs 10.000 to stun everyone

1785
01:22:49.336 --> 01:22:50.406
10.000?!

1786
01:22:50.430 --> 01:22:53.002
I'm saying stick to a budget
of Rs 1200 to 1300. dear

1787
01:22:53.026 --> 01:22:54.594
Kamatchi...shut up!

1788
01:22:55.560 --> 01:22:56.940
Okay. anna

1789
01:22:57.296 --> 01:22:58.656
I've bought the sari already

1790
01:22:58.733 --> 01:22:59.952
Rs 10.500

1791
01:23:01.048 --> 01:23:02.649
You spent so much?

1792
01:23:03.418 --> 01:23:05.858
If we ask anything
you'll don your Scrooge avatar!

1793
01:23:06.016 --> 01:23:07.736
Where did you get this much money?

1794
01:23:07.776 --> 01:23:09.950
I borrowed from Kumarasamy

1795
01:23:09.974 --> 01:23:12.151
Should you take a loan
to make your sister look lovely?

1796
01:23:12.176 --> 01:23:15.696
Oh! How did you afford a car
from Chennai to Palakkad now?

1797
01:23:15.696 --> 01:23:17.049
From my kitchen piggy bank!

1798
01:23:17.183 --> 01:23:18.376
Forget all that. dear

1799
01:23:18.408 --> 01:23:20.380
Take a look at the sari
to drape my dear sister in

1800
01:23:20.405 --> 01:23:21.485
Happy draping!

1801
01:23:21.510 --> 01:23:22.631
Driver. start the car

1802
01:23:23.174 --> 01:23:24.353
You girls take a look

1803
01:23:25.896 --> 01:23:26.956
DAI!

1804
01:23:27.166 --> 01:23:29.708
I'll give you a solid piece
of my mind. you moron

1805
01:23:30.136 --> 01:23:33.136
I am going through hell
with this family & co as my tenant

1806
01:23:41.003 --> 01:23:42.474
'Krishnamurthy - 1.20.000'

1807
01:23:46.656 --> 01:23:47.896
Kutlu. where are you?

1808
01:23:48.668 --> 01:23:49.909
- Sir?
- Tell me. Sengamalam

1809
01:23:49.934 --> 01:23:51.574
'How many times to call you?'

1810
01:23:51.976 --> 01:23:54.792
- We toil for you to line your pocket
- Why are you blabbering?

1811
01:23:54.816 --> 01:23:57.856
Sir. do something to
find my son's murderer

1812
01:23:58.096 --> 01:23:59.422
What is the use of crying?

1813
01:23:59.570 --> 01:24:00.856
I am there for you
I'll handle it

1814
01:24:04.376 --> 01:24:05.736
My dear akka

1815
01:24:14.748 --> 01:24:15.896
Move over and sit

1816
01:24:15.896 --> 01:24:17.038
Adjust a bit. bro

1817
01:24:17.070 --> 01:24:19.304
- Driver. come here
- Yes. madam

1818
01:24:19.656 --> 01:24:21.416
You are casually zip zap zooming

1819
01:24:21.736 --> 01:24:24.373
I'll pay you only to and fro
Chennai and Palakkad

1820
01:24:24.536 --> 01:24:26.635
Madam. I went only because
your relatives called

1821
01:24:26.659 --> 01:24:29.801
If they ask you to accompany them
to their grave. will you go there too?

1822
01:24:30.176 --> 01:24:31.976
- Let him go. ma
- Why buy trouble?

1823
01:24:32.056 --> 01:24:33.336
- 'Get down'
- Why. ma?

1824
01:24:33.376 --> 01:24:35.712
Why are you humiliating me
at my sister's funeral?

1825
01:24:35.736 --> 01:24:37.616
Won't your relatives travel by bike?

1826
01:24:37.616 --> 01:24:39.216
They are used to only car-rides!

1827
01:24:40.745 --> 01:24:42.656
- Keep quiet. ma
- You shut up. di

1828
01:24:42.696 --> 01:24:43.933
'We are caught now'

1829
01:24:44.496 --> 01:24:45.856
Aiyo! Police

1830
01:24:46.016 --> 01:24:47.416
They have come in search of us

1831
01:24:47.440 --> 01:24:48.763
We are doomed. eh?

1832
01:24:56.176 --> 01:24:58.256
Shall we drink a few pegs
and enjoy mutton curry?

1833
01:24:58.281 --> 01:25:00.001
Great idea
Say that first

1834
01:25:04.496 --> 01:25:05.936
What is this. Kamatchi?

1835
01:25:06.092 --> 01:25:07.332
He is dead as a door nail

1836
01:25:07.776 --> 01:25:08.912
Shhhh! Come

1837
01:25:08.936 --> 01:25:09.976
What. Raghava?

1838
01:25:10.176 --> 01:25:11.736
Akka. happy Deepavali

1839
01:25:11.776 --> 01:25:13.656
Finished offering God
on this festive occasion?

1840
01:25:13.696 --> 01:25:14.915
Good news for you

1841
01:25:15.126 --> 01:25:17.171
That boy who stalked our girls

1842
01:25:17.195 --> 01:25:19.256
Kamatchi and I hit him
and killed him. akka

1843
01:25:19.256 --> 01:25:20.296
Good lord!

1844
01:25:20.576 --> 01:25:22.456
- You killed him?
- 'Yes. akka'

1845
01:25:22.456 --> 01:25:23.576
What do you mean?

1846
01:25:25.311 --> 01:25:27.453
If my husband found out
he will chop you to pieces. da

1847
01:25:27.478 --> 01:25:29.078
Don't te...tell this to anyone

1848
01:25:29.180 --> 01:25:31.020
Escape before the police nab you

1849
01:25:31.553 --> 01:25:33.825
- Give the phone to my bro-in-law
- Sis-in-law?

1850
01:25:33.849 --> 01:25:36.081
How could you do this?

1851
01:25:36.535 --> 01:25:38.999
- Parasakthi knows
- Why did you tell her?

1852
01:25:39.023 --> 01:25:40.282
It was Parasakthi who sketched

1853
01:25:40.306 --> 01:25:41.696
'The entire plan for us'

1854
01:25:44.963 --> 01:25:46.663
- Did she ask you to kill him?
- 'Cha cha!'

1855
01:25:46.688 --> 01:25:48.694
'We came to knock sense
into his head and warn him'

1856
01:25:48.719 --> 01:25:49.744
Varghese refused

1857
01:25:49.769 --> 01:25:50.869
'I bashed him up'

1858
01:25:50.995 --> 01:25:52.435
He retaliated

1859
01:25:52.616 --> 01:25:54.736
Immediately your brother beat him up

1860
01:25:54.776 --> 01:25:57.370
'He beat up your brother
When he hit your brother'

1861
01:25:57.393 --> 01:25:59.405
I got angry. I beat Varghese
He returned the blows

1862
01:25:59.430 --> 01:26:00.497
Your brother lost his cool

1863
01:26:00.520 --> 01:26:01.564
'Pushed him to the ground'

1864
01:26:01.588 --> 01:26:03.204
There was a stone at that specific spot

1865
01:26:03.456 --> 01:26:05.295
How did we know
a stone will be there?

1866
01:26:05.536 --> 01:26:07.431
We knew he was dead
only this morning

1867
01:26:09.207 --> 01:26:10.448
Now we are murderers

1868
01:26:10.576 --> 01:26:12.376
Get the hell back to Palakkad

1869
01:26:12.725 --> 01:26:13.762
Okay

1870
01:26:13.787 --> 01:26:16.076
We got a gift for our niece
We'll keep it at the doorstep

1871
01:26:16.101 --> 01:26:17.141
Ask her to take it

1872
01:26:21.634 --> 01:26:23.794
If they ask anyone any question

1873
01:26:23.818 --> 01:26:26.027
- I'll tell them the truth
- Truth be told. what is it?

1874
01:26:26.052 --> 01:26:28.429
- Whatever they ask I'll tell them
- Go...go inside

1875
01:26:28.454 --> 01:26:29.574
- Go
- What else to do?

1876
01:26:31.373 --> 01:26:33.213
[Malayalam] Stay there
Follow them separately

1877
01:26:37.366 --> 01:26:38.765
[dog barking]

1878
01:26:51.268 --> 01:26:53.218
'Murder Cases'

1879
01:27:05.971 --> 01:27:07.612
Didn't you buy a silk sari?

1880
01:27:07.739 --> 01:27:09.659
Only the rich can show off like that

1881
01:27:09.859 --> 01:27:12.059
There are so many
neo-rich families sprouting!

1882
01:27:12.259 --> 01:27:13.779
'Can I compete with them?'

1883
01:27:21.313 --> 01:27:22.674
Your brother's wife

1884
01:27:23.065 --> 01:27:24.385
K.R.Vijaya

1885
01:27:26.019 --> 01:27:27.179
Clarity head to toe!

1886
01:27:27.390 --> 01:27:28.413
Oh my God!

1887
01:27:28.437 --> 01:27:29.997
Don't humiliate me

1888
01:27:30.059 --> 01:27:32.019
How to behave at a funeral

1889
01:27:32.699 --> 01:27:34.779
How everyone will be grief stricken

1890
01:27:34.903 --> 01:27:37.303
Learn all these nuances
and speak accordingly. di

1891
01:27:37.714 --> 01:27:39.474
Our relatives are all around us

1892
01:27:40.881 --> 01:27:42.315
My beloved sister

1893
01:27:42.339 --> 01:27:43.659
Whatever be the case

1894
01:27:43.699 --> 01:27:45.379
Isn't she your sister-in-law?

1895
01:27:45.619 --> 01:27:47.619
Will you keep quiet?

1896
01:27:47.674 --> 01:27:51.994
What would you have done if there was
a funeral at your house tomorrow. di?

1897
01:27:52.259 --> 01:27:54.539
I would have torn them to tatters. da!

1898
01:27:55.071 --> 01:27:57.271
'Aunt. can I have an omelet?'

1899
01:27:57.379 --> 01:27:58.779
Without onion

1900
01:28:00.137 --> 01:28:01.771
'Go easy on the powder for your face'

1901
01:28:04.659 --> 01:28:07.339
Oh! Shouldn't eat egg today. no?

1902
01:28:07.819 --> 01:28:08.882
So...sorry

1903
01:28:13.019 --> 01:28:14.101
Brother

1904
01:28:15.078 --> 01:28:17.306
I've got a good alliance
for Sakthi. shall I go ahead?

1905
01:28:18.659 --> 01:28:20.539
My dear niece. handsome groom

1906
01:28:20.779 --> 01:28:22.099
Want to see his snap?

1907
01:28:22.099 --> 01:28:23.739
Want to see me snap
like a volcano?

1908
01:28:24.859 --> 01:28:26.299
No...not like that

1909
01:28:26.819 --> 01:28:28.299
Mobile is ringing
Good omen!

1910
01:28:29.231 --> 01:28:31.481
- Shall I check that alliance?
- The problem is

1911
01:28:31.505 --> 01:28:32.505
'What happened?'

1912
01:28:32.529 --> 01:28:36.059
'She bunked college today too
We have to reach before dawn'

1913
01:28:36.099 --> 01:28:38.520
'She can't bunk college tomorrow
Sooner we leave the better'

1914
01:28:38.545 --> 01:28:40.272
'Do not call me hereafter'

1915
01:28:42.659 --> 01:28:45.148
- Hello?
- Why aren't you picking my calls?

1916
01:28:45.517 --> 01:28:47.395
Police are hounding
my house looking for you

1917
01:28:47.626 --> 01:28:48.795
Police. huh?

1918
01:28:48.819 --> 01:28:51.088
'They want to conduct an inquiry
for your entire family'

1919
01:28:51.145 --> 01:28:53.043
They claim you have killed

1920
01:28:53.179 --> 01:28:54.739
Nothing of that sort

1921
01:28:54.763 --> 01:28:57.352
My sister passed away. we came
to attend the funeral in Palakkad

1922
01:28:57.377 --> 01:28:59.391
- I don't understand
- 'We reach tomorrow morning'

1923
01:28:59.416 --> 01:29:01.846
- Can I trust you?
- 'If you don't. check my WhatsApp status'

1924
01:29:01.871 --> 01:29:03.910
Along with my sister's obituary poster

1925
01:29:03.935 --> 01:29:05.255
'Show that to the police'

1926
01:29:08.532 --> 01:29:10.632
Hey! How can you ask him
if he is the killer?

1927
01:29:10.665 --> 01:29:12.736
Planning to make them escape
by giving them a hint?

1928
01:29:13.705 --> 01:29:15.332
Kovi. bring him along
We will file an FIR

1929
01:29:15.357 --> 01:29:16.378
FIR. huh? Sir

1930
01:29:16.403 --> 01:29:18.257
I asked for tea with milk
You gave me black tea

1931
01:29:18.282 --> 01:29:20.213
- I even made tea for you
- 'He didn't add sugar'

1932
01:29:20.238 --> 01:29:21.298
'Bring him in'

1933
01:29:36.739 --> 01:29:39.979
Why is there a 'To Let' board hanging?
Is Uyir Ulag shifting from here?

1934
01:29:40.659 --> 01:29:42.699
He has given us a warning
to make us vacate

1935
01:29:44.499 --> 01:29:46.939
Let's wait and watch
who shifts where!

1936
01:29:53.779 --> 01:29:54.979
Hey!

1937
01:29:56.539 --> 01:29:58.179
The police have come into our home

1938
01:29:59.005 --> 01:30:00.085
Police?

1939
01:30:14.219 --> 01:30:16.779
Don't do it. da
We will get caught. da

1940
01:30:16.859 --> 01:30:18.059
Don't kill

1941
01:30:18.216 --> 01:30:20.335
Police will nab you. da

1942
01:30:20.359 --> 01:30:22.799
- Don't. da
- STOP IT!

1943
01:30:30.071 --> 01:30:31.911
[scream of panic]

1944
01:30:32.539 --> 01:30:33.941
Wretched woman!
[gnashing teeth]

1945
01:30:38.761 --> 01:30:40.801
[door creaking]

1946
01:30:45.819 --> 01:30:47.099
[thunder rumbling]

1947
01:30:47.326 --> 01:30:49.086
'Madhuuuu'

1948
01:30:50.751 --> 01:30:52.791
'Get up. Madhu'

1949
01:30:58.859 --> 01:31:00.359
Come to me. Madhu

1950
01:31:00.383 --> 01:31:02.019
[panic-stricken scream]

1951
01:31:05.339 --> 01:31:06.739
'Come. Madhu'

1952
01:31:06.979 --> 01:31:08.153
Come to me

1953
01:31:09.289 --> 01:31:11.648
Why did you kill me. di?

1954
01:31:12.179 --> 01:31:13.257
HUH?

1955
01:31:16.446 --> 01:31:17.926
Was it Varghese?

1956
01:31:19.101 --> 01:31:21.261
He came in my dream just now
I chased him away

1957
01:31:21.567 --> 01:31:22.767
Shoo him and sleep

1958
01:31:25.071 --> 01:31:26.467
[shouting slogans]

1959
01:31:27.268 --> 01:31:28.299
Arrest him

1960
01:31:28.339 --> 01:31:29.579
Arrest him
Arrest him!

1961
01:31:29.579 --> 01:31:31.099
Arrest the murderer

1962
01:31:31.139 --> 01:31:32.339
Move...move aside

1963
01:31:32.339 --> 01:31:33.605
Move out...go

1964
01:31:35.619 --> 01:31:37.102
'Unless we riot
you won't react'

1965
01:31:37.126 --> 01:31:39.339
- Move back
- Akka...don't

1966
01:31:39.339 --> 01:31:40.387
Akka...wait

1967
01:31:40.412 --> 01:31:42.372
How many days
since my son was killed?

1968
01:31:42.579 --> 01:31:45.066
Police haven't traced my son's murderer

1969
01:31:45.090 --> 01:31:46.132
'Give me the match box'

1970
01:31:46.156 --> 01:31:47.516
- 'Give me the damn match'
- HEY!

1971
01:31:48.619 --> 01:31:50.483
If you create a ruckus
in front of our station

1972
01:31:50.553 --> 01:31:52.060
Will your dead son come back to life?

1973
01:31:52.085 --> 01:31:54.111
'I am pressurized
100 times more than you'

1974
01:31:54.136 --> 01:31:55.256
In another 10 days

1975
01:31:55.551 --> 01:31:56.572
How did he die?

1976
01:31:56.596 --> 01:31:58.735
'Who killed him?
I'll get you the right answers'

1977
01:31:58.758 --> 01:32:00.139
Till then go home and sit quiet

1978
01:32:00.179 --> 01:32:02.059
- We can't go. sir
- Our family member is dead

1979
01:32:02.099 --> 01:32:04.455
Do you want her to die. sir?
What do you think of yourself?

1980
01:32:04.480 --> 01:32:05.546
HEY!

1981
01:32:05.779 --> 01:32:07.385
Think you are Sivaji in 'Manohara'?

1982
01:32:07.409 --> 01:32:08.421
Clear out

1983
01:32:08.779 --> 01:32:10.139
Only 10 days

1984
01:32:10.163 --> 01:32:11.563
You have only 10 days grace time

1985
01:32:11.587 --> 01:32:14.284
'If you don't find my son's murderer
you'll know my true colors'

1986
01:32:14.308 --> 01:32:15.341
Go...clear out

1987
01:32:17.299 --> 01:32:18.419
- Swami
- Sir?

1988
01:32:18.459 --> 01:32:20.699
Isn't he dealing
this case carelessly?

1989
01:32:20.846 --> 01:32:21.864
You think so?

1990
01:32:21.889 --> 01:32:24.603
Remember Varghese and he got
entangled in a scuffle earlier?

1991
01:32:24.628 --> 01:32:25.632
What. sir?

1992
01:32:27.464 --> 01:32:28.584
Hey!

1993
01:32:28.793 --> 01:32:30.426
Go...go there

1994
01:32:30.787 --> 01:32:31.906
Hey!

1995
01:32:32.059 --> 01:32:33.339
What are you up to?

1996
01:32:33.339 --> 01:32:34.739
Move...clear out

1997
01:32:35.042 --> 01:32:37.499
How dare you manhandle me
in my own area!

1998
01:32:37.539 --> 01:32:38.539
Wait...wait

1999
01:32:38.579 --> 01:32:39.619
Hey Khakhi!

2000
01:32:40.379 --> 01:32:42.419
If I dip you in Surf
you will get bleached!

2001
01:32:45.855 --> 01:32:46.935
What is your name?

2002
01:32:47.891 --> 01:32:49.139
Varghese

2003
01:32:49.278 --> 01:32:50.519
Belong to this area?

2004
01:32:51.219 --> 01:32:52.379
Okay. go

2005
01:32:53.379 --> 01:32:55.687
As soon as he heard my name
Twirly Moustache backed off?

2006
01:32:56.219 --> 01:32:58.499
Thinks he's as cool as Mysskin
Interrogating with coolers

2007
01:33:07.339 --> 01:33:08.339
Sit down

2008
01:33:11.259 --> 01:33:13.579
Sir. why is the investigation
crawling at snail speed?

2009
01:33:14.497 --> 01:33:16.349
- Whom do you want me to arrest?
- Parimala

2010
01:33:17.379 --> 01:33:18.391
How dare you hit-

2011
01:33:18.436 --> 01:33:20.699
Sir. he has humiliated Parimala to the core

2012
01:33:20.699 --> 01:33:22.779
He has uploaded photos
in Insta of Madhumitha

2013
01:33:22.819 --> 01:33:25.182
Kissed Parimala's daughter openly
in the middle of the road

2014
01:33:25.207 --> 01:33:26.808
Parimala would have confronted him

2015
01:33:28.179 --> 01:33:29.739
'What. Parimala?'

2016
01:33:30.179 --> 01:33:32.849
Varghese would've acted over smart
So Parimala would've killed him

2017
01:33:32.874 --> 01:33:35.834
'After murdering. he chopped
the hand just to confuse us. sir'

2018
01:33:35.859 --> 01:33:36.979
Any other suspects?

2019
01:33:37.019 --> 01:33:38.259
His brother-in-law and brother

2020
01:33:38.259 --> 01:33:41.379
Swag moment for us because
they think we are a pair of murderers

2021
01:33:41.419 --> 01:33:43.299
We are 'swag-baggers'!

2022
01:33:43.299 --> 01:33:45.779
Sir. his daughter Parasakthi
has a foul temper

2023
01:33:45.819 --> 01:33:48.619
One day Varghese threw an egg
on her face and humiliated her

2024
01:33:48.619 --> 01:33:50.687
Maybe she asked
her boyfriend to kill?

2025
01:33:50.866 --> 01:33:51.954
'Possibility'

2026
01:33:51.978 --> 01:33:54.618
Sengamalam's husband was killed
by this chap called Peter

2027
01:33:54.979 --> 01:33:57.419
'Sengalamalam urged Varghese
to take revenge and kill Peter'

2028
01:33:57.788 --> 01:34:00.108
'Peter's younger brother
is this chap Jomi George'

2029
01:34:00.699 --> 01:34:04.051
'Did he befriend Sengamalam
with a plan to kill Varghese maybe?'

2030
01:34:06.579 --> 01:34:07.979
Why did they kill Varghese?

2031
01:34:08.452 --> 01:34:09.613
'Gang revenge?'

2032
01:34:14.176 --> 01:34:15.376
'Humiliation?'

2033
01:34:15.645 --> 01:34:16.805
Or love?

2034
01:34:17.341 --> 01:34:18.742
This case baffles me

2035
01:34:31.277 --> 01:34:33.155
Won't you call me if you are sick?

2036
01:34:33.179 --> 01:34:34.419
I felt very weak

2037
01:34:34.899 --> 01:34:37.379
Why didn't you tell me?
You could've texted or called me

2038
01:34:38.659 --> 01:34:40.482
- Give my regards to my uncle
- Don't open it

2039
01:34:40.507 --> 01:34:41.671
How can you think I will?

2040
01:34:48.819 --> 01:34:50.139
[dog barking]

2041
01:34:54.412 --> 01:34:55.495
Yov! Parimala

2042
01:34:55.963 --> 01:34:57.008
Parimala

2043
01:34:57.033 --> 01:34:58.101
- What is it?

2044
01:34:58.583 --> 01:34:59.841
Uyir Ulag?

2045
01:35:00.699 --> 01:35:01.859
New 'jibba'?

2046
01:35:02.019 --> 01:35:04.819
Of course it's new!
What is the entire family up to?

2047
01:35:05.131 --> 01:35:06.945
- We are planning to cook
- Oho!

2048
01:35:07.306 --> 01:35:09.037
Joint effort of cooking

2049
01:35:09.061 --> 01:35:10.235
And killing too. huh?

2050
01:35:10.259 --> 01:35:12.779
Just assume we are the murderers

2051
01:35:13.179 --> 01:35:14.819
Won't a killer feel hungry?

2052
01:35:14.843 --> 01:35:16.883
- Won't he eat?
- (S)he can eat of course

2053
01:35:17.139 --> 01:35:18.379
But eat gruel in jail!

2054
01:35:18.379 --> 01:35:19.739
- Not in my house
- Yov!

2055
01:35:19.779 --> 01:35:21.099
Chee! Shut up

2056
01:35:21.739 --> 01:35:24.659
Uyir. we are in no way
connected with this murder

2057
01:35:24.699 --> 01:35:25.716
You can go

2058
01:35:25.741 --> 01:35:26.821
So you claim!

2059
01:35:27.099 --> 01:35:28.739
But I opened
and read this letter

2060
01:35:28.874 --> 01:35:30.034
You didn't kill him

2061
01:35:30.059 --> 01:35:32.339
One of your legal heirs is the killer

2062
01:35:32.339 --> 01:35:33.779
He wants 3 million. I say

2063
01:35:33.819 --> 01:35:35.085
How will you answer this?

2064
01:35:35.109 --> 01:35:36.114
30 lakhs?!

2065
01:35:36.139 --> 01:35:39.099
Ulag. that blackguard of a blackmailer

2066
01:35:39.099 --> 01:35:40.779
Keeps hiking the compound interest?

2067
01:35:40.819 --> 01:35:41.863
Huh?

2068
01:35:41.888 --> 01:35:44.931
