What are you searching for?

2310
01:46:29.339 --> 01:46:31.459
All I do is run a small scale
catering business

2311
01:46:31.483 --> 01:46:33.234
What are you looking for here?

2312
01:46:33.258 --> 01:46:34.357
'Check behind that photo'

2313
01:46:34.381 --> 01:46:36.781
I'll smash your teeth
Go inside and sit

2314
01:46:36.963 --> 01:46:38.463
'Anna. check in the kitchen'

2315
01:46:41.259 --> 01:46:42.335
Sir

2316
01:46:45.045 --> 01:46:46.929
You've cooked up
quite a smokescreen. huh?

2317
01:46:47.739 --> 01:46:50.739
If I take you under custody
you will be denied bail for sure

2318
01:46:51.374 --> 01:46:52.414
But tell me this

2319
01:46:53.220 --> 01:46:55.060
I believe you killed your son?

2320
01:46:55.682 --> 01:46:56.693
Hey Isai

2321
01:46:56.718 --> 01:46:58.290
- Bring her
- Sir?

2322
01:46:58.499 --> 01:46:59.859
Come along

2323
01:47:00.296 --> 01:47:01.337
Let go of my hand. di

2324
01:47:02.169 --> 01:47:03.407
'She is escaping. sir'

2325
01:47:08.059 --> 01:47:09.659
Stop...stop running. di

2326
01:47:10.179 --> 01:47:11.739
Run...run

2327
01:47:12.139 --> 01:47:13.539
What are you doing?

2328
01:47:13.779 --> 01:47:16.587
I asked you to find Varghese's killer
You are doing everything but that

2329
01:47:16.612 --> 01:47:19.392
Sir. we went to enquire
who killed Varghese

2330
01:47:19.494 --> 01:47:21.625
The mother has killed
her own son. sir

2331
01:47:22.059 --> 01:47:24.419
We tried to nab her
but she escaped. sir

2332
01:47:24.521 --> 01:47:25.532
Emperuman

2333
01:47:25.903 --> 01:47:26.976
Tell me. sir

2334
01:47:27.113 --> 01:47:29.033
If you lay a finger on Sengamalam

2335
01:47:29.899 --> 01:47:31.265
I'll disrobe you of your uniform

2336
01:47:31.619 --> 01:47:34.339
Sir. Sengamalam had a lover. right?

2337
01:47:34.979 --> 01:47:36.579
You want me to shift the case to CBI?

2338
01:47:37.619 --> 01:47:39.019
Don't bring in CBI. sir

2339
01:47:39.019 --> 01:47:40.139
'Then do as I say'

2340
01:47:40.179 --> 01:47:41.619
I will do the needful

2341
01:47:41.699 --> 01:47:42.773
- Sir?
- 'Tell me'

2342
01:47:42.797 --> 01:47:44.059
My name is Parimala

2343
01:47:44.099 --> 01:47:46.179
- I came to the station this morning
- 'Yes'

2344
01:47:46.303 --> 01:47:48.179
- I couldn't meet the Inspector
- 'Tell me'

2345
01:47:48.339 --> 01:47:51.019
Is he in now?
Can I meet him in person?

2346
01:47:51.321 --> 01:47:52.324
Not now

2347
01:47:52.348 --> 01:47:54.219
Varghese's mother
Sengamalam is also dead

2348
01:47:54.449 --> 01:47:55.568
Real headache

2349
01:47:55.699 --> 01:47:56.952
'Inspector has also gone there'

2350
01:47:57.265 --> 01:47:58.468
Aiyaiyo!

2351
01:47:59.647 --> 01:48:01.128
My dear 'akka'

2352
01:48:02.819 --> 01:48:04.439
[lamenting]

2353
01:48:05.739 --> 01:48:06.899
What is it. dear?

2354
01:48:07.549 --> 01:48:10.214
Varghese's mother is dead too. it seems

2355
01:48:10.732 --> 01:48:12.772
If you did something
now is the time to confess. di

2356
01:48:14.379 --> 01:48:16.979
Somewhere something has gone wrong

2357
01:48:17.939 --> 01:48:19.539
Something wrong somewhere

2358
01:48:20.499 --> 01:48:23.749
'You'll keep calling 'British British'
every second minute. akka'

2359
01:48:23.773 --> 01:48:25.733
Aiyo! Look at her. sir

2360
01:48:26.401 --> 01:48:27.899
Who will call us hereafter. akka?

2361
01:48:28.897 --> 01:48:31.045
Who will take such good care of us?

2362
01:48:31.219 --> 01:48:33.059
All of you get up. clear out

2363
01:48:35.379 --> 01:48:37.139
Akka...aiyo!

2364
01:48:37.179 --> 01:48:39.819
We don't know what to do
from now on. sir

2365
01:48:39.843 --> 01:48:40.843
Kovi

2366
01:48:42.099 --> 01:48:43.579
She escaped from our clutches

2367
01:48:43.891 --> 01:48:44.979
Who could have killed her?

2368
01:48:57.944 --> 01:48:58.972
'Pass the salna'

2369
01:48:58.997 --> 01:49:02.247
Varghese. you take good care of us
You pay us a hefty monthly salary

2370
01:49:02.272 --> 01:49:03.712
Your business is doing good too

2371
01:49:03.737 --> 01:49:05.818
Can't you give all of us
a 'sare' in your profit?

2372
01:49:09.338 --> 01:49:10.938
- What did you ask?
- Sare

2373
01:49:10.962 --> 01:49:12.162
Hit you!

2374
01:49:12.634 --> 01:49:13.859
You want a share?

2375
01:49:14.259 --> 01:49:18.219
Giving you work itself is a big deal
You have the gall to ask for a share?!

2376
01:49:19.116 --> 01:49:23.271
'If not for us. you'll be begging
like a mongrel for one square meal'

2377
01:49:23.316 --> 01:49:25.459
You are aspiring for a share!

2378
01:49:25.499 --> 01:49:27.099
Hey. I'll chop you to pieces

2379
01:49:30.405 --> 01:49:31.752
Look at his shaggy face

2380
01:49:46.219 --> 01:49:47.219
Listen. dear

2381
01:49:47.259 --> 01:49:49.059
Both our brothers
are arrested it seems

2382
01:49:49.059 --> 01:49:50.499
You hid it from me

2383
01:49:51.078 --> 01:49:52.158
If I had told you

2384
01:49:52.301 --> 01:49:53.381
Would you have saved them?

2385
01:49:57.059 --> 01:49:58.539
- Arnold?
- Sir

2386
01:49:58.539 --> 01:50:01.219
Did a man by name Parimala
from Periyapalli street come here?

2387
01:50:01.259 --> 01:50:02.288
Yes. sir

2388
01:50:02.313 --> 01:50:04.994
He said. 'don't come home
You let me know and I'll come here'

2389
01:50:05.019 --> 01:50:06.699
He said we shouldn't visit him?

2390
01:50:06.723 --> 01:50:08.443
Kovi. start the jeep
Let us pay him a visit

2391
01:50:08.476 --> 01:50:09.931
[dog barking]

2392
01:50:13.356 --> 01:50:14.411
Pa

2393
01:50:14.436 --> 01:50:15.516
'Police. pa'

2394
01:50:17.316 --> 01:50:18.475
Cool...cool

2395
01:50:18.879 --> 01:50:20.776
[dog barking]

2396
01:50:23.207 --> 01:50:25.127
Come...come. sir
Most welcome

2397
01:50:25.973 --> 01:50:27.003
Come in
Please come inside

2398
01:50:27.028 --> 01:50:28.747
Step in with your right foot forward

2399
01:50:29.416 --> 01:50:30.519
Come in

2400
01:50:35.511 --> 01:50:36.736
Please come

2401
01:50:37.596 --> 01:50:39.156
Emperuman
Inspector

2402
01:50:39.355 --> 01:50:40.795
- Hi
- Koviyan

2403
01:50:40.836 --> 01:50:42.378
- Sub inspector
- We have been waiting

2404
01:50:42.419 --> 01:50:43.919
For your visit for so many days

2405
01:50:44.942 --> 01:50:46.502
[sheepish chuckle]

2406
01:50:48.676 --> 01:50:49.986
Do I look like a politician?

2407
01:50:50.010 --> 01:50:51.475
You look like a minister

2408
01:50:51.876 --> 01:50:53.476
Sir. what will you have?

2409
01:50:53.515 --> 01:50:55.555
- Coffee or tea?
- Neither

2410
01:50:55.596 --> 01:50:56.697
What about buttermilk?

2411
01:50:59.727 --> 01:51:00.778
What is this?

2412
01:51:00.803 --> 01:51:02.802
Roasted Bengal gram and
coconut to grind a chutney

2413
01:51:03.276 --> 01:51:04.315
Keep it over there

2414
01:51:05.998 --> 01:51:07.798
Trying to scare me-

2415
01:51:08.676 --> 01:51:09.796
Aiyaiyo!

2416
01:51:09.993 --> 01:51:11.076
Have they come?

2417
01:51:11.101 --> 01:51:13.192
You didn't want your daughters
called to the station?

2418
01:51:13.217 --> 01:51:14.707
'That's why I came in plain clothes'

2419
01:51:15.355 --> 01:51:16.429
Go and sit there

2420
01:51:17.155 --> 01:51:18.355
You both take a seat

2421
01:51:19.116 --> 01:51:20.356
Sit down quickly. girls

2422
01:51:21.499 --> 01:51:22.772
You go and stand there

2423
01:51:22.796 --> 01:51:24.836
Oh! Is that my position? Right

2424
01:51:25.260 --> 01:51:26.940
Who is Parasakthi?
Who is Madhumitha?

2425
01:51:26.964 --> 01:51:28.243
Parasakthi

2426
01:51:28.314 --> 01:51:30.153
- Why are you called Poppy Molly?
- Sir?

2427
01:51:30.177 --> 01:51:31.217
Who?

2428
01:51:32.196 --> 01:51:33.516
Chittu alias Chittarasan

2429
01:51:35.219 --> 01:51:36.323
Chittu?

2430
01:51:36.731 --> 01:51:37.827
Varghese

2431
01:51:38.103 --> 01:51:40.842
So confusing. varkey. biscuit. bun?

2432
01:51:40.866 --> 01:51:42.064
Why did you kill him?

2433
01:51:42.087 --> 01:51:43.281
You know Varghese?

2434
01:51:44.116 --> 01:51:45.475
Who won't know him. sir?

2435
01:51:45.516 --> 01:51:47.343
Someone killed him recently

2436
01:51:47.661 --> 01:51:49.140
Aiyo! When?

2437
01:51:49.165 --> 01:51:50.485
[gritting teeth]

2438
01:51:54.276 --> 01:51:56.730
You are here in person
to hold an inquiry

2439
01:51:58.276 --> 01:51:59.356
'Someone' killed him

2440
01:51:59.356 --> 01:52:01.315
You don't know that 'someone'?

2441
01:52:09.104 --> 01:52:10.521
How do you know Varghese?

2442
01:52:10.688 --> 01:52:11.937
She is my younger daughter

2443
01:52:12.029 --> 01:52:13.171
She has fallen for him

2444
01:52:13.195 --> 01:52:14.903
- Dad
- Sorry. dear

2445
01:52:15.276 --> 01:52:17.035
He has fallen in love with her

2446
01:52:17.059 --> 01:52:18.539
That's how I know him

2447
01:52:18.563 --> 01:52:19.621
Correct

2448
01:52:22.601 --> 01:52:23.892
Were you in love with Varghese?

2449
01:52:23.916 --> 01:52:26.035
He was the one
who fell in love with me. sir

2450
01:52:26.130 --> 01:52:27.210
No. sir

2451
01:52:27.234 --> 01:52:29.154
He was in love with Gomathi

2452
01:52:29.178 --> 01:52:30.418
Gomathi?
[in unison]

2453
01:52:32.217 --> 01:52:34.536
He was never in love with me. sir

2454
01:52:36.267 --> 01:52:37.467
Aiyo!

2455
01:52:40.806 --> 01:52:42.086
'Axe brand balm. huh?'

2456
01:52:42.110 --> 01:52:43.367
You like that balm?

2457
01:52:43.481 --> 01:52:44.543
Look

2458
01:52:45.196 --> 01:52:46.996
I can even be without my husband

2459
01:52:47.076 --> 01:52:49.704
But I am totally addicted to this

2460
01:52:49.729 --> 01:52:50.735
Right. dear?

2461
01:52:50.760 --> 01:52:52.017
[gnashing teeth]
Lunatic!

2462
01:52:53.875 --> 01:52:55.534
Won't you keep quiet
for a while. madam?

2463
01:52:55.558 --> 01:52:57.573
No. I was being helpful
Please continue. sir

2464
01:52:57.676 --> 01:52:59.035
- 'Go ahead'
- God help me!

2465
01:52:59.916 --> 01:53:01.596
My head is splitting. child
Go on. tell me

2466
01:53:02.006 --> 01:53:03.326
Okay. pa

2467
01:53:04.156 --> 01:53:05.236
Appa?

2468
01:53:05.260 --> 01:53:07.048
Not your father
Father's younger brother!

2469
01:53:07.193 --> 01:53:08.273
Huh?

2470
01:53:09.516 --> 01:53:10.915
Sorry. appa

2471
01:53:10.956 --> 01:53:12.156
Sorry. sir

2472
01:53:12.236 --> 01:53:13.266
Yov. Kovi

2473
01:53:13.668 --> 01:53:16.236
He was in love. he was not in love
What did you do to him?

2474
01:53:16.276 --> 01:53:17.700
I did not kill him. sir

2475
01:53:17.881 --> 01:53:19.075
She is the culprit

2476
01:53:19.116 --> 01:53:21.276
- Did you kill him. di?
- Amma!

2477
01:53:21.355 --> 01:53:23.116
Sir. he was in love with my sister

2478
01:53:23.154 --> 01:53:24.731
I went and threatened him. sir

2479
01:53:24.756 --> 01:53:26.596
- 'That's all. sir'
- What did he do to you?

2480
01:53:26.596 --> 01:53:28.356
He threatened to
splash acid on my face. sir

2481
01:53:28.381 --> 01:53:31.026
Before he could harm me in any way
someone closed his chapter. sir

2482
01:53:31.051 --> 01:53:32.691
- That's all
- Oh God!

2483
01:53:32.716 --> 01:53:34.276
Looks like my head will split into two

2484
01:53:34.315 --> 01:53:35.356
[stuttering]

2485
01:53:35.381 --> 01:53:36.677
Inhale deeply

2486
01:53:36.715 --> 01:53:38.076
[sniffing hard]

2487
01:53:38.236 --> 01:53:40.555
'That's the way
Correct...right'

2488
01:53:40.716 --> 01:53:41.755
'How do you feel now?'

2489
01:53:43.315 --> 01:53:44.755
Please keep quiet. madam

2490
01:53:44.796 --> 01:53:46.621
You want me to shut up?
Okay...okay. sir

2491
01:53:46.645 --> 01:53:48.188
That duo is Raghavan and Kamatchi

2492
01:53:48.212 --> 01:53:49.756
You called and asked them to come

2493
01:53:51.156 --> 01:53:52.251
Yes?

2494
01:53:53.821 --> 01:53:54.871
Or no?

2495
01:53:58.476 --> 01:53:59.483
Yes. sir

2496
01:54:00.196 --> 01:54:01.403
We are in Chennai

2497
01:54:01.427 --> 01:54:03.475
You call that boy Varghese

2498
01:54:03.516 --> 01:54:06.076
Ask him to come near
that single tree in Duming Lane

2499
01:54:06.100 --> 01:54:07.937
- Why. uncle?
- Nothing serious. dear

2500
01:54:08.055 --> 01:54:10.602
I want to threaten him to
delete your photo in Insta

2501
01:54:10.626 --> 01:54:13.547
'Your uncle and I have come
to spend Deepavali with you'

2502
01:54:14.168 --> 01:54:15.556
Why go to such lengths. uncle?

2503
01:54:15.556 --> 01:54:18.115
'Otherwise he will dance
on top of your head. dear'

2504
01:54:18.139 --> 01:54:20.596
- 'Don't tell your parents'
- Okay

2505
01:54:20.635 --> 01:54:21.955
Madhu darling

2506
01:54:21.996 --> 01:54:23.836
I want to give you
a gift for Deepavali

2507
01:54:23.875 --> 01:54:25.208
Where should I meet you. darling?

2508
01:54:25.233 --> 01:54:26.594
Will you come to Duming Lane?

2509
01:54:29.294 --> 01:54:30.350
'Good'

2510
01:54:30.375 --> 01:54:31.455
Now tell me

2511
01:54:31.955 --> 01:54:33.058
Who is that Chittu?

2512
01:54:33.082 --> 01:54:34.602
Who is that Chittu. sir?

2513
01:54:34.927 --> 01:54:38.965
Sir. your daughter Sakthi
and that Chittu are lovers

2514
01:54:42.835 --> 01:54:44.857
He has a pet name for her

2515
01:54:45.110 --> 01:54:46.795
Poppy Molly
Do you know?

2516
01:54:47.116 --> 01:54:49.468
I've heard of Rajamouli
Who is Poppy Molly?

2517
01:54:49.646 --> 01:54:50.941
He is a drug dealer

2518
01:54:57.036 --> 01:54:58.292
Poppy means opium

2519
01:54:58.476 --> 01:55:00.516
Molly means MDMA. drug

2520
01:55:00.905 --> 01:55:02.705
What a suitable name he has coined

2521
01:55:03.876 --> 01:55:05.995
Sir. he is not that kind of chap

2522
01:55:05.995 --> 01:55:08.076
Do you know who killed Varghese?

2523
01:55:14.836 --> 01:55:16.116
What are you saying. sir?

2524
01:55:16.116 --> 01:55:17.515
Sir. he's a dummy

2525
01:55:17.635 --> 01:55:19.516
I don't know in what way he's a dummy

2526
01:55:19.555 --> 01:55:20.956
But in this matter he is king

2527
01:55:20.956 --> 01:55:22.516
I don't mean in that way. sir

2528
01:55:22.555 --> 01:55:24.481
Then what 'matter' do you mean?

2529
01:55:25.036 --> 01:55:26.886
I don't mean anything
Just forget it. pa

2530
01:55:26.995 --> 01:55:29.676
Sir. he is not that kind of boy. that's all

2531
01:55:29.716 --> 01:55:31.181
Then Raghavan and Kamatchi?

2532
01:55:31.205 --> 01:55:32.635
'He hit me'

2533
01:55:32.635 --> 01:55:35.251
Seeing him hit me. machan got angry
and shoved Varghese real hard

2534
01:55:35.276 --> 01:55:37.148
His head hit a stone
with a thud and he died

2535
01:55:37.173 --> 01:55:38.853
How did we know
a stone was on that spot?

2536
01:55:38.878 --> 01:55:40.634
He died and lay there lifeless

2537
01:55:40.659 --> 01:55:42.289
You are branding us as murderers?

2538
01:55:42.636 --> 01:55:44.875
- Yov! Send them away
- You mean we can go. sir?

2539
01:55:45.278 --> 01:55:46.757
- Clear out
- Really. sir?

2540
01:55:46.923 --> 01:55:49.313
- Can we go back to Palakkad?
- I said 'go'

2541
01:55:49.337 --> 01:55:50.888
Raghavan and Kamatchi

2542
01:55:51.140 --> 01:55:52.841
'Bashed up Varghese
That part is true'

2543
01:55:53.006 --> 01:55:54.038
'But'

2544
01:55:54.063 --> 01:55:55.249
At the same time

2545
01:55:55.315 --> 01:55:58.116
Chittu comes there to kill Varghese

2546
01:55:58.116 --> 01:56:00.636
'Watching Raghavan and
Kamatchi beat up Varghese'

2547
01:56:00.676 --> 01:56:01.836
'He takes a video'

2548
01:56:01.876 --> 01:56:03.235
Hearing some sound

2549
01:56:03.276 --> 01:56:05.436
'Raghavan and Kamatchi
flee from that spot'

2550
01:56:06.796 --> 01:56:08.275
Varghese is injured badly

2551
01:56:08.316 --> 01:56:11.995
'Chittarasan strangles him
with a steel wire'

2552
01:56:12.796 --> 01:56:14.236
The video he recorded

2553
01:56:14.275 --> 01:56:16.236
'He sent it anonymously to the police'

2554
01:56:16.236 --> 01:56:17.676
'And confused everyone'

2555
01:56:18.115 --> 01:56:21.436
Sir. he didn't even have the guts
to profess his love to me directly

2556
01:56:21.475 --> 01:56:22.956
I called and spoke to him

2557
01:56:23.236 --> 01:56:24.501
He is a good person. sir

2558
01:56:24.548 --> 01:56:26.356
You have seen his good side. dear

2559
01:56:26.395 --> 01:56:28.435
To our police team
he is a murderer

2560
01:56:30.355 --> 01:56:33.115
I thought I had given birth
to 2 rowdy-girls

2561
01:56:33.298 --> 01:56:36.458
But those 2 rowdies have
hooked on to 2 accused!

2562
01:56:36.756 --> 01:56:38.755
I just can't bear this

2563
01:56:38.916 --> 01:56:39.996
Sorry. dear

2564
01:56:42.516 --> 01:56:44.236
- Turn around
- Turn

2565
01:56:46.156 --> 01:56:47.196
Why didn't you tell me?

2566
01:56:47.236 --> 01:56:49.396
Amma said we should choose
the right time to tell you

2567
01:56:49.531 --> 01:56:51.996
Hey! Then I told you
to tell your father

2568
01:56:52.036 --> 01:56:54.316
Yes. you told me
But I broke up with him

2569
01:56:54.355 --> 01:56:55.996
That's why I didn't tell you. pa

2570
01:56:56.196 --> 01:56:58.008
Oh! Break up. huh?

2571
01:56:59.196 --> 01:57:00.331
Then what. sir?

2572
01:57:00.355 --> 01:57:02.116
They fell in love
and fell out of love

2573
01:57:02.155 --> 01:57:04.156
So your investigation stops here

2574
01:57:04.195 --> 01:57:05.356
Tell them the rest of it

2575
01:57:05.356 --> 01:57:07.956
'Appa. after that
we patched up'

2576
01:57:10.716 --> 01:57:13.116
After a break-up
why did you need a patch-up?

2577
01:57:13.315 --> 01:57:14.356
No. pa

2578
01:57:14.395 --> 01:57:17.116
'We both felt miserable
without each other'

2579
01:57:17.155 --> 01:57:18.256
So why feel terrible?

2580
01:57:18.279 --> 01:57:20.002
We talked it over
and patched up. pa

2581
01:57:20.316 --> 01:57:22.019
When I went back to tell amma

2582
01:57:22.043 --> 01:57:23.219
Game over?

2583
01:57:23.792 --> 01:57:25.992
3 break-up
2 patch-up till now. pa

2584
01:57:26.016 --> 01:57:27.776
- 'Total 5'
- Oh God!

2585
01:57:27.876 --> 01:57:30.316
Now is it a break-up
or relationship?

2586
01:57:30.835 --> 01:57:32.196
Relationship. pa

2587
01:57:32.236 --> 01:57:33.355
But we have taken a break

2588
01:57:33.396 --> 01:57:34.440
AIYO!

2589
01:57:34.519 --> 01:57:35.965
Have you given birth to a daughter?

2590
01:57:35.989 --> 01:57:38.666
Are you conducting the investigation
or did we come here to do so?

2591
01:57:39.475 --> 01:57:41.196
I swear I can't handle this. sir

2592
01:57:41.356 --> 01:57:42.955
Can I help myself to the balm?

2593
01:57:43.716 --> 01:57:46.516
Sniff hard once
into your nostrils

2594
01:57:46.540 --> 01:57:47.860
With a deep inhale

2595
01:57:49.733 --> 01:57:50.813
Aiyaiyo!

2596
01:57:50.847 --> 01:57:52.047
You know I'm in poor health!

2597
01:57:53.275 --> 01:57:54.276
Sorry. sir

2598
01:57:54.636 --> 01:57:56.155
He won't really hit me
Just for fun

2599
01:57:56.155 --> 01:57:58.156
He will make a fake strike. that's all

2600
01:57:58.675 --> 01:58:00.436
Why should Chittu kill Varghese. sir?

2601
01:58:00.475 --> 01:58:01.915
Greed for money of course

2602
01:58:03.756 --> 01:58:06.916
'Varghese was dealing with drugs
worth a mere Rs 10000 to Rs 15000'

2603
01:58:06.916 --> 01:58:09.014
'Chittu entrusted him
with drugs worth 5 million'

2604
01:58:09.038 --> 01:58:10.878
'Chittu told him to keep it safe'

2605
01:58:11.155 --> 01:58:15.036
'Can Varghese zip his lips?
He sells it to another party'

2606
01:58:15.516 --> 01:58:18.516
'Varghese lies to Chittu
claiming someone stole the stash'

2607
01:58:18.556 --> 01:58:21.115
'Unable to bear
his friend's royal betrayal'

2608
01:58:21.355 --> 01:58:23.035
Chittu kills Varghese

2609
01:58:23.035 --> 01:58:24.076
Aiyo!

2610
01:58:24.076 --> 01:58:26.956
Sir. my daughters have
no role to play in this drama

2611
01:58:27.316 --> 01:58:28.388
Be patient. sir

2612
01:58:29.196 --> 01:58:30.396
That Chittu

2613
01:58:30.635 --> 01:58:34.955
Has given your daughter Sakthi
cocaine worth 25 lakhs

2614
01:58:36.620 --> 01:58:38.419
I can't believe whatever
you are saying. sir

2615
01:58:38.444 --> 01:58:41.148
Even the police can't believe
how dangerous a criminal your lover is

2616
01:58:41.173 --> 01:58:42.692
The day before he killed Varghese

2617
01:58:42.814 --> 01:58:45.834
'He gave a fake complaint
in the station about his missing bike'

2618
01:58:46.007 --> 01:58:48.448
Police are looking
for the murderer outside

2619
01:58:48.516 --> 01:58:51.235
'Varghese's killer coolly sits
outside the police station'

2620
01:58:51.276 --> 01:58:52.756
'And he is spying on the police'

2621
01:58:52.756 --> 01:58:53.825
'Now do you realize'

2622
01:58:53.850 --> 01:58:56.610
'What a master criminal
your lover Chittu is?'

2623
01:58:56.635 --> 01:58:57.916
Wretched scoundrel!

2624
01:58:57.954 --> 01:59:00.073
Is that why you were
delayed in coming here?

2625
01:59:00.098 --> 01:59:01.133
Yes

2626
01:59:01.158 --> 01:59:03.376
Where have you hidden
the cocaine your Chittu gave you?

2627
01:59:03.401 --> 01:59:04.977
Sir. I haven't stashed any cocaine here

2628
01:59:05.002 --> 01:59:06.930
You are just asking
whatever comes to your mind?

2629
01:59:06.955 --> 01:59:08.250
I can't agree to your deductions

2630
01:59:08.275 --> 01:59:10.234
Oh! You won't accept it?

2631
01:59:11.662 --> 01:59:13.582
Hello. bring her to the station

2632
01:59:13.606 --> 01:59:15.046
I'll prove it to her using Chittu

2633
01:59:15.196 --> 01:59:16.483
Sir...sir

2634
01:59:17.041 --> 01:59:19.601
Aren't you the one
who sent us the Speed Post?

2635
01:59:19.795 --> 01:59:21.276
- What Speed Post?
- Not him

2636
01:59:22.276 --> 01:59:24.156
- Did you send?
- Not him either

2637
01:59:24.316 --> 01:59:25.516
Was it you then?

2638
01:59:26.272 --> 01:59:27.647
Yes. it was me

2639
01:59:27.736 --> 01:59:28.810
What 'Speed Post'?

2640
01:59:28.835 --> 01:59:29.993
Nothing. sir

2641
01:59:30.018 --> 01:59:33.009
I had a niggling doubt on all 3 of them
regarding this murder case

2642
01:59:33.034 --> 01:59:35.353
So I was sending them
ransom notes often

2643
01:59:35.427 --> 01:59:36.667
Why did you do that?

2644
01:59:39.197 --> 01:59:40.516
From my childhood

2645
01:59:40.555 --> 01:59:42.475
I was very keen on
joining the police force. sir

2646
01:59:42.996 --> 01:59:44.676
I'll breeze through the physical tests

2647
01:59:44.716 --> 01:59:46.716
But when it came to written tests

2648
01:59:47.236 --> 01:59:48.916
I was failing continuously

2649
01:59:49.555 --> 01:59:51.310
'After repeated attempts'

2650
01:59:51.530 --> 01:59:52.795
I crossed the eligibility age

2651
01:59:53.716 --> 01:59:55.915
Because of that police mind
churning within me

2652
01:59:56.356 --> 01:59:58.716
Even now. I was
sitting at home by myself

2653
01:59:58.756 --> 02:00:00.516
'I was doing my own investigation'

2654
02:00:01.898 --> 02:00:03.138
That's all. sir

2655
02:00:03.636 --> 02:00:05.155
Thank God you failed the test

2656
02:00:11.525 --> 02:00:13.964
Hey! What have you done with your life?

2657
02:00:14.432 --> 02:00:16.171
The Inspector is saying
all kinds of stuff

2658
02:00:16.196 --> 02:00:17.196
Sorry. Molly

2659
02:00:17.221 --> 02:00:18.857
I'll hit you if you call me
'Poppy Molly'

2660
02:00:19.207 --> 02:00:21.515
You have given me cocaine
worth 25 lakhs it seems

2661
02:00:21.540 --> 02:00:23.059
Pothead
Weed junkie!

2662
02:00:23.995 --> 02:00:25.592
Did you really do all this?

2663
02:00:25.653 --> 02:00:26.813
Yes. Molly

2664
02:00:26.837 --> 02:00:27.873
Sorry

2665
02:00:27.898 --> 02:00:28.978
Sakthi

2666
02:00:29.003 --> 02:00:31.124
Then did you kill Varghese and Mustafa?

2667
02:00:31.956 --> 02:00:33.676
Why are you looking there?
Answer me

2668
02:00:37.906 --> 02:00:40.057
Then where did you hide
that stash worth 2.5 million?

2669
02:00:40.593 --> 02:00:42.073
In your house

2670
02:00:43.876 --> 02:00:45.810
'The cops came to your house
when I was leaving'

2671
02:00:46.356 --> 02:00:49.075
'I got scared and hid it
in a carton in your box'

2672
02:00:49.636 --> 02:00:52.795
You planned this deliberately
trying to get all of us behind bars

2673
02:00:53.171 --> 02:00:54.194
Tell me. da

2674
02:00:54.258 --> 02:00:55.279
Safe-

2675
02:00:55.600 --> 02:00:56.616
Safety measure

2676
02:00:56.781 --> 02:00:57.971
'Is this the way to earn?'

2677
02:00:58.023 --> 02:01:00.756
'Do you need to earn
in this crooked way?'

2678
02:01:01.578 --> 02:01:02.641
Thanks. ma

2679
02:01:02.666 --> 02:01:04.289
Why thank me
for spitting on his face?

2680
02:01:04.329 --> 02:01:07.119
He didn't respond to our questioning
He opened up immediately to you

2681
02:01:07.437 --> 02:01:09.197
He is very true to your love

2682
02:01:09.744 --> 02:01:11.052
Kovi. did you
record everything?

2683
02:01:11.076 --> 02:01:12.316
- Pucca record. sir
- Very good

2684
02:01:13.034 --> 02:01:15.459
Will you return the stash in your place?

2685
02:01:15.484 --> 02:01:16.564
Aiyo!

2686
02:01:18.676 --> 02:01:19.756
Sakthi

2687
02:01:21.115 --> 02:01:22.596
- Sakthi
- Kovi. follow her

2688
02:01:22.596 --> 02:01:23.875
- Okay. sir
- Sakthi

2689
02:01:23.912 --> 02:01:25.744
Sakthi. it is true I smuggled drugs

2690
02:01:26.956 --> 02:01:28.636
'But I didn't plan to kill anyone'

2691
02:01:29.596 --> 02:01:30.625
- Sakthi
- Parasakthi

2692
02:01:30.650 --> 02:01:31.697
'I swear-'

2693
02:01:33.419 --> 02:01:34.423
'Sakthi'

2694
02:01:34.756 --> 02:01:36.196
Do you know Naveen?

2695
02:01:36.316 --> 02:01:37.327
Friend. sir

2696
02:01:37.351 --> 02:01:39.054
He died. he was
like a brother to me

2697
02:01:42.077 --> 02:01:43.277
He is my son

2698
02:01:45.636 --> 02:01:47.476
Thank you
Thank you for everything

2699
02:01:47.515 --> 02:01:48.595
Go home safe

2700
02:01:55.758 --> 02:01:57.558
- Sudhandhiram
- What happened?

2701
02:01:58.156 --> 02:01:59.956
Everything is over

2702
02:01:59.995 --> 02:02:01.766
We don't have any problem hereafter

2703
02:02:02.035 --> 02:02:05.092
We have stacked those old cartons

2704
02:02:05.116 --> 02:02:06.274
Inside one of those boxes

2705
02:02:06.796 --> 02:02:08.635
That boy has hidden the cocaine

2706
02:02:08.659 --> 02:02:10.459
Keep it safe
I'll be home soon

2707
02:02:10.704 --> 02:02:12.024
Good lord!

2708
02:02:12.355 --> 02:02:15.396
Didn't I clean up the whole house
the day my sister was visiting us?

2709
02:02:15.396 --> 02:02:17.168
I disposed everything
on weight basis. dear

2710
02:02:17.192 --> 02:02:18.512
[shocked gasp]

2711
02:02:22.568 --> 02:02:23.617
Soooper!

2712
02:02:24.235 --> 02:02:26.359
- Super. dear
- How did I know?

2713
02:02:26.386 --> 02:02:28.513
Middle class family members

2714
02:02:28.609 --> 02:02:30.133
Whichever the place
Whatever the time

2715
02:02:30.157 --> 02:02:31.171
Not even a single day

2716
02:02:31.195 --> 02:02:34.075
He won't let them relax
heaving a sigh of relief

2717
02:02:35.035 --> 02:02:36.222
That God

2718
02:02:36.245 --> 02:02:37.299
Am I right?

2719
02:02:38.153 --> 02:02:39.162
Thank You!

2720
02:02:44.196 --> 02:02:45.242
Come

2721
02:02:46.956 --> 02:02:48.115
Sakthi

2722
02:02:49.643 --> 02:02:51.053
Varghese's murderer

2723
02:02:51.676 --> 02:02:53.076
It wasn't Chittu. dear

2724
02:02:53.643 --> 02:02:55.083
Then who. pa?

2725
02:02:56.946 --> 02:02:58.972
'Sakthi. it is true I smuggled drugs'

2726
02:02:59.066 --> 02:03:00.756
'But I did not kill anyone'

2727
02:03:00.908 --> 02:03:02.596
'Sakthi. I swear this is the truth'

2728
02:03:05.811 --> 02:03:07.195
I've tracked down your network

2729
02:03:07.195 --> 02:03:09.474
You have to go behind bars
for the crime you committed

2730
02:03:09.498 --> 02:03:11.259
That's of no use to you or to me

2731
02:03:11.441 --> 02:03:12.481
One other option

2732
02:03:12.916 --> 02:03:14.395
I have to kill you right here

2733
02:03:14.596 --> 02:03:16.567
That serves no purpose
to me or to you

2734
02:03:16.756 --> 02:03:18.136
I'll offer a soooper deal for you

2735
02:03:18.160 --> 02:03:19.321
Kill that Varghese

2736
02:03:19.521 --> 02:03:22.516
You take over his business
and carry on. we share 50-50

2737
02:03:22.555 --> 02:03:25.555
You handle the business shrewdly
I'll back you up and take good care of you

2738
02:03:25.555 --> 02:03:28.371
Or else 25 years in Puzhal jail
stuck within 4 dirty walls eating gruel

2739
02:03:28.396 --> 02:03:29.770
Business or broth?

2740
02:03:53.413 --> 02:03:54.666
Why should I kill Mustafa. sir?

2741
02:03:54.691 --> 02:03:56.172
If you don't. we'll get caught. da

2742
02:03:59.625 --> 02:04:01.467
You are poking your nose unnecessarily

2743
02:04:02.491 --> 02:04:03.852
I'm warning you

2744
02:04:03.876 --> 02:04:04.915
LISTEN TO ME

2745
02:04:04.956 --> 02:04:06.235
Hey! The gun may go off

2746
02:04:06.276 --> 02:04:07.816
HEAR ME OUT. DA

2747
02:04:17.236 --> 02:04:18.701
Sir. I won't kill
Varghese's mother

2748
02:04:18.724 --> 02:04:19.971
I won't let you kill her either

2749
02:04:19.999 --> 02:04:21.916
I got to know the real 'aroma'
of her cooking

2750
02:04:21.955 --> 02:04:24.276
That Inspector is the main culprit
for everything. Chittu

2751
02:04:25.195 --> 02:04:26.875
He must have killed my son

2752
02:04:39.835 --> 02:04:40.956
Hey kiddo

2753
02:04:41.436 --> 02:04:42.676
Why are you off color?

2754
02:04:42.715 --> 02:04:46.276
Seniors are using drugs
in the college bus and torturing us. pa

2755
02:04:46.315 --> 02:04:48.355
- Go and complain
- Don't complain

2756
02:04:48.379 --> 02:04:50.020
- You go in another bus
- Shut up. di

2757
02:04:50.113 --> 02:04:53.913
Sir. seniors are using drugs
in the college bus and torturing us

2758
02:04:54.019 --> 02:04:55.066
Ask them to meet me

2759
02:04:55.091 --> 02:04:56.411
Is this college
or something else?

2760
02:04:56.436 --> 02:04:57.796
I am suspending you for 1 month

2761
02:04:57.835 --> 02:04:58.901
Sir...sir. please sir

2762
02:04:58.925 --> 02:05:00.436
If you repeat this once more

2763
02:05:00.556 --> 02:05:01.569
I have to dismiss you

2764
02:05:01.593 --> 02:05:03.480
- Don't do this to us. sir
- Get out of my room

2765
02:05:03.504 --> 02:05:05.063
'Don't hit me. bro
It hurts. don't hit'

2766
02:05:05.088 --> 02:05:06.454
I didn't tell. bro
Please let me go

2767
02:05:06.479 --> 02:05:08.608
'Yes. his name is Naveen'

2768
02:05:08.632 --> 02:05:11.778
'He had the gall to
snitch on us to the Principal'

2769
02:05:12.961 --> 02:05:14.196
Hit him

2770
02:05:17.281 --> 02:05:18.727
'You deserve to die'

2771
02:05:18.970 --> 02:05:20.929
Smash your face
beyond recognition

2772
02:05:22.396 --> 02:05:23.490
Hello?

2773
02:06:52.123 --> 02:06:55.442
'In India. only in Tamil Nadu
there is 0% drugs usage'

2774
02:06:55.476 --> 02:06:56.836
'Because of crimes elsewhere'

2775
02:06:56.836 --> 02:06:58.756
'No one can blame Tamil Nadu in toto'

2776
02:06:58.756 --> 02:07:00.636
'Within 24 hours of the crime'

2777
02:07:00.676 --> 02:07:02.978
'Tamil Nadu Police department
has imprisoned the accused'

2778
02:07:03.003 --> 02:07:04.603
'Law & order here is-'

2779
02:07:10.915 --> 02:07:13.756
'Sir. I'm not standing before you
as a police man in uniform'

2780
02:07:13.756 --> 02:07:16.466
1000s of children are sacrificed
to the scourge of drug abuse

2781
02:07:16.795 --> 02:07:18.636
I stand here as one such father. sir

2782
02:07:18.916 --> 02:07:20.556
Drug trafficking
has to be wiped out. sir

2783
02:07:20.682 --> 02:07:22.915
It has spread like cancer
in our society. sir

2784
02:07:23.196 --> 02:07:24.475
If a 13 year old boy

2785
02:07:24.796 --> 02:07:26.635
Gets addicted to drugs for 3 years

2786
02:07:26.635 --> 02:07:28.664
He becomes mad in 4-5 years

2787
02:07:28.775 --> 02:07:30.003
He goes to an early grave. sir

2788
02:07:30.237 --> 02:07:31.455
This has to be eradicated. sir

2789
02:07:31.490 --> 02:07:33.546
Otherwise a whole generation
will be eliminated. sir

2790
02:07:33.571 --> 02:07:35.607
'The present generation
is excelling in studies'

2791
02:07:35.632 --> 02:07:37.112
'Jobs. sports'

2792
02:07:37.137 --> 02:07:38.616
'Lawyers fighting for justice'

2793
02:07:38.641 --> 02:07:40.428
'Police who will stand up
against injustice'

2794
02:07:40.453 --> 02:07:42.024
'They are showing good progress. sir'

2795
02:07:42.049 --> 02:07:45.529
'In the midst of this dream is a gang
peddling poison called drugs'

2796
02:07:47.196 --> 02:07:48.595
'If we don't eliminate this gang'

2797
02:07:48.636 --> 02:07:50.395
Our land will end up
as a grave yard. sir

2798
02:07:50.635 --> 02:07:51.756
Only solution

2799
02:07:51.916 --> 02:07:53.556
Power held in the hands of our superiors

2800
02:07:53.916 --> 02:07:55.315
If you hand it over to us

2801
02:07:56.476 --> 02:07:58.356
We will wipe out
this drug mafia. sir

2802
02:07:58.756 --> 02:08:00.516
We will control drug abuse. sir

2803
02:08:00.996 --> 02:08:01.996
Emperuman

2804
02:08:02.116 --> 02:08:04.195
I may have an IPS degree to my name

2805
02:08:04.458 --> 02:08:07.236
But a minister who has passed
a mere 10th grade has more power

2806
02:08:07.636 --> 02:08:08.714
What do you want me to do?

2807
02:08:08.738 --> 02:08:11.591
'Instead of challenging the system
just salute and do your assigned job'

2808
02:08:36.357 --> 02:08:37.941
'Sir. drug addict'

2809
02:08:49.728 --> 02:08:51.168
'You robbed me of authority'

2810
02:08:51.595 --> 02:08:53.916
'But I converted your system as my weapon'

2811
02:08:54.513 --> 02:08:55.716
'In our country'

2812
02:08:55.756 --> 02:08:57.556
'Even if one person
dares to deal with drugs'

2813
02:08:57.955 --> 02:08:59.916
'I. Emperuman.
will stand before him'

2814
02:09:00.556 --> 02:09:01.996
'And destroy him'

2815
02:09:07.983 --> 02:09:09.038
Taken everything?

2816
02:09:09.063 --> 02:09:10.946
I'll return your deposit
minus rent for 3 months

2817
02:09:11.292 --> 02:09:12.972
Take rent for 10 months altogether

2818
02:09:12.996 --> 02:09:14.356
That is your wish

2819
02:09:14.395 --> 02:09:16.836
Have you committed to another murder?

2820
02:09:18.196 --> 02:09:20.155
Don't rejoice too much
over another man's sorrow

2821
02:09:20.995 --> 02:09:22.842
When you have trouble
knocking at your door

2822
02:09:22.866 --> 02:09:24.626
No one will be around
to cry with you

2823
02:09:24.817 --> 02:09:26.592
No one will come to help
when I am in trouble

2824
02:09:26.617 --> 02:09:28.536
Quoting old proverbs
in the form of a new dialog

2825
02:09:28.561 --> 02:09:30.376
Go and take Sudhandhiram to Pala-

2826
02:09:30.401 --> 02:09:31.889
'You should have aimed at his mouth'

2827
02:09:31.914 --> 02:09:33.145
Go. be confident

2828
02:09:33.169 --> 02:09:34.489
All of you will be behind bars

2829
02:09:34.513 --> 02:09:36.304
subtitled by rekhs

2830
02:09:36.328 --> 02:09:38.418
subtitled by rekhs
calibrated by pradeep

2831
02:09:39.036 --> 02:09:40.428
- Anna
- Tell me

2832
02:09:40.489 --> 02:09:42.541
Koviyan has snitched
about you to Asst Commissioner

2833
02:09:42.566 --> 02:09:44.955
Sir. Inspector Emperuman
is behind all these murders

2834
02:09:44.980 --> 02:09:46.032
Seriously?

2835
02:09:46.057 --> 02:09:49.165
Not only that. he has planned to
kill Chittu serving jail term. sir

2836
02:09:49.863 --> 02:09:50.873
'Chittu?'

2837
02:09:50.898 --> 02:09:52.323
'He has to hang from a fan today'

2838
02:09:52.396 --> 02:09:53.836
- Okay. anna
- Hey!

2839
02:09:54.310 --> 02:09:56.571
You can't see such a father
anywhere in the world. girls

2840
02:09:56.596 --> 02:09:59.219
Will anyone shift all the stuff
in such a higgledy piggledy way?

2841
02:10:00.115 --> 02:10:01.515
Inspector

2842
02:10:02.164 --> 02:10:03.305
Switch on the speaker

2843
02:10:03.330 --> 02:10:05.689
Sakthi. I'll follow you
wherever you go

2844
02:10:06.595 --> 02:10:09.289
Whatever dilemma you are in
I will ensure you are safe

2845
02:10:09.313 --> 02:10:10.349
Okay. sir

2846
02:10:10.374 --> 02:10:11.454
Not 'sir'. my dear

2847
02:10:11.754 --> 02:10:12.795
Dad

2848
02:10:13.218 --> 02:10:14.379
Okay. pa

2849
02:10:14.842 --> 02:10:16.282
'Inspector sir'

2850
02:10:16.464 --> 02:10:17.504
Parimala speaking

2851
02:10:18.316 --> 02:10:20.635
I am indebted to you
for this protection always. sir

2852
02:10:20.709 --> 02:10:24.361
- But first you be safe and sound
- Why?

2853
02:10:24.385 --> 02:10:28.315
Every truth. at all times. truth be told
cannot be hidden from everyone. sir

2854
02:10:28.938 --> 02:10:31.293
We know every single deed you did

2855
02:10:31.915 --> 02:10:33.115
What do you know?

2856
02:10:33.115 --> 02:10:34.915
[triumphant laughter]

2857
02:10:35.145 --> 02:10:37.691
I will share those details
with you in Part II. sir

2858
02:10:38.789 --> 02:10:41.076
[know-it-all laughter]

2859
02:10:43.970 --> 02:10:46.451
'Tearing us apart'

2860
02:10:51.336 --> 02:10:55.824
"Who are you to block the way?
Step inside and see the play!"

2861
02:10:56.178 --> 02:11:00.858
"A deadly game where lives are lost
Facing the gun. you pay the cost"
